Began well from the one draw, tracked leader to straight, obtained run through a tight passage shortly after straightening, hit the front inside the 200 metres to assert.
Ridden early settling in 4th within 3L of pace, switched out for a run entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Moderate start, soon picked up to rear of midfield on rails, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, finished off race well closing stages.
Jumped moderately from a wide gate, ridden forward to race 2-wide one length back in 2nd, in similar position entering straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well, settled just better than midfield mainly in 4L 5th on rails, gained closer entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Began from the widest gate, remained wide behind midfield, ran home at the same pace.
Quickly into lead on rails setting a typical pace, unable to sustain run passing the 200 metres, dropped out.
Jumped moderately, trailed the field to straight only running past well-beaten horses.
Jumped moderately, never seen with a chance in last few.
Jumped well enough, but soon dropped to last few.
Broke well enough, raced keenly and wide without cover in better than midfield far side, gave ground steadily from around home bend.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in the lead, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, took rail, dashed strongly 250M.
Eased back, along nicely along the fence, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, took rail, blocked 4-2, dashed well when clear.
In front of midfield 2 wide, just held ground in final stages.
Pushed forward 2-3 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Failed to muster despite being vigorously ridden along, midfield 2 wide, checked first bend, no turn of foot.
Behind midfield along the fence, checked severely first bend, ran on fairly in straight.
Checked start, at back 2 wide, no progress.
Eased back, 2 wide, never a factor.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, dropped off rapidly 500M.
Sent forward to take the fence and led comfortably, kicked clear soon after straightening, scored easily by 4Ls.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, finished off well for 2nd.
At back, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, saved ground turning in, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Eased back from the widest gate, travelled 10Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, closed off well for 4th.
Midfield without cover early, gradually moved forward to settle outside the leader from 1900M, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, kept on well until final stages weakened.
Taken back from a wide barrier, travelled 12Ls behind the leader on the fence, saved ground turning in, made some ground in straight without any serious threat.
Camped midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, gradually moved forward 700M, kept on one pace until 100M weakened.
Settled midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, unable to show any acceleration in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made no impression in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, never ran on.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, under pressure 600M, flattened badly rounding the Home Turn, finished tailed out.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, found cover 1200M, dropped off 600M, finished tailed out.
Fast break to lead on rail, 0.5L up & began to extend 400m, driven for home turning in, pressed in run, held on.
Sharp start & raced rail 1 back, shifted out entering stretch & ridden to 2nd 250m, closed under strong drive, just failed.
Moderate start, restrained to race near rear on rail, niggled 600m, shifted out & driven into stretch, strong closer to grab 3rd late.
Broke ok, early pace to advance & sit handy 3 wide no cover, niggled 430m, every chance but outpaced, boxed on evenly.
Sluggish start, bustled forward to sit midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 400m, kept on centre track without threatening.
Fast start & rousted to dispute lead, soon settled 2nd 1 off, niggled 400m, under pump turning in, all out when lost 2nd 250m & slight bump, tapered to wire.
Broke ok, settled back 1 off near tail, shifted 3 deep for minor advance 430m, widest in stretch run, kept on tepidly.
Slow start, driven initially, over-raced 1050m, parked rail midfield, niggled 450m, plugged on tamely.
Tardy break, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, ridden along 400m, found nil & soon empty, eased when beaten.
Slow start raced rail at tail, niggled 450m, driven into stretch but found nothing & never a factor.
Taken back from wide gate to sit last pair 1 off, niggled into final turn, driven 300m, found nil.
Smart start, bustled initially to park 1 back on rail, niggled 500m, driven into stretch, quickened to lead 120m, drew clear.
Broke well, bustled throughout to race 1 back 1 off 4th, lost ground & hard at it turning in, boxed on & closed late to snag 2nd on nod.
Fast break, posted outside leader, niggled 600m, hard-ridden 400m, battled past fading longtime leader at 50m but no match for winner, lost 2nd at wire.
Speed to lead, to rail 800m, extended 1L clear 550m, rolled off fence & shaken up 300m, all out & headed 120m, tapered to wire.
Smart start, snagged to slot midfield 1 off with cover, hard-ridden & shifted out home turn, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke ok, raced rail midfield, niggled throughout, under pump 450m, stayed on moderately.
Slow start & last, soon advanced & to rail behind midfield, off heels 550m, shaken up 250m, tight for room & shifted out, still not fully clear, kept on late & bumped close home.
Sharp start, soon outpaced & rousted, bustled along 3 wide no cover back of midfield, driven turning in, plugged home one pace.
Sharp break, restrained to 3 wide with cover near rear, ridden 450m, plugged on evenly.
Slow start, raced 1 off with cover near tail, hard-ridden into stretch, plodded on without consequence.
Taken back from widest gate, trapped 4 deep no cover until restrained to tail 600m, taken to rail 480m, 2L adrift turning in, plodded on past beaten rival.
Slow start, raced rail near tail, ridden on turn, found nil in weak effort.
Settled in midfield along the rail, 4L behind the leader, once straightened dashed strongly to score.
Urged forward from the widest barrier to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, headed by the eventual winner at 200M, closed off okay.
Travelled in midfield, 4-3/4L off 2 wide with cover, dashed at 200M, finished off well for 3rd.
Pushed forward and sat in box-seat, 2-1/2L behind the leader, no dash in the Straight, just held on for 4th.
Pushed forward sat one-off and one-behind the leader, finished off only one paced.
Settled in worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow pace, made steady ground.
In front of midfield, 2-1/2 L off 2 wide with cover, responded little when asked in the Straight, not competitive.
Settled in worse than midfield, 6L behind 2 wide with cover, little dash at 200M, weakened after 150M.
Sat towards the rear along the rail, 6-3/4L behind the leader, slight progress before weakening badly approaching 100M.
At rear, 7-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, never threatened.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
In midfield, 3-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, finished tailed out. (Bled from both nostrils)
Jumped well, not pushed, settling 3-back, one-off. Taken 3-wide turning for home, hit front 250m, tiring final stages but held.
Restrained on jumping and taken back, settling at rear between horses. Taken wide in straight, finished strongly, just failed.
Ridden along early, cutting to fence 3-back 1000m. Left fence entering turn, switched out 250m for clear run, finished off nicely.
Outpaced early, dropping to clear last back stretch. Swung wide entering straight and finished off strongly.
Pressed forward from outside draw settling one-back, one-off 1000m. Rolled forward 400m, hit front 280m, caught shortly after, boxed on.
Ridden to hold fence inside leader to 800m before taking the sit. Took inside run on straightening but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, not pushed, dropping behind midfield but held 3-wide without cover. Wide around turn, one-paced in straight.
First out but not pushed, setting in box seat back stretch. Shuffled two-back entering turn, no room top of straight, boxed on.
Allowed to find own pace, settling four-back one-off back stretch. Urged forward 500m, wide into straight, one-paced.
Pressed forward to take clear lead passing 900m. Under pressure turning for home, collared 280m, faded.
Pressed forward 4-wide, unable to cross in and dropped back 1000m. Widest into straight, found nothing under hard riding.
Began fairly, ridden to hold fence four-back from leader. Lost position around turn and tailed off passing 200m.
Sat 2-3Ls behind runaway leader, moved up to challenge 400M, soon opened up a good lead on straightening, kept on well to the line and fully in control final 100M.
Slow to muster speed despite being ridden along, held up behind midfield, brought wide nearing 400M, ran on well to go 2nd near line but not getting to winner.
Settled in 5th, 2-wide in mid-division, kept on mildly turning home, couldn't get to winner, lost 2nd late stages.
Taken across behind runners, in rear group 10Ls off the pace early and middle stages, ran on well final 300M but had too much to make up.
Positively ridden, held up about 4Ls behind runaway leader, moved to a contending position 500M, kept on moderately on straightening.
Positioned ahead of midfield 4Ls behind runaway leader, had every chance turning in, turned one pace 200M.
Began only fairly, held up near the rear 9Ls off the pace, moved closer home turn, stayed on only fairly, never a threat to leaders.
Taken back after the start, settled down towards rear 8Ls off the strong pace, driven along 500M but didn't muster the speed to challenge.
Held up in midfield 6Ls behind runaway leader, kept to inside turning in, ran on same pace, faded late stages.
Dropped back to last over 10Ls off the strong pace, plenty to make up 400M but made limited progress only, never threatened. (No Vet findings.)
Taken back but Unable to slot in, 3-wide no cover after 1300M, 7Ls to make up 400M but didn't respond to riding. (No Vet findings.)
Strode to the lead 1300M, set good pace in front and opened up 3Ls lead mid-race, weakened nearing 400M, gave way.

Broke well from a poor draw, settled wide in rear of midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, ran on to assert authority over 200 metres out.
Soon in prominent position despite an awkward start, settled 2L back in 5th far side in muddling pace, held every chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.

Taken back to midfield near rails, snuck up to 2L 4th entering back straight, remained similar turning for home, tight on rails early in straight and forced to steady over 200 metres out, fought on to re-gain place late.
Moderate start, soon dropped to tail-end, trailed the field to straight, made significant progress in the run to finish.
Moderate start from the widest gate, gradually shifted back to just worse than midfield near rails, came under pressure entering straight, no extra inside final 200 metres.
Made use of the one draw to lead on rails setting a muddling pace, headed under pressure when no extra over 200 metres out.
Broke well from a middle draw, travelled in 2nd outside the leader to straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Settled in last few, saved ground entering straight, only ran past well-beaten horses.
Jumped fairly, failed to muster despite ridden along, raced keenly in midfield in slackened pace far side, no extra after straightening.
Soon dropped to rear despite ridden along, never seen with a chance.
Settled mainly in midfield on rails, slightly close up when pace slackened on far side, dropped out inside final 300 metres.
Ridden early, settled for better than midfield 3-wide position far side, yielded ground on home bend. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped fairly, travelled very wide without cover in better than midfield, widest runner entering straight, never recovered.
Pressed on from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover in a prominent position, dropped out under pressure from rounding home bend.
Eased back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, 3 wide, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, closed off strongly when clear.
Midfield along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the sectionals, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden forward to hold the rail and keep up with the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, at back along the fence, suited by the fast pace, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Slow away, at rear 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no turn of foot.
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 3 wide at back, never improved.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Very slow away, never competitive.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, dashed well to score by 1L.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, finished off nicely for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace to the line for 4th.
At back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow pace, switched widest turning in and made plenty of ground in straight.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on only fairly and well beaten over the last furlong.
Sent forward from a wide gate, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until final furlong weakened.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, only passed few tired runners in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, made no impression in straight.
Eased to worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow pace, switched wide turning in, never ran on.
Always at rear despite hard ridden along throughout, never looked likely.
Camped midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily until checked 250M, never a factor thereafter.
Driven forward to park outside the leader, despite suited by the slow tempo, flattened 300M.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on until 300M weakened.
Fast start, snagged 1st turn to sit 1 off with cover midfield, niggled for progress 550m, lacked toe turning in & rousted , grinding run to overhaul leader late.
Broke well, wide no cover 1st turn, tracked behind 2nd 1 off with cover, driven & shifted out 400m, grinding run to lead 230m, emptied & headed close home.
Missed break, settled rail at rear of main pack, edged 1 off 1100m, progress & darted to rail 500m, run blocked 420m, shifted out & driven 350m, powered home late.
Disputed early lead, soon settled 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed lead 550m, upsides & ridden into stretch, led 380m, headed under pressure 230m, tapered.
Broke ok, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, advanced under pump from 500m to 4th 350m, peaked on run 200m & tapered.
Smart start, rousted to dispute lead early strides, soon headed & settled rail midfield, niggled 700m, shifted 1 off final turn & driven, plugged on evenly.
Moderate start, raced back of midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, driven 400m, boxed on for minor headway, eased late when beaten.
Missed break, bustled initially & raced 1 off near rear, niggled 1100m & pushed 3 wide with cover, advanced a spot 800m, driven wide into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Outpaced & rousted at break, slotted rail back of midfield, unable to hold position 800m & bustled, stayed on tepidly centre track.
Disputed early lead, soon kicked clear & snagged rail, pressed final turn, driven but headed 380m, weakened to wire.
Broke well, rousted until settled back handy on rail, niggled to 3rd 700m, ridden under pressure turning in, found nil & faded tamely.
Lacked pace, soon 2nd last & detached from main pack, ridden 750m, empty turning in & eased, tailed off.
Smart start, 5 wide no cover 1st turn, back to behind midfield 1300m, pushed forward wide no cover to sit handily 3 deep 1000m, backpedalled 600m, tailed off.
Missed break & raced last, soon well adrift of next runner, ridden along until turning in, tailed off & eased.
Tardy break, raced midfield on rail, shifted out home turn, driven 400m & quickened down inner to lead 100m, drew clear.
Moderate start, parked midfield 3 deep with cover, to 1 off 800m, switched wide final turn & ridden, quickened to edge brief lead 150m, headed 100m, held in run.
Fast start, settled handy 1 off with cover, driven 420m & switched out, quickened to press lead, not a threat in solid run home, held on for 3rd.
Fast start, disputed lead 3 deep, to rail 900m & narrow lead, shaken up 350m, all out & headed 100m, tapered to wire.
Outpaced at start, rousted initially, settled near rear 1 off, widest into stretch & driven 400m, ran on centre track for sound inroads.
Decent break, taken back to 1 off with cover behind midfield, bustled briefly backstretch, fanned wide final turn, driven 400m, swept home for solid late headway.
Broke ok, slotted back of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out 400m & driven, closed off for late inroads.
Fast break & prominent 1 off, settled 1 back 900m, shifted 3 deep to challenge 500m, progress to 2nd & ridden 400m, emptied 200m & swamped.
Smart break, settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, to rail 800m, edged out home turn, crowded in run, driven 300m, boxed on evenly.
Awkward start, bustled early to sit rear pair 1 off, last turning in & driven, stayed on for minor headway centre track.
Awkward start, raced rail last pair, minor progress on turn, hard-ridden 400m, boxed on moderately.
Moderate break, raced rail behind midfield, tight for room 350m, switched out, not tested in run, jockey lost right stirrup at start.
Sharp break widest & ridden to dispute lead 4 wide, to 1 off 900m & close 2nd, niggled 550m, ridden 430m, one-paced & emptied 200m, weakened out.
Broke well, raced rail close up until settled 1 back 900m, under pump 400m, found nil & faded tamely.
Ridden forward from barrier 9 to sit outside the leader, 1-1/4L behind, eased home to victory.
At rear along the rail, 7-1/2L behind the leader, kept pushing and finished off well for 2nd.
Failed to muster speed early, then taken back to settle towards the rear 7-1/4L off 2 wide with cover, ran on okay.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/2L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off only fairly.
Rolled forward to take box-seat, sat 2-1/2L behind the leader, fair run ended when bumped at 200M.
Settled in worse than midfield, 6-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, no dash and never threatened.
In midfield along the rail, 4-3/4L off the pace, remained along the rail in the Straight, hampered near 150M, did not run on.
Sat towards the rear along the rail, 6-1/2L behind the leader, made ground steadily until badly checked at 150M.
Rolled forward to lead along the rail by 1-1/4L, headed at 350M, gave ground thereafter.
Sat in front of midfield, 3L off the pace 2 wide with cover, ridden early when rounding turn, dropped off soon after straightening.
Lunged at gate and lost ground start, taken to fence, trailed field to straight, got split 350m, hit front 150m, held off late challenge.
Bumped heavily start, urged forward but stuck 4-wide without cover in midfield. Turned wide, finished strongly down centre track.
Jumped OK, ridden to find cover, settling along rail 4-back from leader. Finished strongly in straight while weaving about to find clear running.
Hampered start, pushed forward, settling outside hind quarters of leader. Rolled forward passing 200m to look a chance, flattened close home.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Joined up front passing 200m but kept on well until shifting out abruptly close home. Not ridden out.
Allowed to find own pace, settling three-wide behind midfield. Inconvenienced passing 1000m, got close to heels 700m, widest in straight, one-paced.
Hampered start, urged forward, taking box seat. Came off fence on straightening, kept on steadily until one-paced close home.
Hampered start, ridden to hold rail 3-back from leader. Stayed on rail in straight but only one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced start, pushed forward 3-wide, 2L from leader. Taken wider in straight, made ground to 200m before tiring.
No early pace, settling at rear in one-off position. Well back turning for home, switched out straight but made little headway.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling at rear but wide. Very wide in straight but found nothing under pressure.
Began well, urged forward but raced fiercely between horses 2L from leader. Under pressure 400m, shifted out abruptly 200m when giving ground.
Began awkwardly, then ridden along in one-off position behind midfield. Switched out in straight but found nothing and faded.
Pressed forward but caught three-wide without cover behind leading pair. Covered extra ground turn and faded quickly in straight.
Never far off in 5th, 3Ls off the pace making the turn for home, made good progress along inside, switched 150M out and finished off strongly to lead from 100M, ridden out.
Settled 3-wide in mid-division on jumping from draw 12, made good progress to lead briefly inside 150M, couldn't match winner's finishing pace final stages.
Restrained to sit just off leader, pushed along to challenge 450M, ran on steadily for 3rrd, not matched winner's pace final 150M.
Began only fairly, proved difficult to settle, in rear 8Ls off the pace home turn, brought wide and closed off strongly final 300M to just miss 3rd.
Held up along fence in mid-division, looked one pace early straight but did best work over final 200M, encouraging debut.
Chased leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, kept on steadily turning in but gradually outpaced by leaders over final 200M.
Dropped back to the rear from wide barrier, 6Ls behind leader 400M, ran on moderately without threatening first two.
Slow to begin, near last 6Ls off the pace, ran on mildly inside 400M but never seriously threatened.
Slow to begin, held up 3-wide behind midfield, showed signs of greenness in the race, brief effort early straight, couldn't sustain run final 150M.
In mid-division, got its head up passing 1000M and proved difficult to settle, stayed on same pace on straightening, never threatened.
Urged to take the lead, took them along slowly middle stages, had 2Ls advantage early straight, weakened 200M, soon headed and no extra late stages.
Tracked leaders along the inside, soon weakened turning home and out of contention.
Pressed forward from wide draw, settling a half length outside leader. Kicked ahead on straightening, held off late challenge while laying out against the whip.
Crowded out and bumped start, not pushed, settling 3-wide behind midfield. Urged forward 600m, finished strongly down centre track.
Crowded start, ridden to go forward but not enough speed, settling four-back along rail. Got clear run in straight and finished off strongly.
Jumped well, ridden to hold forward position, settling one-off but 2L from leading pair. Chased leader throughout without closing gap.
No early speed and soon at rear of main bunch in one-off position. Switched out in straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, urged forward to find cover in midfield, then travelled keenly middle stages. Got clear run in straight and ran on steadily.
Blew the start, became intractable and unbalanced jockey, losing ground. Trailed field to turn, turned wide, finished off nicely.
Ridden to hold rail, three-back from leader. Left fence turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Inconvenienced start, no speed, dropping to rear along fence. Switched out in straight to make challenge but found nothing.
Pressed forward from outside draw to lead on settling. Joined up front 600m, headed turning for home and weakened.
Bumped and unbalanced start, pushed forward to grab box seat before turn. Spent force on straightening and faded.
Ridden along one-off but 4L from leader. Kept position around turn but gave ground quickly in straight.

Pushed forward from the wide barrier to be handily placed in 5th, 3wd no cover before forcing cover at 1000m. Came wider on the turn and ran on, taking the lead at 200. Chopped down late, but had just enough to hold the win.

OK away and eased forward early to settle midfield, on the fence. Sat back and smoked the pipe until the turn, but was boxed in looking for a run. Got clear at 200m, producing a huge run to the line and just missing late.

OK away and elected to sit just worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Near last on the turn, but pushed forward when clear from 350m. Closed off impressively with the fastest last sectional of the race.

Began well and pushed forward early to be handily placed in 3rd, 1 off the fence and 2L off the leaders. Loomed at the top of the straight and led briefly until 200m, before peaking and dropping back late.
Tried to find a position in midfield early, but stuck wide and on heels before getting in 1 off the fence at 1000m. Well placed and a clear run from the turn, but only ran on fairly in the straight.
Began OK, but only eased forward early to be placed towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Came widest on the turn and went well to the line for a promising Hong Kong debut.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to be in the last pair, 10L off the leaders. Ran on OK late from a rear position, easing up late when out of contention.

Dropped back from the wide barrier early to sit last, 11L off the leaders at the 800m. Made up ground from that point, and ran to the line OK in the straight to finish near the first half of the field.
Began well and pushed forward early to share the lead, on the fence. Led at 350m, but began to fade soon after and dropped back. Eased to the line late.
Jumped well and allowed to roll forward early to be handily placed early. Restrained back at 1300m to sit midfield, 1 off the pace and over racing. Didn't finish off late.

OK away and taken forward to be handily placed in 4th on the rail, 2.5L off the early leaders. Positioned OK on the turn, but didn't respond to hands and heels riding in the straight and never ran on.
Only fairly away and dropped back early to sit near the rear of the field, on the fence. Never kicked, and drifted out under the whip when asked for anything in the straight.
Began awkwardly, and never fully settled early when finding a position near midfield, on the rail. Asked the question in the straight, but never responded and eased to the line late.

Pushed forward through runners early to share the lead, 1 off the fence. Dropped out quickly from the 400m, and never ridden out in the straight to be almost 3L behind the 2nd last runner across the line.
Close up chased leaders along the 2-path, took keen hold 1200M, picked up strongly 350M, led 200M and sped off to a clear lead, held firm final stages.
Held up 3-wide in mid-division, driven out 350M, closed off soundly to go 2nd near line but well held by winner.
Settled down in midfield 3-4Ls behind the pace, driven along 400M to chase leaders, got up for 2nd 100M, kept on but not reaching winner, beaten to 3rd near line.
Held up 3-4Ls off the pace in midfield and kept to the inside throughout, not clear run 200M, kept on mildly when every chance final 150M.
Dropped back to a 2-wide spot towards the rear, closed off moderately but couldn't quite get to leaders.
Restrained to near the rear, 7Ls behind leader, swung 3-wide home turn, closed off well early straight but run ended 150M.
Soon led, took them along slowly middle stages, driven out near 300M, headed 200M then gave way. (No Vet findings.)
Never better than midfield, raced 3-wide throughout, couldn't sprint with the main rivals inside 400M, plodded home.
Chased leaders along the 3-path with no cover, fought on to 250M, weakened.
Strolled forward chasing leader, remained a presence until weakening nearing 200M. (No Vet findings.)
Switched off to last 9Ls behind leader, waited with till 450M but gave only limited response, never threatened.
Began awkwardly, recovered to a position behind midfield, not picked up on straightening, never reached contention.
Restless in stalls, raced further back than intended, 2nd last turning and had 7Ls to make up, found disappointingly little. (No Vet findings / Unacceptable Performance.)
Shake up early to obtain a forward spot just off leader, outpaced 400M, soon beaten.

Well there on stands rails, hit the front under pressure passing the 200 metres.
Jumped well, settled not far off the pace, steadied for a stride 300 metres out, fought on well to miss narrowly.
Settled near midfield but not far off the pace, commenced move inside final 300 metres, fought on steadily without threatening.
Slightly slow to jump, settled in last few, produced good late impression along stands rails inside final 200 metres.
Always thereabouts, failed to quicken under pressure to challenge inside final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to last few, awkwardly placed behind runners 600 metres out, produced good late impression past beaten runners in the run home.
Soon took up running, led until finding no extra over 200 metres out.
Settled near midfield from the one draw, produced short-lived effort to hold minor chance near the centre of the track over 200 metres out, no further impression.
Broke well, lost touch after first 200 metres, dropped further back coming onto course proper, produced some late impression closing stages.
Handy early, folded up quickly inside final 300 metres.
Jumped well, settled just off the pace, came under pressure coming onto course proper, dropped out tamely.
Soon dropped to last few, forced to check about 600 metres out, never a danger.
Amongst leaders early racing near the centre of the track, dropped away quickly from the 400 metres.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 400, ran on strongly 250M to score.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Eased back, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 4-2, closed off strongly when clear.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Settled in box seat, pace good, lack room 400M, just held ground when clear.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on until 100M flattened.
Eased back, trapped 4 wide, pace good, made some ground in straight.
In front of midfield, pace good, trapped 3 wide, flattened 200M.
Eased to sit behind midfield along the rails, pace good, no turn of foot in straight, on heels 250M.
Eased back, 3-4 wide, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good sectionals, reduced quickly 200M.
At rear along the fence, pace good, never improved.
Raced very wide, never competitive at rear.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow tempo, ran on well to score by a head.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow pace, stormed home for 2nd, missed by a head.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow sectionals, finished off nicely for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on gradually for 4th.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the slow pace, one paced without any serious threats.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace without threatening.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, however weakened final 150M.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow sectionals, made minor ground in straight.
Eased back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, never ran on.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Taken back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, never ran on.
Prominent, however inclined to lay out throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Always at rear, hung out badly rounding the Home Turn, finished tailed out.
Taken back at start, settled near rear 1 off outside fence, advanced a spot 600m, strong traveler & held up until shifted inside & shaken up 50m, surged centre to lead 80m, driven clear.
Broke well, tracked lead in 4th, niggled 480m, switched inside & ridden to challenge 350m, quickened to lead 120m, no extra & headed 80m.
Speedy start, sat close 2nd inside leader, ridden 400m & took narrow lead 280m, all out & headed 120m, boxed on to wire.
Fast break & sat handy 3rd without cover, driven 400m, out-paced but kept on.
Broke ok, raced handily 1 off outside fence, travelled well & shaken up 300m, lacked kick & tapered late.
Tardy break, taken to rail & soon 2.5L adrift at tail, niggled to chase 400m, shifted centre & stayed on for late inroads.
Tardy start & bustled along on rail near rear, edged out & ridden 300m, close to heels & checked to rail 180m, stayed on for minor late headway.
Broke ok but soon bustled & outpaced behind midfield, under pump 500m, plugged on same speed, never a factor.
Fast start to lead, soon to rail, ridden 400m & drifted off fence, emptied & headed 280m, faded tamely.
Smart start, raced midfield in touch, ridden 500m, found nil & weakened tamely.
Broke well, sat rail fore of midfield, shifted out & ridden 420m, quickened to lead 140m, edged ahead.
Fast start wide, slotted 1 off 1 back 4th, shifted out turning in, ridden 400m, driven to lead 220m, fully extended & headed 140m, boxed on in defeat.
Broke ok, raced midfield on inner, edged out 450m, driven 400m, ran on centre track, just missed 2nd.
Broke well, taken back from wide to slot 1 off near rear, edged 3 deep 750m, fanned wide final turn, driven & ran on strongly, just missed frame.
Tardy start, niggled along on rail near rear, driven 400m, edged out in run, kept on for minor headway.
Tardy break, pushed forward, sat 1 back on rails, shifted out 400m & quickened between horses to lead 300m, all out when headed 220m & faded.
Missed break & bustled, raced 2nd last 1 off, edged 3 deep 750m, driven widest final turn, ran on centre track for solid headway.
Fair start, sat back of midfield on inner, off heels 750m & shuffled back a spot, shifted to 1 off, checked 400m, driven 300m, plugged on evenly.
Taken back from widest to race tail on rail, shaken up 430m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Bustled to lead on rail, joined at fore turning in, ridden & all out when headed 300m, tapered to wire.
Broke ok, snagged to race back of midfield 1 off with cover, advanced a spot 1000m, over-raced 800m, shifted wide & driven home turn, outpaced & faded.
Sluggish break, pushed forward to fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out & ridden final turn, one-paced, checked off heels 250m, tapered tamely.
Fast start & rousted to dispute early lead, settled 0.75L 2nd outside leader, niggled 700m, ridden to share lead turning in, emptied & headed 300m, weakened.
Urged forward to take the rail and led at slow sectionals, unleashed once straightened, held off late challenge to score by a nose.
Sat in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, took advantage of the slow pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Travelled in front of midfield along the rail, 3L off the pace, niggled when rounding turn, finished off nicely for 3rd.
Settled in worse than midfield, 7-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow tempo, dashed strongly and made vast ground in the straight.
Raced in midfield, 4-1/4L off 3 wide without cover, no dash and ran home one paced.
At the rear, 9-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow pace, made ground steadily in the straight.
Raced outside the leader, 1-1/4L off the pace, little dash at 300M, out of steam passing 200M.
Settled in worse than midfield along the rail, 6-1/4L behind the leader, not suited to the slow tempo, made slight ground only.
Raced in worse than midfield, 6L off the pace 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, only improved slightly in the straight.
Travelled in midfield along the rail, 4-1/2L off the pace, made no impression in the straight.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat, 1-1/2L behind, despite suited to the slow tempo, flattened after 250M.
In midfield, 4-1/2L off the pace 2 wide with cover, not competitive and dropped off significantly after 200M.
Always at the rear, was never competitive.
At back throughout, never a factor.
Began well, pressed forward settling one-back, one-off 950m. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 290m, hung in 200m and again 150m, kept on well.
Began fairly, ridden forward, settling two-back, one-off. Switched out entering straight and ran on strongly under whip.
Began best, led to 950m before taking sit. Angled out 400m, hit front 290m, tightened 200m, checked and unbalanced 150m, boxed on.
Jumped well, ridden to hold rail 2-back from leader. Switched out in straight to make run and kept on steadily.
Steadied shortly after start and taken in but held 3-wide at rear before turn. Taken wider 400m and ran on steadily while hanging in under whip.
Taken in shortly after start settling between horses at the rear. Got close to heels 500m, switched out straight, ran on fairly.
Began fairly, taken to fence 3-back from leader. Shaken up 400m, raced tight 350, switched out 300, kept on fairly till checked 75m.
Taken in shorty after start, settling along fence at rear. Improved position around turn but one-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position but kept wide without cover from 900. Covered extra ground throughout, one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, outpaced, dropping behind midfield. Hard ridden top of straight but little progress before tightened passing 200m.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead passing 950m before crossing to fence. Overtaken shortly after straightening and faded.
Had feet off ground when gates opened and began fairly. Pressed forward but wide, settling outside leader 900m. Faded steadily in straight.
From draw 1 got into a trailing position behind leaders, briefly held up top of the straight, closed off well to lead near 200M, kept responding when pressed by rivals both side final stages.
Switched off to the rear 7Ls off the pace, waited with until reaching top of straight, angled out to clear 400M, pressed winner final 150M but was held.
Never far off 3Ls off the pace, no clear run 300M- 200M before going through narrow gap to challenge, well held by winner final 100M.
Dropped back to rear 7-8Ls off the pace, driven out 450M, checked 250M when commencing his run, regrouped and stayed on final 200M to go 4th near line.
Held up in midfield 4-5Ls off the pace first half, in touch home turn, wide bid 550M, ran on moderately, one paced 150M and no impression on leaders thereafter.
Positively ridden, prompted the pace 2-wide, kicked on 550M, lost lead inside 300M, fought on same pace to line.
Near the rear early stages, moved closer to a midfield position middle stages, driven wide 500M, stayed on well early straight but run peaked 200M, no threat 150M.
Contested the early pace, crossed to the lead 1500M and remained prominent to home straight, fought on early straight but no extra passing 200M.
Lost ground when jumping in the air at start, ridden forward from rear but soon left with no cover, joined leaders from 1200M, faded away 250M when hard run took toll (Mucus.)
Slow to begin, held up near the rear 6-7Ls behind leaders, kept to inside throughout but not picked up turning in, never threatened.
Contested early lead, taken across for cover behind leaders, proved difficult to settle 1400M then moved out to 3-wide position, not quickened in straight, got tired 200M.
4-5Ls off the pace, never better than midfield, not travelled and had to be niggled along approaching home turn, had nothing to offer in straight and was left behind 200M. (no Vet findings.)
Chased the pace, travelled keenly, failed to pick up passing 400M, eased mid-straight. (No Vet findings.)
Bumped, unbalanced soon after starts, pressed forward along rail 2-back from leader. Took rails run entering straight, hit front 200m, battled strongly, just held.
Began well, ridden forward, settling two-back, one-off. Urged forward entering straight, finished strongly down centre track to just miss.
Quickly away, grabbing box seat and trailing leader to straight. Switched out 400m, tightened 300m, finished strongly.
Crowded start, taken to fence, 3-back from leader. Left fence around turn, ran on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Taken out shortly after start, steadied 1500m, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Taken wide in straight and finished off nicely.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across to rail but towards rear. Stayed on rail throughout, ran on steadily in straight.
Quickly into stride, taking clear lead on settling and slowing pace. Kicked ahead top of straight but collared 200m and weakened.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Trailed field to 200m before making up some late ground.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, settling one-back, one-off. Urged forward top of straight, looked chance 200m, flattened 100m.
Ridden along early but wide, before easing behind midfield in one-off position. One-paced in straight.
Knuckled over at start, pressed forward, settling1L behind leader. Crept closer around turn, gave ground quickly in straight. Substantial amount of mucus in trachea.
Began OK, but not used early and happy to sit midfield, on the rail. Had to force a run just before the 300m, but ran on strongly from there. Slowing down late, but had to much in hand and held.

Eased out of the barrier and dropped back to sit towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Near last on the turn, but ran home strongly in the straight, clocking the fastest last sectional, but left with too much to do.
OK away and not used up early to settle just behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran home strongly in the straight, rolling past 4th horse but just losing 2nd on the line.

Pushed forward from the wide barrier early to eventually settle in 2nd, outside the leader. Tackled the leader from the top of the straight and led from 300m. Weakened from 150m, and dropped out from 50m losing a place late.
Fairly away and not used up early to settle 3rd last early, on the rail and 7L off the leader. Held up in the run home until 300m, running on OK when clear.
Bumped on jumping and taken back from the wide barrier to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Ran on steadily in the straight, without ever threatening to place.

Kicked well, and pushed to hold the lead on his own early. Bumped and slightly unbalanced at the top of the straight. Still in front at 300m, but tackled by the chasers, and faded out quickly from there.
OK away and settled midfield early, on the rail. Battled on fairly in the straight, but never kicked and went to the line 1 paced.

Dawdled out of the barrier and settled at the rear of the field, 9L off the leader. In the last couple on the turn. Ran on fairly in the straight and picked up a couple of slower runners on the way to the line.
Settled midfield, 1 off the fence after beginning OK. Plugged away 1 paced in the straight.
Jumped well and taken forward to be handily placed 4th, 2L off the leader and 1 off the fence. Lay out under pressure in the straight, and never fully tested.
Taken forward from the wide draw to sit midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Well positioned with clear running on the turn, but ran flat and dropped back through the field quickly in the straight.
Began well and taken forward early to be handily placed 3rd, on the rail. Never responded to pressure in the straight, and eased a long way out. Vet reported blood in trachea.
Began OK, but didn't push forward and settled worse than midfield, 3 wide. Race was run before the turn, and faded quickly in the straight to be tailed out 26L last. Unacceptable performance.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back in midfield, same position on turn, in traffic early in straight, found daylight near final 200M and finished off very strongly thereafter to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5 lengths back at rear, 3 wide with cover on turn, finished off very well, just beaten by the winner late.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, angled out after turning in, finished off well to get 3rd without threatening the first two.
Crowded out start, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail at rear, there to turn, no clear running until final 200M, made some progress thereafter to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in 4th, still no cover on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well until headed final 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear to turn, made minor progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 to 3 lengths back on rail, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M.
Began awkwardly, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight when hard run took effect.
Away with them, travelled keenly in the early stages, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back in 5th, similar position on turn, unable to get clear running in straight, not tested. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, showed early speed to race prominently, a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter and eased final 100M.

Jumped well, settled in midfield one off the rails, commenced run 3-wide rounding home bend, asserted authority passing the 200 metres.

Broke well from the middle gate, settled 3L back in 5th travelling 3-wide down far side, took closer order from the Rock, improved under pressure from 1L 3rd into straight to hold minor chance briefly but winner too strong.
Tailed-off early, joined back-markers rounding home bend, hampered by faller entering straight, made steady headway near the centre of the track without threatening.
Taken back to settle behind midfield, 3-wide rounding home bend and into straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Not far off, improved to dispute lead rounding home bend, failed to hold place under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Settled behind midfield on rails, hampered by faller entering straight, kept on steadily to finish.
Ridden to soon take up running, joined in front when pace slackened rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 200 metres.
Settled in last few from the widest gate, slightly affected by the fall entering straight, made no impression thereafter.
Settled 2 back in 4th, gained slightly closer near the Rock, badly hampered by faller on home turn, never recovered. (Lame next day)
Slightly slow out, given reminders before settling in midfield on rails, badly hampered by faller entering straight, never recovered. (Lame)

Placing: UR
Comment: Jumped well from the middle gate, soon obtained one-back position on rails, apparently stumbled and dislodged rider entering straight.
Pressed forward, secured a prominent spot 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, pace good, ran on strongly to the line for 2nd.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
On heels early, midfield, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed to taka rail and led at good pace, hung on until 200M flattened.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased to rear, pace good, made some ground 200M.
On heels early, pushed forward, box seat, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, on heels early, emptied 300M.
Eased back, raced 2-4 wide, never competitive.
Trapped 3 wide throughout, never a factor, tailed out.
Eased back, raced keenly, checked 400M, tailed out.
Taken back to settle worse than midfield, 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, stormed home for a stylish win.
Prominent, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the fast tempo, kept on strongly until over the final few strides headed by the impressive winner.
Eased to settle worse than midfield from a wide barrier, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Taken back as usual, travelled 11Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on without any real threats.
Rolled forward to settle outside the leader at fast tempo, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Rolled forward to settle midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast pace, one paced home.
At rear, travelled 12Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made some ground in straight.
Jumped slowly, then niggled along to settle in midfield, 6Ls behind the leader along the fence, never ran on.
Always at back, despite the fast pace, never looked likely.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led at fast sectionals, flattened badly final 200M. (Bled)
Punched forward along the fence, however, weakened rapidly rounding the Home Turn.
Broke well, taken to rail back midfield, shifted 1 off & niggled 500m, driven into stretch & fanned centre track, quickened 200m, sprinted to lead 80m, in command.
Speed to lead 1500m, bustled to rail 1250m & set tempo, shaken up 400m, pressed 150m, battled on, headed 50m, no extra.
Taken back at start to last, closed a spot & last pair 1 off 750m when over-raced, driven widest final turn, rattled home to make frame.
Taken back at start to 1 off near rear, edged 3 wide with cover 900m, bustled to midfield 650m, ridden 500m, very wide final turn, stayed on for minor inroads.
Led at start, headed 1500m & settled 1 back on rail, driven 400m & shifted out, quickened to press lead 150m, held & peaked 100m, faded to wire.
Early speed, posted handy 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, edged out & driven 300m, flat-footed but boxed on & rallied late.
Snagged from wide gate to race last near tail on rail, last pair 750m, driven into stretch, ran on for minor headway.
Rolled from widest to sit 1 off with cover behind midfield, over-raced 950m, off heels 750m, not clear run turning in, switched inside & driven, stayed on for late gains.
Smart break, restrained to midfield 3 wide no cover, rolled forward 700m, driven 4 wide into stretch, one-paced in tepid run home.
Broke well, restrained to race midfield 1 off with cover, over-raced 730m, shifted wide on tune, found nil & plodded home.
Broke well, parked 2nd 1 off no cover, niggled 600m, under pump 450m, soon beaten & faded in stretch.
Sluggish start, rousted forward to rail fore of midfield, niggled 400m, under pump turning in, found nil in weakening run.
Speed to lead, to rail & restrained 1070m, sat 1 back, closed on leader & switched out 260m, driven to lead 100m, edged away.
Bustled wide to lead 1070m, soon to rail, slowed pace & headed 600m, led again 420m, shaken up 300m & kicked 1L clear, all out & headed 100m, no extra.
Shifted left at break & heavily impeded rival, recovered to race rail toward rear, niggled 500m, driven 400m, boxed on to 3rd 100m, gradual closer.
Fast break, settled rail midfield, over-raced 700m, shuffled back a spot & niggled 620m, bustled for progress 500m, edged 1 off & ridden final turn, ran on centre track.
Fast start, bustled up to 2nd 1 off no cover, shuffled to 3rd 1 back 600m, soon niggled, 3 wide & driven turning in, plugged on one pace.
Broke with others, sat rail behind midfield, shifted 1 off & over-raced 820m, shifted out turning in & driven, stayed on moderately.
Broke with others, lacked toe & settled near rear 1 off, shifted 3 deep with cover 820m & advanced to midfield, shaken up 300m, plodded on tamely.
Slow start & bumped, raced last pair 1 off, 8L back & under pump 550m, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Broke ok, over-raced initially, parked midfield 1 off with cover, every chance when shifted wide home turn & driven, struggled in run home.
Broke ok, rousted initially, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, over-raced 820m, ridden 450m, wide & unbalanced on turn, found nil.
Broke well, raced 4th 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep no cover 850m & advanced, narrow lead 600m & posted 1 off, headed 420m, driven but emptied quickly & faded.
Tardy start & impeded heavily, raced last on rail, over-raced 750m, checked off heels & lost ground, 8.5L back & niggled 500m, driven into stretch, found nil.
Travelled in midfield along the rail, 5-1/2L behind the leader, once straightened unleashed strongly to score by a nose.
Sat just in front of midfield, 3-3/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, ridden just after 500M, ran on well for 2nd.
At the rear along the rail, 9-1/2L behind, not suited to the slow tempo, finished off nicely despite held up until 200M.
Raced towards the rear, 7-1/2L off the pace 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on gradually for 4th.
Prominent, sat outside the leader, suited to the slow pace, run ended when weakened passing 200M.
Travelled towards the rear along the rail, 7L behind the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, made ground steadily in the Straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, 6-1/2L off the pace 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, finished off only one paced.
Travelled in box-seat, 2-3/4L behind the leader, suited to the slow tempo, weakened soon after 250M.
Prominent, 2-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited to the slow pace, did not run on.
Rolled forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L, despite suited to the slow pace, weakened and headed after 200M.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
In midfield, 5L off 2 wide with cover, hung out when rounding turn, run ended thereafter.
Pushed forward but wide before settling half a length outside leader 1200m. Kicked ahead 250m, joined up front 200m, kept battling to line.
Ridden along to stay with leading pack but kept 3-wide mostly without cover. Kept on solidly in straight only to fail narrowly.
Allowed to settle early, holding rail 2-back from leading pair. Closed in slightly around turn, switch out in straight, finished well.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling in one-of position 3L from leader. Switched wide in straight and finished well down centre track to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward to lead passing 1450m, cutting to fence 1200m. Collared soon after straightening but battled on gamely.
Crowded out start, taken to rail, settling 3-back from leader. Taken out turning for home, ran on steadily in straight.
Restrained and shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Trailed field to straight before running on fairly.
First out, holding inside rail till 1450m, slipping into box seat 1200m. Kept on gamely before fading final stages. Has substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Ridden along but unable find cover and kept 3-wide towards rear. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Steadied and shifted in behind horses from wide draw to get to rail at the rear. Last passing 200m before running past beaten horses.
Began well, pressed forward but raced keenly in midfield and forced to race wide. Kept on fairly early in straight but tired rapidly final 200m.
Began fairly, then ridden along in one-of position behind midfield. Under pressure turning for home and finished tailed off.
Reserved in mid-division, 4Ls off leader 400M, closed off strongly to lead 50M, steadily pulled away.
In close attendance to the pace, driven out to a narrow lead near 100M, continued with a steady bid but couldn't contain the winner close home.
Urged to lead from the break, set even pace, kept on soundly leaving the turn, headed near 100M, pleasing debut.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, settled down 3-wide and 5Ls back near the rear, stayed on well down outside, just missed 3rd.
Not hurried early stages, settled near the rear 4-5Ls off the pace but travelled keenly middle stages, made some mild progress over final 250M.
Steadied in early stages to obtain cover, held up near the rear 5Ls behind leaders, did best work late when switching out 200M, late impression.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, raced as the back marker 6Ls behind leader, made steady progress along the fence final 300M.
Broke sharply, tracked leader along the 2-path, continued in that position racing into straight but couldn't produce the needed closing response, swamped late stages.
In mid-division 2-wide, kept on same pace turning home and never mounted a serious challenge. (Lame RF)
3Ls off the pace along inside, never better than midfield, gradually retreated from 250M.
Never far off the pace but caught wide no cover passing 1000M, beaten early straight, eased mid-straight. (Mucus)
Fanned wide first turn, restrained to find cover in midfield along the 3-path, never gained contention leaving the turn.
First out, steadied, taking sit behind leading pair in one-off position. Shaken up top of straight, hit front 50m, held off challenge.
Bumped shortly after start, ridden along in one-off position 4L from leader. Taken wide in straight and ran on strongly to miss narrowly.
Began well, pressed forward to lead on settling, then steadied and passed 900m. Retook lead 680m, kept on strongly until swamped final 50m.
Bumped, unbalanced shortly after start, pressed forward taking box seat before turn. Held for run early in straight, finished off nicely.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw but kept away from fence. Raced keenly around turn, wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Bumped shortly after start, pressed forward to lead 800m, then eased, sitting outside leader around turn. Kept on well till flattened 100m.
Jumped well, ridden along in midfield in one-off position. Switched out in straight but only one-paced.
Bumped shortly after start, taken to fence but at rear. Stayed along fence around turn and kept on fairly in straight.
Began well, pressed forward but wide and left without cover from 800m. Rolled forward turn to look chance 300m before tiring.
Hard ridden to hold rail in midfield, two-back from leader. Stayed on rail in straight but only one-paced.
Began fairly, bumped shortly after, steadied, dropping to last in one-off position. Switched out in straight but found nothing under pressure.
Bumped shortly after start, steadied, taken to rail at the rear. Hampered turning for home, plodded in straight.

Jumped fairly, settled just off the leader on rails, came to challenge upon straightening and hit the front over 200 metres out, just held on to the line.
Taken back to race in last few, switched off rails for a run entering straight, ran on well inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Settled one-out-one-back, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening the length of straight.
Met minor interference early settling well behind, made good progress down the centre of home straight, did best work late.
Settled towards the ear, baulked for a run to the 200 metres, finished off race well.
Closer up early before drifting back to forward of midfield in 6th on rails, came under pressure entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well from a wide draw, gradually shifted across to travel in 2nd just outside the leader, hit the front briefly inside the 300 metres, soon faded.
Began from the widest gate, settled in 5th within 3L of pace travelling wide without cover, ran home one-paced.
Trailed the field most of way, ran on well past beaten horses inside final 150 metres.
Settled in midfield 3-wide, went wider entering straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Jumped awkwardly, in rear early, gradually improved on rails to rear of midfield, baulked for a run until the 300 metres, plugged on under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly, soon recovered to rear of midfield, baulked briefly around the bend, forced to switch inside for a run at the 400 metres, kept on well to the line. (Mucus in trachea)
Soon took up running, led the field to the 300 metres, folded up quickly.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, found nothing in the run home. (Bled)
Settled just off the pace group, drifted away 250M to score, not fully tested.
Settled in front, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Bumped start, at rear, raced on inner part of track, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, held ground in final stages.
Bumped start, midfield, raced on the inner part of track, ran on ok.
At rear, benefited by the fast pace, raced flat until 150M made good ground.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Bumped start, at back, raced on the inner part of track, lack room 400M, ran on fairly.
At back, raced on the inner part of track, never progressed.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast pace, raced on the inner part of track, out of fuel 350M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast sectionals, raced on the inner part of track, emptied 400M.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, faded 300M.
Pressed forward, not suited by the fast pace, raced close to the inner part of track, dropped off rapidly 250M.
Jumped slowly, then stride forward gradually to park outside the leader at very slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score by 2Ls.
Hard ridden forward to obtain the box seat, enjoyed the very slow tempo, ran on gradually for 2nd.
Camped handy, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the very slow sectionals, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung wide turning in, despite the very slow tempo, made some steady ground in straight.
Taken back to rear, travelled 11Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung widest turning in, harmed by the very slow pace, ran on nicely.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the very slow pace, one paced home.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the very slow pace, unable to show any dash in straight.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the very slow sectionals, kept on until 200M flattened.
Blundered badly soon after jumping, travelled 10Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the very slow pace, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the very slow pace, never ran on and weakened 100M.
Always at rear, harmed by the very slow sectionals, never ran on.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at very slow tempo, kept on until weakened 300M.
Settled worse than midfield throughout, hampered by the very slow tempo, unable to run on.
Settled worse than midfield about 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the very slow tempo, never ran on. (substantial amount of mucus in its trachea)
Broke ok, taken back to midfield 1 off with cover, switched wide home turn, shaken up 400m, quickened to 2nd 250m, powered to lead 150m, drew clear.
Smart start, niggled to race rail fore of midfield, edged 1 off 500m, not clear run into stretch, shaken up & switched to rail 250m, ran on late to 2nd.
Taken back at break, raced rail in rear, edged out final turn but not clear run in stretch, switched off heels 250m & driven, closed off late to 3rd.
Fast break wide, crossed to take narrow lead 1 off, edged 1L clear & to rail 1100m, 2L clear & shaken up 350m, all out & headed 150m, weakened to wire.
Tardy break, raced rail behind midfield, shifted out 500m, ridden 400m, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke OK, snagged to midfield, trapped 3 wide no cover, rolled forward to sit outside leader 900m, niggled 650m & soon under pump, found little in stretch, faded.
Restrained at start, caught 3 deep & taken back to near rear, advanced a spot 600m, wide into stretch & driven 400m, boxed on one pace.
Started ok, rousted initially, sat handy 1 off no cover, gained cover 900m, switched out 3 deep 550m, ridden 430m, found little, tapered & swamped at 200m.
Broke well, snagged to settle fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted wide final turn & driven, one-paced & tapered final 200m.
Fast start, rousted to sit close 2nd on rail, restrained to 1 back on fence 1100m, niggled a touch 550m, switched out & driven 450m, found little & weakened out.
Slow start, sat 1 off with cover near tail, shifted 3 deep 550m, driven turning in, plugging on tepidly when impeded 200m, no extra.
Moderate start, niggled to race behind midfield 1 off with cover, under pressure & backpedalled 600m, last turning in, plodded on evenly.
Sluggish start & bustled initially, raced 3 deep in last place, 4 deep 550m, widest into stretch & driven, plodded on tamely.
Moderate start, parked midfield on rail, shifted out entering home stretch, crowded 400m, driven 300m, one-paced & eased when beaten.
Smart break but lacked toe & bustled a touch to race rail midfield, closed to 1 back turning in, checked out of pocket 350m & driven, quickened to lead 140m, drew clear.
Good break, raced close 2nd 1 off with cover, niggled on turn, shaken up 350m, battled to nick 2nd at wire.
Started well, tracked 1 back 1 off, shifted 3 deep 450m, cruised to lead 300m, driven 250m, found little extra & headed 140m, out-battled in duel for 2nd.
Slow start, raced rail behind midfield, progress on turn, driven 300m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Taken back at start to tail, progress on turn & edged out turning in, shaken up 300m, closed centre track for minor late headway.
Fast start wide & bustled to lead, steadied & headed 880m, trapped 3 deep & drifted back on turn, midfield & driven 600m, boxed on evenly in stretch.
Broke with others, rousted a touch & raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, over-raced & bumped 700m, shuffled back to rear rank, driven wide into stretch, boxed on one pace.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven on turn & shifted out, one-paced & tapered final 150m.
Moderate start & bustled, rough passage wide with cover back of midfield, bumped 700m, vey wide final turn, driven 300m, plugged on tamely.
Sharp start, bustled on rail to narrow lead 880m, driven 400m, all out & headed 300m, folded & faded.
Fast start, prominent initially, soon bustled & sat handy 3 wide with cover, over-raced 750m, bumped 700, shuffled back & bumped 500m, weakened tamely.
Broke with others, rousted & outpaced, trapped wide no cover midfield, tough passage & shuffled back on turn, very wide into stretch, driven 400m, found nil, eased when beaten.
In worse than midfield, 8L behind along the rail, unleashed strong finishing effort once straightened, scored easily by 3-1/2L.
Prominent, 2L off the pace 2 wide with cover, dashed well after passing 200M, ran on well for 2nd.
Rolled forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, kept on well until headed by the eventual winner at 150M, held on for 3rd.
Ridden forward, sat outside the leader 1/2L behind, little dash at 300M, one paced home thereafter.
Travelled in front of midfield along the rail, 3-3/4L behind the leader, no dash in the Straight.
Settled in midfield, 6L off the pace along the rail, taken widest after turn, finished off only one paced.
In worse than midfield, 6-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, not competitive in the Straight.
In front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, no dash and weakened after 150M.
At the rear, 10-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, only improved slightly in the Straight.
Sat towards the rear along the rail, 9-3/4L behind the leader, made no more than minor ground.
Towards the rear, 9-1/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, made no impression in the Straight.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat, 2L behind the leader, run ended when couldn't find extra passing 250M.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
In midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, swung widest after turn, did not run on.
Hard ridden from outside draw to lead 950m but wide. Narrowly headed by inside horse 700m, retook lead 400m, kicked ahead 300m, held off challengers.
Began awkwardly, pushed forward along rail 2-back from leader. Ran on strongly from 300m but run ended close to line.
Began fairly, pressed forward, settling 3-back passing 800m. Improved around turn, took rails run and loomed inside leader 200m, no extra final stages.
Began fairly, steadied, dropping to rear along fence, Made up ground around turn, held for run in straight until 300m, finished strongly.
Jumped well, settling midfield in one-off position. Checked 700m when racing keenly, ran on fairly before struggling final 200m Wounded left front leg.
No early speed, racing at rear but wide. Taken wider in straight, boxed on fairly. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Ridden to hold midfield position but wide, hard to settle and checked 800m. Swung wider into straight but only plodded home. Superficial wound right front leg.
Outpaced and distant last until straight when ran on fairly past tired horses.
Quickly into stride, pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide. Lost position around turn, weakened gradually in straight.
No early speed, taken to rail and last of main bunch entering turn. Never competitive.
Knuckled over start, pressed forward but wide 2L behind leader. Boxed on early in straight before tiring. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea,
Jumped well, hard ridden along rail inside leader. Led marginally from 700m to 400m, before giving ground in straight. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.

Began awkwardly, settled down towards the rear along stands' rail, cruised into contention from 350M, held up near 250M but quickened smartly once in the clear, drew away at the line winning debut impressively.
Tracked leaders, loomed a strong chance 300M when guided to challenge, led near 200M but had no answer to winner's finishing kick final stages.
Restrained in mid-pack, travelled well to 400M, waited with till 250M, ran on steadily to the line.
Within 2Ls of leaders towards stands' side, kept up with the chase on leaders final 400M but always held.
Vied for lead towards the stands' rail, remained a presence to 200M, headed and faltered late stages.
Prompted the pace, always in firing line but couldn't quicken with main rivals inside 400M, soon out of contention.
Held up in mid-division 3Ls off the pace, lacked acceleration passing 400M, did not factor.
Urged to go forward vying for the lead, gradually outpaced from 300M and dropped out of contention.
Chased leaders towards the outside of group, kept on same speed when driven out 400M, soon outpaced by main rivals.
Up with pace off stands' rail, pushed along to hold his position passing 500M, gave way 300M. (Lame next day.)
Lost ground at the start, brought across towards stands' rail, detached from the field halfway, made up some ground late but never reached contention.
In mid-division towards the outside of the group, not quickened when driven along halfway, never involved.
In midfield 4Ls off leaders, struggled to keep up 500M, never a factor.
Pushed along early stages but failed to muster, detached from field 600M, soundly beaten. (Jockey : horse did not travel well at any stage / No Vet findings)
Began fairly, then squeezed out, settling on rail 5L from leader. Badly held for clear run early in straight, got inside run 200m, finished strongly.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Under pressure early before kicking clear before turn. Kept on strongly in straight but run down final strides.
Began well, ridden forward, settling 2-back from leader. Took inside run in straight, a little tight for room 200m, kept on well.
No early speed, then difficult to settle, checked 1300m, dropping to rear. Taken wide in straight, finished strongly while laying in 300m under pressure.
Crowded out start, ridden forward, settling midfield but wide. Lost position turning for home, wide in straight, finished off nicely.
Allowed to settle racing behind midfield in one-off position. Not asked for an effort until 400m when switched out and ran on steadily.
Not pushed settling at rear. Rolled forward but wide entering turn, kept on well until 200m before tuning one-paced.
Pressed forward outside early leader before taking hold and slipping into box seat. Urged forward turning for home, 2nd into straight before tiring from 300m.
Allowed to settle at rear along fence. Urged forward top of straight, made ground to 200m before tuning one-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Steadied passing 1000m, bumped around turn, boxed on one-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, dropping to rear. Difficult to settle approaching turn, found little in straight. Lame right front leg.
Knuckled over on jumping, pressed forward outside leader before settling one-back, one-off. Lost position around turn, tired in straight.
Hard ridden from outside draw to go forward, settling 2L behind leader back stretch. Still in contention entering straight before tiring.
Began OK, ridden forward to find cover, checked 1400m. Steadied around turn when looking for run, gave ground steadily from 300m.
Eased forward early to settle midfield, but stuck 3 wide with cover. Came wider on the turn and ran strongly to the line, holding off a late charge by 2nd.

Taken out slightly on jumping, before coming in to be worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Had to come around runners in the straight to get a clear run, and progressed quickly to make up a 5L deficit and nab 2nd.

Jumped before acceptances and pressed forward early to be behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Ran on steadily early in the straight, before looked to have peaked 200m. Picked up the bit again from 150m, and just weakening late.
Eased forward early to settle around midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran steadily to the wire, and catching 3rd late but didn't have a powerful kick.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed 4th, 1 off the fence. Ran on steadily in the straight, and had a nose in front at the 200m. Peaked soon after and swamped late.
OK away and found a position midfield, on the rail, when settling. Looked to have peaked at 200m, but ran on OK again from 150m and picked up a couple of slower ones.
Jumped well from the inside draw to sit forward of midfield, on the fence. Came in off heels at 150m, before switching out again 100 when awkwardly placed and losing momentum.
Dropped back early to be last early. Checked off heels at 500m and lost ground. Awkwardly placed on heels at 300m before switching inside, and outside the same horse again at 150m and lost momentum.
Taken forward early to be handily placed 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Well placed at the top of the straight, but never kicked and went to the line 1 paced.
Crowded soon after jumping and taken back to sit in the last 3, 8L off the leader. Only plugged away fairly in the straight.
Pushed early from the wide draw to lead. In front at the 200m, but peaked and weakened quickly from that point before easing out late.

OK away and pushed forward early. Stuck wide for most of the back straight, before settling just forward of midfield. Ran flat when asked the question at the top of the straight, and never ran on in the straight.
Lifted front feet off the ground and lost ground on jumping, eventually pushing to sit midfield, 1 off the rail. Came wide on turn, but ran flat when asked the question and eased out early.
Began OK from the wide barrier, but struggled to keep up early and last by the 800m, 10L off the leader. Tailed off by the home turn, and never persevered with in the straight.
