Shared pace on rails before allowing eventual runner-up to cross to rails, well poised outside the lead rounding home bend, renewed effort to gain slender advantage under pressure 200 metres out.
Worked his way across from the middle gate to soon obtain lead and then rails run 1000 metres out, unable to resist winner's tenacity and headed 200 metres out. (Tactic questioned)
Moderate start, soon dropped towards the rear, picked up to midfield on rails rounding home bend and saved ground on the turn, fought on steadily without threatening. (Lame due to punctured sole)
Soon dropped well behind, racing keenly in last on the bend, still trailing the field entering straight, finished off race well inside final 200 metres, did best work late.
Awkward start, soon ridden to prominent one-out-one-back position in 3rd, failed to quicken under pressure in the run home.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, settled just worse than midfield, shifted widest turning in, produced good late impression closing stages.
Taken back from a wide gate, gained closer on rails around the bend, baulked and switched out for a run over 200 metres out, failed to quicken to threaten.
Jumped well, settled wide without cover in midfield, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began well, soon settled in midfield, ran home one-paced.
Sluggish at start, eventually picked up pace from approaching 1000 metres, travelled 2L back in 4th on rails rounding home bend, weakened under pressure upon straightening.
Broke well from a poor draw, gradually settled wide in last few, found nothing in straight.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward, led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 250M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300m.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow sectionals, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, harmed by the slow tempo, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early, hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, never progressed.
Very slow away, took rail at back, harmed by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, little dash when clear.
Midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, no dash when clear.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, benefited by the slow pace, soon reduced 350M.
Never competitive at rear.
Sent forward to take the fence and led at fast sectionals, kept on strongly to the line by 3/4L.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, finished off strongly to get 2nd, missed by 3/4L.
Rolled forward to settle outside the leader, despite harmed by the fast pace, kept on steadily to the line for 3rd.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, despite harmed by the fast tempo, kept on one pace to the line for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, ran on nicely until weakened over the last few strides.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, made some ground in straight without real threats.
Crowded start and failed to muster despite hard ridden along in the early stages, settled 10Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Camped handy with cover, harmed by the fast sectionals, one paced home.
Taken back, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast tempo, never ran on and dropped off 300M.
Always at rear, despite benefited by the fast pace, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast pace, never ran on.
Camped handy, however trapped wide without cover throughout, soon weakened after straightening.
Sluggish start & bustled, recovered to midfield 1 off with cover, checked 600m, ridden turning in, crowded & not clear 380m, shaken up 320m, swept to lead 75m, drew clear.
Speed to lead out wide, edged across to settle 1 off 850m & held narrow advantage, shaken up 380m & kicked 1L clear, all out & headed 75m, boxed on.
Rousted at start to post handy 3 wide no cover, driven 360m & advanced to 2nd, attempted to hang in throughout stretch run, boxed on one pace.
Smart start, sat 1 back on fence, crowded 400m, shifted 1 off & ridden 350m, not clear run & checked 280m, driven 200m, stayed on for minor late headway.
Tardy break & rousted to settle midfield 3 wide with cover, driven wide into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Smart start & bustled up inside leader to race close 2nd, to rail 850m, driven 420m, one-paced in run & tapered late.
Broke well, raced 1 off 1 back, niggled 550m, driven 400m, kept on evenly.
Taken back at start to 1 off near rear, shaken up 430m & shifted centre track, kept on one pace.
Tardy start & bustled to race 3 wide with cover back of midfield, checked 600m, driven 500m, plugged home evenly.
Slow start & outpaced, rousted rail near rear, niggled throughout, hard-ridden into stretch, one-paced in run home.
Broke ok, trapped 4 wide no cover back of midfield, hard-driven & widest into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Taken to tail from widest gate, ridden 400m & shifted out, plodded on same speed.
Smartly away, soon outpaced & niggled to race 4th 1 off with cover, shifted out entering stretch, bumped 400m, quickened & dueled for lead final 240m, edged it close home.
Sharp start & prominent initially, settled rail in 5th, switched out & bumped rival 400m, driven to challenge, dueled for lead final 240m, outpointed last strides.
Tardy break, bustled a touch to race rail midfield, ridden 500m & shifted out, stayed on strongly to go 3rd at 150m, closed to wire.
Fast start, prominent early, settled back 6th 1 off with cover, under pump 650m, centre track & hard-ridden in stretch, boxed on evenly.
Slow start & raced last pair 1 off, shifted 3 deep for progress 650m, widest into stretch, bumped rival 400m & shaken up, stayed on without threatening.
Broke ok, rousted to lead 1300m, to rail & headed 1150m, raced 1 back & niggled, ridden along 520m, boxed on evenly.
Broke well, taken back to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wide into stretch, squeezed up & bumped 400m, ran on for minor inroads.
Slow start & ridden initially to 1 off with cover behind midfield, towards tail & driven turning in, stayed on for moderate headway.
Broke well, snagged back to rail near rear, driven turning in, stayed on moderately.
Broke ok, niggled early to hold position, raced midfield 3 wide no cover, wide into stretch, shaken up 400m, found nil & weakened.
Broke well, rolled forward to lead 1150m, crossed to rail 1000m & raced 2L clear, shaken up 380m, all out & headed 240m, faded out.
Broke ok widest, taken back to midfield but trapped 4 wide no cover, rolled forward from 1200m to sit 2nd 1 off at 900m, under pump 700m, found nil in stretch & faded out.
Awkward start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, under pump 600m & outpaced, struggled in tame run home.
Reared start & lost ground, raced rail last pair, niggled at tail 600m, detached & driven turning in, struggled in run home.
Urged forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/2L through slow sectionals, ran on well and held off challenge from 2nd to score.
Rolled forward to obtain box-seat, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader, suited to the slow pace, finished 2nd with a convincing effort.
Sat in front of midfield, 2-1/4L off 3 wide without cover, benefitted by the slow tempo, finished off nicely for 3rd.
At the rear along the rail, 7L behind the leader, improved slightly around turn, once straightened unleashed strong finishing effort for 4th.
In midfield, 3L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, finished off only one paced.
Travelled close to midfield, 4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, no dash in the straight.
Settled in midfield along the rail, 3-1/4L off the pace, not suited to the slow tempo, uncompetitive in the straight.
Travelled towards the rear, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, improved slightly near 200M only.
Sat in worse than midfield, 4-1/4L off the pace 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, weakened near 250M.
Raced prominently and outside the leader, 1-3/4L behind, despite suited to the slow pace, weakened gradually in the straight.
Always towards the rear and finished last, not competitive.
Ridden to find cover, settling 3-back between horses. Raced fiercely turn, checked 650m, finished strongly while laying in. Just got there.
Began well, shared early pace before easing two-back, one-off. Turned 4-wide, hit front 300m, looked winner, nailed on post.
Quickly into stride, grabbing box seat and trailing leader to straight. Ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Jumped with field then taken to rail 2-back from leader. Left fence entering straight and ran on steadily.
Began fairly, then pressed forward to lead on settling. Caught shortly after straightening but boxed on well until closing stages.
Hard ridden from outside draw but didn't muster and trapped 3-wide in midfield. Kept wide throughout but boxed on gamely in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and taken to fence towards rear. Switched out entering straight and finished off fairly.
Began well, pressed forward, settling one-off, one-back. Under pressure on straightening and gave ground gradually.
Slow into stride and last on settling. Trailed field to straight, switched wide, and ran on fairly.
Began fairly, ridden but didn't muster, dropping towards rear in one-off position. One-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners but raced fiercely and unable to find cover, racing wide at rear. One-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, then taken to fence 3-back from leader. Hard ridden from 400m but failed to make headway.
Pressed forward from start to sit outside leader to straight. Gave ground steadily after passing 300m.
Close up in 5th within 3Ls of leader, driven out 350M, led near 150M and pulled nicely clear for a commanding victory.
Prominently placed, had cover behind leader from 800M, ridden along nearing 400M, not finishing pace of winner but stayed on well enough to hold 2nd on the line.
Held up 4Ls off the pace in midfield, took time to gather on straightening, closed off well final 150M, just missed 2nd while offered no serious threat to winner.
Slow to begin, held up behind midfield first 800M then advanced 3-wide moving nearer to leaders, kept on steadily when driven out 400M, not reached winner.
Restrained to near the rear 6Ls off the pace, into clear 400M, ran on well to just miss a minor placing.
Positively ridden, crossed to lead 800M, pressed by rivals middle of the turn, kept on well early straight, headed 150M, faded towards line.
Up with early pace, travelled keenly when crossed by rivals middle stages, stayed on mildly over final 400M, always held by leaders.
Began only fairly, restrained behind midfield 5Ls behind leaders, shuffled back to near the rear 600M, made limited progress in straight and never reached contention.
Taken back from wide barrier, 8Ls back at the rear in middle stages, niggled along 600M, ran on only fairly on straightening.
Caught 3-wide no cover from 1000M, strode forward to join leader but unable to shift closer to fence, kept on same pace early straight, no extra 200M. (No Vet findings.)
Taken back from wide barrier, 7Ls off the pace in rear group, outpaced early straight, never able to challenge.
Up with pace along the 2-path but couldn't find much when the race got serious, dropped out 200M.
First into stride, clear leader to turn before steadying pace. Kicked 2L clear 400m, kept finding under pressure final 100m for narrow win.
Began well, pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off. Ran on strongly in straight but unable overhaul leader.
Steadied after start and shifted in behind midfield in one-off position. Improved around turn, very wide in straight, finished strongly.
Got off with field, ridden along 2-wide in midfield 4L from leader. Kept wide in straight and ran on steadily to be closes at finish.
Not used early, settling 3-back along rail. Left fence turning for home, ran on steadily in straight.
Shifted out and bumped at start before crossing to rail 4-back from leader. Switched out in straight and finished off nicely.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in, settling at rear in one-off position. Still well back entering straight before running on steadily.
Began well, ridden to hold rail 2-back from leader. Took inside run in straight and ran on steadily to 200m before turning one-paced.
Quickly into stride, pressed forward but wide, settling outside leader approaching turn. Still in contention entering straight before giving ground.
Pressed forward on jumping to hold rail, before slipping into slipstream of leader from 800m. Looked chance passing 400m before fading.
Steadied soon after start, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Trailed field thereafter and never competitive.

Placing: UR
Comment: Reared when gates opened, dislodged rider and stayed in stall. Took no part in race.

Eased forward early to sit forward of midfield, 1-2 off the fence, but never fully settled in the back straight. Had to make up 3L on the leader in the straight, and gradually wore him down. Strong over the last 100m.

Pushed forward early to stake a claim, and was sole leader by the 1000m. Looked to have outlasted challengers in the straight, and was running strongly in front at 100m. Peaked in the last 50m, and picked off for the win late.

Only fairly away and settled worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Raced tight and off hindquarters at 350m. Pulled out from there and ran home strongly. Battled for a place late, and just got 3rd in a bob on the line.

Slightly awkward away and dropped back early to be 3rd last, 9L off the leader. One of the last on the turn, and came wider in the straight. Ran home strongly, and went head to head in run for 3rd, and lost the bob on the line.
Began awkwardly, but pushed forward early to be handily place 3rd/4th, 1 off the fence. Well placed to kick from the 200m, but found nothing in the tank. Peaked late and was swamped on the line.
Steadied early from the wide draw to settle in midfield, 1 off the fence. Plugged away steadily in the straight, but never threatened a place.
OK to begin and taken up to be forward of midfield, on the fence. Ran on steadily in the straight without threatening a place, and raced tight briefly on the line.
Bumped on jumping and then steadied to get cover, worse than midfield, on the fence. Pushed in the straight, but only went to the line fairly.

Cruised across from the jump, and was stuck 3 wide with no cover up the back straight, just behind the leader. Came into 1 off the fence leaving the back straight. Stoked up on the turn, but didn't ignite and went home 1 paced.
Slow away, and dropped back early to be 2nd last, 10L off the leaders. Only battled on fairly when asked the question at the top of the straight, and not pushed to the line late.

Pushed forward from the wide draw to take the early lead, before being crossed at 1000m and dropping back to 3rd. Let down from the top of the straight, but never responded and dropped out quickly from the 300m.
Began OK, and eased forward from the inside draw to be midfield, on the rail. Never responded when asked the question and ran to the line flat, before easing from the 150m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to be 12L last at the 800m. Never improved in the run and last all the way until last 50m, only beat one who was easing out late.
Began well and taken forward early to be handily place 4th/5th. Under pressure before the turn. Showed nothing in the straight and eased out late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back at rear, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight and finished off very well to score.
Moderately away, raced 4 lengths or so back in midfield, similar position on turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off very strongly when clear final 200M, just missed.
Away with them, raced 6 lengths back at rear, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress when clear after 250M, no threat to the winner.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back in 6th, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back at rear, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made reasonable progress to be nearest on line.
Began well, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced 2 wide, 4-5 lengths back in midfield, carried wider on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 7 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, finished off one paced.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, got cover on turn, peaked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back early, improved after 1200M to race outside the lead, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 2 wide on turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed early speed to take the lead, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 150M.
Slightly slow out from gate 13, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in 5th, no cover for the majority of the race, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect. (Bled)
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Began well from the middle draw settling just off the pace, ran home one-paced.
Began well from a wide gate, settled 3-wide in 5th in forward of midfield, kept on well to finish.
Began moderately, settled behind midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled in 4th on rails within 3L of pace, drifted slightly backward far side, made modest progress without threatening.

Sent forward to park outside the leader, enjoyed the very slow sectionals, accelerated strongly to score by 1L.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the very slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.

Camped handy, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, suited by the very slow tempo, one paced to the line without any serious threat.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the very slow sectionals, ran on only fairly.

Sharp break wide, crossed to sit 2nd 1 off no cover 1300m, ridden to close 400m, battled to lead 250m, drew 1L clear & boxed on to wire.
Sharp break, settled behind pace on rail, 2L back & niggled a touch 800m, shifted out to challenge 420m, boxed on in pursuit, to 2nd 250m, always held.
Broke ok, raced rail midfield, shaken up 420m & shifted off fence, hard-ridden 350m, hung out 200m, shifted back in & kept on evenly to nick 3rd.
Slow start, niggled at tail, ridden along 500m, stayed on gradually under strong drive to just miss frame.
Fast start to lead, crossed to rail 1500m & raced 1.5L clear, 1L ahead & shaken up 380m, all out & headed 250m, tapered & lost 3rd close home.
Sluggish start & bustled to race rear rank 1 off, over-raced 900m, niggled 650m, driven turning in & dour progress, checked 200m, closed off for minor inroads.
Tardy break, raced 1 off behind midfield, edged out on turn, shaken up 380m, stayed on centre track for minor headway.
Sluggish start & niggled along to race rail behind midfield, over-raced 1200m, under pump 500m & shifted out, plugged on evenly.
Broke ok & rousted initially, raced handy 1 off with cover, niggled 580m & shifted out on turn, hard-driven 400m, found nil & faded.
Taken back from wide gate, raced 3 deep with cover near rear, niggled 1000m, shifted out & driven 430m, plugged on moderately.
Tardy start & taken back of midfield 3 wide with cover, very wide into stretch, plodded on tamely centre track.
Decent start, sat midfield 1 off with cover, shifted wide on turn & driven 420m, struggled & faded tamely.
Taken back from widest gate, trapped 4 wide no cover back of midfield, pushed on to mid rank 900m, gave ground on turn & driven 500m, widest into stretch, found nil & weakened.
Broke ok, caught 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, 4 wide on turn & outpaced, driven 400m, found nil & faded right out.
Broke well far side, raced handy mid rank centre track, cruised to leader's flank 440m, shaken up 350m, quickened under drive to lead 140m, driven clear.
Fast break, tracked leader 1L back, easy progress to lead 440m, shaken up 320m, failed to shake off pursuers, headed 140m, no extra.
Sharp start, raced handy mid rank on rail, shifted inside 200m, closed off readily to just miss 2nd.
Speed to lead, crossed to snag stands rail 700m, headed 440m, under pump 400m, battled back into contention 260m, out-kicked & boxed on evenly.
Smart start, raced handily mid rank, ridden 400m, hung to centre track & boxed on one pace.
Slow start & rousted initially to settle rail back of midfield, ridden 380m, drifted in & plugged on one pace.
Fast break, tracked leader close to stands' side fence, advanced to narrow 2nd 420m, ridden 320m, found little under pressure & faded out.
Tardy break, lacked toe & bustled a touch to race back of midfield, ridden under pressure 500m, one-paced in tepid run home.
Moderate start, soon niggled near tail, ridden 400m, outpaced & plugged on evenly.
Broke ok, soon niggled centre track near rear, under pump 550m, plodded on same speed.
Tardy start & outpaced, soon near tail on rail, last at 450m, driven 350m, kept on same speed to pass beaten rivals.
Slow start, raced tail centre track, niggled to advance a spot 450m, ridden 400m & edged towards far side, plodded on past fading rivals.
Tardy break & crowded early strides, bustled a touch to race back of midfield, ridden 450m, struggled in weakening run to wire.
Broke with others, raced centre track back of midfield, niggled early, under pump 450m, found nil & faded out tamely.
Rolled forward to lead by a short-head through slightly slow sectionals, once straightened unleashed strongly and cruised to a comfortable victory.
Travelled in midfield along the rail, 3L behind the leader, suited to the slow tempo, finished off nicely for 2nd, only lost out to an impressive winner.
Slotted into box-seat and was 1-1/2L off the pace, suited to the slow tempo, ran on well in the Straight.
At the rear, 4-3/4L behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow pace, closed off nicely, just missed out on 3rd.
Travelled in front of midfield, 1-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, shifted wide after turn for clear running, ran on okay.
Settled in midfield, 2-1/2L off the pace 3 wide with cover, raced widest momentarily in the middle stages when pushed out, dashed until 200M only.
Raced towards the rear, 4-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, improved only slightly after straightening, did not run on thereafter.
Prominent, 1/2L off the pace 3 wide without cover, despite suited to the slow tempo, finished off only one-paced.
Towards the rear and raced along the rail 4-1/4L behind the leader, harmed by the slow pace, not competitive.
Travelled in front of midfield, 3L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo and difficult to settle throughout, did not run on.
At rear, 5-3/4L off along the rail, no daylight in the Straight, not fully tested.
Sat outside the leader throughout, suited to the slow tempo, kept on with the main field until 200M weakened.
Travelled behind midfield, 3-3/4L off the pace 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, remained at rear in the Straight.
Travelled in front of midfield mostly but difficult to settle throughout, dropped off once straightened.
Ridden forward from wide draw before getting cover three-back, one-off 1000m. Not asked for effort till straightening, hit front 200m, kept on well while laying in.
Bumped start, pushed forward, taking box seat. Badly held up for run in straight before finishing well when clear 200m.
Ridden along early settling two back along rail. Switched out after straightening and ran on well closing stages.
Pressed forward to sit outside leader on settling. Put under pressure top of straight and kept battling to the line.
Crowded for room shortly after start, then taken forward one-off, two-back. Urged forward on straightening, hit front 300m, caught 200m, flattened 100m.
Began well, settling one-back, one-off. Steadied turning for home, looked chance passing 300m, then one-paced.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, then set steady pace to 300m when passed. Eased off heels 150m when giving ground.
Jumped with field but no early pace, settling towards rear in one-off position. Switched out in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Steadied soon after start, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Never in the hunt.
Steadied shortly after start then shifted across behind runners towards rear. Last entering straight and never competitive.
Bumped start, pressed forward three-wide without cover behind leading pair. Kept on till 200m before fading. Had mucus in trachea and entrapped epiglottis with ulceration.
Bumped start, ridden to hold rail behind midfield to straight. Gave ground quickly after passing 300m.
Eased to race in 2nd last 6Ls off pace, bustled along 550M, closed off strongly when driven wide in straight, got up near line.
Caught wide 1st turn, strolled forward from 1100M to join leader, strongly pressed leader from 400M, briefly in front 50M, headed late stages.
Had rail run from draw 2, held up in midfield 3Ls off pace, no clear run early straight, came through narrow passage 250M, closed off well to go 3rd just in time.
Quickly into stride, led from 1200M at a well-handled pace, pressed by rival 500M, continued on well in the lead but ended near 50M, weakened into 4th near line.
Not hurried early stages, settled down 5Ls off the pace behind midfield, held up from top of the straight to 200M, finished off willingly when switched into clear, nearest finish.
Shifted across behind runners from widest barrier, held up in last 6Ls off the slow pace middle stages, ran on well along inside, lacked room late stages not ridden out towards the finish.
Sent forward, tracked pace from 1200M, kept on steadily turning in but always held by leaders.
Began only fairly, driven forward but struck heels of rival and blundered 1500M, ended up 2-wide in midfield, stayed on moderately turning home, never a serious threat. (No vet findings)
Raced 3-wide behind midfield 4-5Ls off leaders, crept closer home turn, kept on same pace over final 300M.
Eased back early stages, towards the rear 5Ls back and saved ground along the fence, unable to obtain clear run in the straight, not tested.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, gave limited response when urged along 500M, gave ground mid-straight.
Began awkwardly, pushed along the 3-path to obtain a more handy spot behind leaders, no cover from 900M, faded out of contention nearing 250M.
Began awkwardly from draw 13, towards the rear and no closer than 3-wide throughout, weakened turning in, soon left behind. (No vet findings)

Placing: DNF
Comment: Broke down 1300M, retired out of the race.
Pressed forward to sit one-back, one-off behind leader. Had clear run entering straight, rolled forward from 300m, just got there, racing tight closing stages.
Began well, pushed forward, sitting 1L behind leader on settling. Inched closer around turn, hit front 300m, battled strongly when challenged, pipped on post.
Crowded for room soon after start, crowded again 1300m, dropping 4-back along rail. Crowded passing 1000m, switched out in straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, rolled forward along rail, two-back from leader. Held for clear run early in straight before finishing off nicely final stages.
Steadied soon after start, shifted across behind runners, settling at rear in one-off position. Switched wide 400m and ran on strongly closing stages.
Began well, pushed along in midfield in one-off position to straight where ran on steadily to 100m before turning one-paced.
Began fairly, then taken to rail three-back from leader. Stayed on rail in straight and boxed on gamely without looking dangerous.
Began well, urged forward, taking box seat 2L from leader. Kept on well in straight before giving ground from 200m. Not ridden out closing stages.
Pressed forward from widest draw, taking clear lead before crossing to fence 1100m. Caught 300m but kept on well till swamped final 100m.
Bumped start, steadied, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Ran on fairly in straight.
Tightened start, attempted to savage another runner and stumbled. Niggled at throughout to hold midfield position before tiring in straight. Trainer warned of racing manners.
Bumped start, ridden along but left wide without cover at rear passing 1200m. Allowed to roll forward, swooped around field and 3rd into straight before tiring.
Outpaced, dropping between horses at the rear. Lost touch with main field soon after straightening, finishing a long way back.
Began fairly, ridden along but kept very wide at rear, then became difficult to settle. Lost touch with field 400m and finished tailed off.
Began well and taken forward to be handily placed 4th, 1 off the fence. Took on early leader on the turn. Pulled away from 400m, and went to the line unchallenged.

OK away, and eased forward early to sit just worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Forced a run through at the 400m, but had 4L to make up on the winner. Ran well in the straight, but left with too much to do.

Broke well and pushed forward early to be handily placed in 3rd, 1L off the leader on the rail. Dropped back by the turn and plugged on steadily before rallying again late to take 3rd in a tight finish.
Pushed forward from the kick to take the lead early. Lost the lead at the top of the straight to the winner. Plugged away in the straight, weakening late, run down and missing a place.
Easy away, settling on the rail around midfield. Came inside to the rail after losing a run at 400m. Ran well to the line from there, and slightly on heels late.

OK away and eased forward early to sit forward of midfield, on the rail. Held up on heels until 250m, and running on steadily until held up again over the last 75m and couldn't be ridden out, missing a place in a tight finish.

Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Raced keen up the back straight, and came off heels at 1000m, and 900m. Near last on the turn, but improved steadily in the run home.

Inconvenienced on jumping and dropped back to race in the last group, 4 wide with limited cover and pulling. 7L last on straightening. Ran steadily until held up from 200m-100m, running well when clear late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to be last early. Ran to the line steadily in the straight, picking off some of the slower ones.

Began awkwardly and pushed forward early to be handily placed 1 off the fence, a ½ length off the early leader. Got the head up coming out of the back straight. Used up early and faded quickly in the straight.

Cruised forward early to settle midfield, 1 off the fence. Raced slightly tight on the turn, but had clear running at the top of the straight. Only plugged away 1 paced in the straight, and easing up late.

Taken back from the wide draw to be placed in the last couple, 3-4 wide. Unsettled and off heels 700m. Came widest on the turn, and drifted wider in the straight. Only plugged away, and not pushed out late.
Taken across early to sit midfield 3 wide, before being sitting wide with no cover from 1000m. Well placed on the turn, but never kicked and not pushed vigorously to the line.
Eased across early to sit around midfield, 3 wide with cover. Briefly tight on the turn. Ran flat when asked the question, and eased when jockey had concerns about the action.

Sat outside the leader throughout, suited to the slow pace, no dash once straightened.
In midfield, 3-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, made slight ground only in the straight.
Travelled just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, hardly improved.
In front of midfield, 2-1/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, suited to the slow tempo, couldn't find extra at 300M.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, struggled to put up a challenge.
Always at the back, never in contention.
In worse than midfield along the rail, 5L behind, weakened badly passing 300M.
Bumped start, pressed forward settling two-back along fence. Taken out 600m, blocked for run 400m, switched in, pressed forward to hit front 100m, held on.
Began well, not pushed, settling midfield in one-off position. Taken 4-wide passing 600m, bumped top of straight, ran on strongly to fail narrowly.
Jumped with field but caught wide behind midfield and allowed to roll forward settling 2.5L from leader 800m. Closed in around turn, hit front 200m, battled but swamped final strides.
Jumped best, led initially before being eased, settling 1.5L behind leader. Took over lead passing 400m, joined up front 200m, swamped final strides.
Began OK, not pushed, settling at rear. Last into turn, switched wide in straight, ran on strongly to be closest at finish.
Restrained after start, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Stayed on rail entering straight and ran on steadily.
Bumped start, bumped again shortly after, then pressed forward 3L from leader along fence. Kept on fairly to 200m before turning one-paced.
Began OK but raced fiercely, then checked 1300m. Difficult to settle, dropping towards rear between horses, One paced in straight.
Crowded out start, then tightened and checked, dropping to rear but wide without cover. Boxed on one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, pressed forward inside early leader before taking clear lead 1300m. Overtaken on straightening and faded.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-off, two-back. Checked around turn, lost position on straightening, faded.
Began fairly, no early pace, dropping behind midfield along rail. Shuffled back around turn, last into straight, plodded.
Restrained behind the pace along the fence, into clear 350M and chased home leader strongly, went head to head final with rival 50M, got up near finish.
Quickly crossed to the lead nearing 1000M, set good pace to straight, continued on strongly under urge and kicked 2L clear 250M, strongly pressed by rival final 100M, headed near line.
Began only fairly and unable to muster speed despite ridden, ended up near last 6Ls back, ran on well from off the pace on straightening, advanced to 3rd inside 150M, not reached first two.
Taken keen hold in midfield, saved ground along inside, kept on steadily turning in but not getting to first two. Respectable first up.
Eased back to near the rear early stages and shifted in to obtain cover, 3-wide turning for home, stayed on moderately for non-threatening 5th.
Began awkwardly, bustled along to chase leader, held 2nd till 250M, had little left in reserve late stages and weakened towards the line.
Settled 2-wide in the group chasing leaders, kept on same pace when driven 350M, never seriously threatened.
Held up 4-5Ls behind midfield, clear run and every chance passing 350M but stayed on only fairly, never reach contention.
Began awkwardly, ended up 6Ls back near the rear off the inside, kept on same pace final 400M, no impression on leaders.
Not far off, travelled along the 3-path ahead of midfield, remained in range turning home but failed to make an impact when driven out. (No Vet findings)
Strode forward, 3-wide no cover chasing leaders, driven out 400M but no progress, faded 250M.
Taken back from 12, obtained a 2-wide position behind midfield, unable to sprint with rivals inside 400M, never involved.
Towards the rear, outpaced and detached from the field middle stages, made no progress final 400M over this inadequate trip.
Sluggish away from 14, caught wide in midfield throughout, beaten top of straight.
Quickly into stride from wide draw, then eased 1250m to find cover three-back, one-off. Four-wide into straight, pressed forward strongly to win on line.
Pressed forward, racing 3-wide 1L behind leader. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 300m, battled when challenged but pipped on post.
Jumped well, travelled keenly when one-off, two-back. Found clear run entering straight, rolled forward to join leaders 200m, battled to line.
Ridden to hold forward position between horses 2L from leader. Closed in entering straight, kept on strongly under hard riding only to fail narrowly.
Pressed forward from outside draw, taking over lead 1250m but kept one-off by inside runner. Joined up front 200m, battled but swamped final strides.
Not pushed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Not asked for effort till straightening, finishing well down centre track.
Began well, allowed to stride forward holding rail 2-back from leader. Came off fence 600m to challenge but only one-paced in straight.
Steadied soon after start and shifted across behind runners, settling last. Switched out 450m and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Outpaced, dropping to rear in one-off position. Last into straight before making up some late ground.
Broke loose before start but declared fit. Began OK, holding rail in midfield to turn. One-paced in straight.
Slow into stride, ridden but didn't muster, settling at rear along fence. Switched out entering straight but only one-paced.
Slow, outpaced, dropping to rear in one-off position. Improved around turn but found nothing in straight.
Outpaced, taken to rail towards rear. Came off fence around turn but found nothing under hard riding in straight.
First out, led to 1250m then took sit. Got shuffled back turning for home, gave ground quickly in straight. Lost right fore plate on jumping.
Bumped on jumping and not used up early to settle midfield, on the fence. Came wider on the turn and ran strongly to the line, with the only challenger left with too much ground to make up.

OK away, and cruised forward early to be just forward of midfield, 1 off the fence. Tight on turning and held up until 200m, before coming across 4 sets of heels to get a run down outside. Big run late, but had too much to do.

Began awkwardly, & crowded soon after before pressing forward to be placed forward of midfield 4.5L off the leaders. Tight on turn, ran well in the straight, but unable to match winner & run down late to miss 2nd.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to be handily placed in 3rd, 1 off the fence. Well placed in the straight, and ran steadily to the line but easily taken by the first 3.

Dropped back from the wide draw to be placed worse than midfield and stuck 4-5 wide, before dropping to last at the 800m, 11L off the lead. Came wide in the straight, and flew late recording best final sectional.

Fairly away before pressing forward to share the lead, 1 off the fence. 2nd on the turn, and ran on steadily at the top of the straight. Tight at 250m, before bumped and laying away from heels at 150m and dropping out.

Dropped back from the wide draw to be at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence and 9L off the leader. Lost momentum when restricted at 400m, but ran steadily from that point and picked off some of the slower types.

Began well and cruised forward early, before being restrained to be handily placed in 4th, on the rails 1.5L off the leader. Ran steadily when asked from 400m but lost momentum when hampered 150m, and dropped out.
Bumped on jumping, and then pressed forward to take the lead. Led by 1.5L turning for home, but ran flat in the straight and eased out from the 150m after being hampered.
Began OK and taken up sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Never got settled and was taken to 3 wide no cover from the 900m. Battled on gamely, but was a beaten horse early in the straight.

OK away, but tended to over race early when placed worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Went searching for a run at the top of the straight, but didn't have the power to take advantage and only went to the line fairly.
Fairly away and eased forward to be worse than midfield early, on the rails. Never produced in the straight, running one paced and eased out from the 200m.
Bumped just after the kick and not used up early to sit just behind midfield, 3 wide with cover. Came wider on the turn, but was already under pressure and went to the line flat.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to sit 2nd last, 10L off the leader. Never kicked in the run home and dropped out late, easing towards the line.

Made all from the one draw in an apparently favouring track, hung on well.
Jumped well, soon obtained rails run just off the pace chasing the leader to straight, kept on well without threatening.
Ridden along wide without cover in first few, similar entering straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, raced keenly behind midfield, commenced move entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield from a wide draw, remained wide to halfway out, raced nearer the rails rounding home bend, kept on same pace in the run home.
Jumped well, 2L back in 4th when unbalanced and lost position past the Rock, found nothing in straight. (Bled)
Tightened at start, trailed the field to straight, kept on past well-beaten horses.
Travelled in last few on rails, kept on without quickening in straight.
Sluggish start, remained well behind throughout.
Gradually settled towards the rear from the widest gate, never seen with a chance.
Prominent briefly, soon dropped to midfield on rails, steadied for a stride 600 metre out, faded out of contention inside final 400 metres.
Began well, raced outside the leader to home bend, folded up quickly after straightening. (Bled & lame)
Pushed forward to cross, led comfortably at good pace, drifted away 300M to score.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield 2 wide, little dash 200M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, ran on fairly in straight.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, ran on until 100M flattened.
Checked early, at rear, 2 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, took rail, ran on only fairly in final stages.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, held ground in straight.
Hold the rail at back, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, hung out badly around the bends, never progressed.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, reduced rapidly 400M.
Rolled forward to hold the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, accelerated strongly to score another impressive victory.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow pace, dashed nicely for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow sectionals, ran on gradually.
Ridden forward to take the fence and shared the lead at slow sectionals, kept on until final 50M weakened.
Camped handy, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, kept on one pace to the line.
At back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, ran on nicely.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Failed to muster despite niggled along throughout, unable to make any impression in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and stumbled, at back throughout, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader from a wide draw, kept on one pace until weakened final 200M.
Broke well, slotted 1 off with cover 4th, shifted 3 deep & ridden to challenge 420m, swept off turn & quickened centre track to lead 120m, won cosily.
Speed to lead & soon to rail, nudged a touch to extend 400m, 1L clear & driven turning in, all out & headed 120m.
Broke well & bustled on rail to sit 1 back, switched 1 off & driven 230m, quickened up & battled to just hold 3rd.
Fair break, taken back to 1 off with cover, niggled 450m & shifted 3 wide, hard-ridden widest into stretch, ran on without threatening.
Awkward start, sat rail midfield, niggled 520m, ridden 400m & shifted out, grinding minor inroads to just miss frame.
Decent start & bustled a touch, slotted 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 520m, under pump 430m, fanned wide into stretch, stayed on dourly to just miss frame.
Slow start & bustled up at tail, rolled on rail to sit near rear, shifted out on straightening & hard-ridden, outpaced but kept on to press for minors.
Lacked toe & bustled early, soon settled at tail, niggled 500m, driven home turn, outpaced & boxed on tepidly.
Fast break & parked close 2nd 1 off, niggled 500m, driven under pressure final turn, found nil & weakened tamely.
Speed to lead, set tempo on rail, narrow lead when kicked on turning in, drew clear under drive, eased close home.
Broke well, raced 4th 1 off with cover, niggled 650m, under pump 450m, shifted out final turn, boxed on determinedly to nick 2nd.
Started well but outpaced & rousted, settled rail midfield, niggled 650m & driven 400m, shifted centre track & closed for late gains.
Bustled initially to press lead, slotted rail 1 back, niggled 600m, hard-driven 450m, outpaced but fought on dourly in defeat.
Pushed on from wide gate & 3 wide no cover 1st turn, parked 2nd 1 off no cover, niggled 600m to press leader, driven turning in, outkicked but boxed on until emptied 100m.
Fast start & rousted, restrained & over-raced 1st turn, settled 5th on rail, niggled 450m, hard-ridden turning in & outpaced, plugged on again late.
Awkward break, raced midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 670m, shifted 3 wide 430m & driven wide into stretch, closed to vie for minors, tapered late.
Taken back from wide to race 1 off at tail, last pair & niggled 600m, driven into stretch & plugged on tepidly.
Buffeted start & raced 2nd last on rail, niggled 450m, shifted out on turn & driven, hung out in tepid run home.
Smart start, snagged to 1 off with cover back of midfield, niggled 600m, driven 500m & minor wide progress on turn, boxed on until emptied 150m & faded.
Taken back from wide to 1 off with cover near tail, under pump 450m, found nil in tame run home.
Sluggish break, raced near rear, niggled along, driven 450m, found nil & weakened in run.
Slotted into box-seat after deciding against to lead, remained prominent until found extra at 100M to finish off for the win.
Sat just in front of midfield along the rail and 2-3/4L behind, held up until near 150M, finished off nicely thereafter.
Rolled forward to take the rail and led until 150M when headed, still ran on well for 3rd.
Towards the rear, 6-1/4L off 2 wide with cover, taken widest after turn, dashed well for 4th.
Sat in just behind midfield along the rail, 4L behind the leader, made slight ground only.
In midfield, 3-1/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, no dash in the straight.
Sat in front of midfield, 1-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, over-raced in the middle stages, did not run on.
Pushed forward, and sat outside the leader, weakened after 150M.
Travelled close to midfield, 4-3/4L off 2 wide with cover, finished off only one paced.
Behind midfield, 5L behind and trapped 3 wide without cover, did not improve.
Taken back and was never in contention.
Ridden early before settling one-off behind midfield. Took closer order around turn, four-wide entering straight, finished strongly to win close home.
Pressed forward 3-wide from outside draw, settling two-back, one-off. Rolled forward turn, hit front 150m, looked winner, run down final strides.
Began well, pushed to lead in one-off position before crossing to rail 1200m. Caught passing 150m but kept on well to line.
Vigorously ridden to hold rail inside leader before settling in box seat passing 1300m. Took rails run in straight and boxed on gamely.
Jumped OK, settling in midfield close to fence. Switched out turning for home, ran on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Inconvenienced start, then taken to fence 3-back from leader. Lost position final turn but stayed on rail and ran on steadily in straight.
Not pressed early and held 3-wide at rear back stretch. Four-wide around final turn, one-paced in straight. Lame left front leg.
Pressed forward, racing 3-wide before settling in one-off position 2L from leader. Urged forward top of straight but flattened 150m and faded.
Crowded start, shaken up but raced keenly first turn and back stretch. Got close to heels turn, one-paced in straight.
Urged forward from wide draw before crossing to fence 2-back from leader. Kept on well until 200m before fading.
Slow into stride, trailed field to 800m, hard ridden around turn to improve but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, holding rail behind midfield, before losing position final turn. Lost contact with field in straight. Had substantial amount of mucus in trachea.
Soon led, had uncontested lead, rallied on strongly when joined by rival 150M, dug in gamely late stages to prevail.
Travelled strongly behind leaders, lodged a bid inside the winner 200M, drew alongside final stages and was just denied in a close finish.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield 4Ls off the pace, gathered momentum passing 250M and closed off willingly late, nearest finish.
Positively ridden and gained a forward spot just off the pace, chased winner from 300M but always held, inclined to lay in late stages.
Held up near the rear 5Ls behind leader, made some progress past 250M, altered course 150M and stayed on mildly down outside.
Not hurried early stages, dropped back to the rear group 7Ls off leader, took a while to pick up in straight, did best work past 150M.
Soon hugged the rail and raced in mid-division, 4Ls to make up leaving 400M, made a mild bid entering straight but evened out late in the drive.
Urged along soon after jumping from 12, obtained a 2-wide spot in the group chasing leaders, pursued to 150M then found no extra late.
Restrained to race towards the rear 5Ls off leader, found less than expected when driven out 300M, never a threat to leaders. (Jockey : horse not suited by the way the track was racing)
Eased back to the rear from wide barrier, proved very difficult to settle down the back straight, 3-wide turning for home and not picked up to challenge.
Began only fairly, unhurried and settled as the back-marker, 7Ls behind leader leaving 400M, didn't respond to riding and soon weakened.
Began only fairly from 11, caught wide no cover throughout, moved closer to midfield before the turn, had little left and gave ground early straight. (lost LF plate at start)
Pressed forward to lead passing 1550m, crossed to fence 1250m and slowed pace, Kicked clear entering straight and kept on strongly under hard riding.
Restrained on jumping and taken to fence at rear. Improved around turn, had to weave between horses in straight but finished strongly.
First out, taken to rail inside leader, grabbing box seat first turn. Under pressure entering straight but kept on well to line.
Ridden along initially before restrained and taken to fence in last place 1200m. Took rails run in straight and finished strongly.
Began well, stayed with pace but lost position after being crossed first turn. Switched out in straight and boxed on gamely.
Not pushed, settling four-back along rail. Took inside run in straight and made ground steadily until steadied 50m.
Inconvenienced start, not pressed settling at rear but wide. Improved around turn but one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, bumped, pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off. Kept on well till 200m when tired and faded.
No early pace, settling at rear but away from fence. Kept wide around turn, very wide in straight but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, hard ridden but didn't muster and held wide behind the pace. Rolled forward from 1000m to sit outside leader 850m. Gave ground soon after entering straight.
Ridden along between horses in midfield before losing position around turn. One-paced in straight though no clear run 100m.
Began well, pressed forward racing 3-wide behind pace-makers. Left without cover from 800m, kept on to 200m when tired badly.

Settled wide in midfield from the widest gate, took closer order from the 800 metres to be 2L 4th 3-wide rounding the bend, sustained effort down home straight to just get up on line.
Soon took up running on rails gaining 2L advantage 200 metres out, flattered and caught final strides.
Settled just worse than midfield, remained similar into straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled towards the rear, steadied briefly after straightening, finished off race well.
Settled wide in midfield from a wide gate, lost position passing the 800 metres and the widest runner rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening. (Tactic questioned)
Slightly slow out but quickly recovered to just behind the leader on rails, kept on before finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Settled in rear, did not find much room early in straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Ridden to keep up with pace early settling one-back 2-wide approaching home bend, kept on until finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Prominent from a wide gate, lost position under pressure rounding home bend, ran home one-paced. (Lame next day)
Sluggish at start, trailed the field most of way, went past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Raced wide without cover in better than midfield far side, lost position sharply rounding the bend, made no impression in straight.
Prominent briefly, gradually settled in midfield on rails, dropped out tamely.
At back, took rail, pace good, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear and scored.
Took rail and led easily at good pace, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Behind midfield, trapped 3 wide with cover, pace good, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide no cover, pace good, ran on well to the line.
Eased back, took rail, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on strongly until 150M flattened.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, made early move around the field in 4 wide, made steady ground.
Midfield along the rails, pace good, no turn of foot in straight.
Settled behind midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, lack room 400M, little dash when clear, run ended 150M.
At back along the fence, never improved.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, no dash.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, soon emptied 350M.
Raced midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader middle part of the track, dashed well to score by 3/4L.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader grand side, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, travelled 3Ls behind the leader middle part of the track, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Camped handy, travelled nicely behind the leader grand side, ran on steadily when clear 300M.
Jumped slowly, settled at rear early, improved gradually mid stages down the middle part of the track, ran on steadily.
At back, travelled 4Ls behind the leader middle part of the track, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader grand side, ran on only fairly.
Pushed to settle midfield along outer fence, kept on fairly and weakened 100M.
Rolled forward to share the lead grand side, kept on until 250M weakened.
At back throughout, never in a competitive position.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Sent forward to share the lead grand side, kept on until final 250M weakened badly.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Showed good early pace to share the lead along outer fence, dropped off badly 350M.
Fast start wide, prominent no cover & taken back from 900m to midfield 3 wide, progress on turn, 3rd & driven 400m, buffeted 340m, quickened final 200m to lead 120m, drew clear.
Fast start to track lead on rail, 1 back from 700m, shifted out 340m & buffeted winner, no match & boxed on to 2nd close home.
Speed widest to lead, worked to rail 700m, pressured final turn, driven 0.5L clear 350m, all out & headed 120m, no extra & tapered, lost 2nd late.
Broke with others, taken back & settled rail near rear, shifted 1 off 700m, not clear run on turn & back to rail, ridden 350m, closed for solid inroads.
Broke ok & niggled along, trapped 4 wide no cover midfield, advanced 880m to press leader 580m, close 2nd & driven 420m, emptied 250m & weakened out.
Taken back, raced 1 off with cover near tail, shifted wide home turn, plodded on evenly centre track.
Sluggish at start, settled rail midfield, over-raced on turn & head in air 550m, driven 350m & switched out, plugged on tepidly & tapered late.
Dropped in at start to last pair 1 off, driven wide final turn, kept on one pace centre track.
Decent break, taken back to 3 wide with cover midfield, shuffled back a spot 700m, bustled 450m & forced wide into stretch, struggled one pace, faded late.
Taken back at start to tail 1 off, driven into stretch, struggled in run home.
Broke ok but soon outpaced, checked 1050m, settled midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out turning in, found nil in weak run home.
Broke well & prominent, raced close up 1 off no cover, 1 off 1 back at 500m, under pump 460m, found nil & weakened.
Smart break, raced handy 3 wide no cover, rolled to lead 980m & to rail 820m, pressed & shaken up 400m, dueled in stretch & edged away close home.
Speed to lead, to rail 1200m, headed 980m & raced 1.5L 2nd 820m, edged 1 off on turn, closed on bridle to vie for lead 400m, shaken up 350m, outpointed in duel to wire.
Sharp break, sat 1 back on rail, shuffled back a spot 820m, driven approaching final turn, boxed on dourly for 3rd.
Started ok, raced 1 off & shuffled to back of midfield, shifted out & ridden turning in, closed off for sound headway.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, edged 3 deep 650m & widest turning in, driven 430m, closed centre track without threat.
Moderate start, raced rail midfield, driven into stretch, boxed on for moderate headway.
Slow start, raced rail near rear, switched out 400m & ridden, boxed on for minor inroads.
Started ok, sat handy 1 off with cover, shuffled back on turn, over-raced 750m & 640m, crowded & switched out 320m, shaken up 250m, plugged on one pace.
Sluggish break & bustled initially, raced 1 off near rear, shuffled to last 600m, ridden along 500m, plodded on one pace.
Moderate break, bustled to race 3 wide with cover midfield, lost cover 950m, wide advance to 3rd 550m, ridden 400m, found nil & faded.
Tardy start widest, raced 4 deep no cover back of midfield, checked 1050m & slotted 3 wide with cover, driven turning in, outpaced & tapered out.
Outpaced & rousted initially, raced 3 wide with cover near rear, awkward turning in, found nothing under drive.
Fast start, raced close up 1 off no cover, shifted 3 wide to challenge 600, ridden 450m, weakened in tame run home.
At back, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, ridden to improve from 800M, ran on nicely from thereon for the win.
Sat towards the rear, 6-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, suited to the fast tempo, finished off nicely for 2nd.
Pushed forward to cross and eventually settled in box-seat, despite the fast sectionals, dashed well from 350M for 3rd.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 3-1/4L off along the rail, bumped at 400M, after that was held up and not tested until 100M.
Prominent, 1-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast pace, kept on until 200M when could not find extra.
Slotted in behind midfield, 5-1/4L off along the rail, checked near 250M, made slight ground thereafter.
At rear along the rail, 8L behind the leader, despite not suited to the fast tempo, made ground steadily inside 200M.
In worse than midfield, 5-1/4L off 2 wide with cover, harmed by the quick sectionals, kept on one paced to the line.
Settled in midfield, 3-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, proved difficult to ride in the Straight, weakened after 200M.
Sat outside the leader, not suited to the quick tempo, out of steam near 200M.
Pushed forward to lead at quick sectionals in the first sections, not suited to quick pace, weakened near 200M.
Not pushed, settling behind midfield but wide. Improved around turn, switched wide in straight, finished strongly to win close home.
Slow, urged forward, settling two-back along rail. Took closer order around turn, took inside run in straight and ran on strongly.
No early pace, dropping to rear but wide. Covered extra ground turn, taken wider in straight, finished strongly.
Began well, quickly in front, crossing to rail. Set good pace, looked winner with 200m remaining, swamped final 50m.
Hampered start, urged forward, settling midfield in one-off position. Blocked when improving 300m, steadied 100m, boxed on in restricted room.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw settling at rear along fence. Stayed at rear to straight before making ground final 200m.
Began well, pressed forward to sit outside leader around turn. Boxed on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Began well, kept in one-off position and gradually shuffled back to rear between horses. Switched out in straight to make run but one-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, settling 3-wide at rear. Took inside run in straight but badly held up 150m. Boxed on.
Hampered start, pressed forward but left wide without cover from 1300m. Stayed in contention to 200m before tiring.
Jumped with field, ridden along between horses behind tearaway leaders. Lost position turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Began well, rolled forward, stalking leader one-back, one-off. Closed in top of straight before running out of steam 200m. Unacceptable performance.
Quickly into stride, pressed forward, taking box seat and tailing leader. Looked chance entering straight before tiring from 200m. Confirmed to be a "roarer".
Shifted across behind runners from a wide draw and last on settling while racing ungenerously. Never in the hunt.
Chased the pace from the outside, strongly challenged leader passing 350M, wrestled the lead 150M out and pulled away towards the line.
Led slowly from the front, kept on well when pressed by rival early straight, lost lead 150M, faded late stages and held on for 2nd just.
Began fairly, held up near the rear 4-5Ls off the pace, took a while to get going passing 400M, did best work final 200M, got up for 3rd near line.
Close up in 4th, advanced to 3rd 200M and kept up the chase on leaders, always held in the run to the line, lost 3rd late. (No Vet findings)
Settled down in midfield 3Ls off the slow pace, in 5th place turning in, held up early straight, altered course 250M and stayed on mildly to the line.
Tracked leaders along the fence, kept on steadily on straightening but lacked extra pace to challenge, raced in restricted room late and not ridden out towards finish.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, unbalanced when bumped by rival 250M, ran on mildly without threatening late stages.
Reserved in the rear, 5Ls off the pace leaving 400M, not pace to challenge, never a threat.
Went forward early, was steadied to rear after 1100M but failed to obtain cover, not quickened in straight, left behind 200M and weakened towards the line. (No Vet findings)
Began well, ridden to stay with pace but 3-wide at 900m. Rolled forward to sit 3rd passing 650m, joined leader 400m, pulled clear final stages.
Quickly in front from outside draw, racing wide till crossing to fence 1100m. Quickened tempo passing 600m, joined up front 400m, kept battling to line.
Began well, ridden along between horses 3L from leader. Not much room top of straight but kept on well to the line.
Ridden along early but wide, then travelled keenly while improving position around turn. Looked a chance at 200m but unable to find extra close home.
Urged forward but wide early, before travelling keenly from 1100m when left without cover. Bumped turn when improving, kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped with field but pocketed on rail and shuffled back behind midfield. Switched out turning for home and boxed on fairly in straight.
No early pace, dropping to rear but wide. Steadied passing 1300m, wide around turn, even wider in straight, kept on one-paced.
Urged forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide to 1000m before rolling forward to sit outside leader at turn. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Ridden to hold forward position, quickly crossing to rail and taking sit on leader. Got shuffled back around turn, one-paced in straight.
Outpaced and soon at rear but wide. Kept wide around turn, taken wider in straight, but only one-paced.
Began well, ridden along in one-off position behind pace before taking box seat around turn. Left flat-footed 600m when tempo quickened, one-paced in straight.
Began OK but steadied 1500m, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Kept on fairly early in straight before tiring.
Crowded for room shortly after start, dropping to rear in one-off position, Switched out in straight to make run but never got going.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, dropping to last along rail. Checked off heels around turn and never likely thereafter.

OK away, dropping back early to sit near the rear of the field, on the rail. Took the short cut on the rails rounding the turn, before coming wider early in straight. Ran fastest in the straight to steal it right on the line.

Bumped on jumping and pressed forward to be handily placed early, before dropping back towards midfield 1000m. Got in front at 250. Ran steadily and looked to have it before won, before being caught right on the line.
Began well and taken forward to be early leader, before allowing to be crossed 1000m and settling 3rd. Ran steadily to the line in the straight, before weakening late. Just held 3rd.

Began well, but only cruised forward early to be midfield, 3 wide. Came wider on the turn and ran strongly in the straight. Raced tight at 200m, but kicked well to the line and was running down 3rd late.

Pushed forward early to be handily placed in 4th, on the rail. Raced tight when aiming to push forward at the top of the straight, and briefly on heels. Ran OK to the line, but ran away from whip and weakening late.
Fairly away and found a position midfield, on the fence. Badly held up in the straight until the 200m when coming wider. Ran on steadily when clear and finished off well.
Slow away and elected to drop back early to sit worse than midfield, 3 wide. Came wide on the turn and ran to the line steadily with minimal urging.
Keen early when steadied to find cover in midfield, 1 off the fence. Raced keen down the back straight. Plugged on steadily in the straight, but never threatened.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to eventually share the lead, 1 off the fence. Faded out from the 350m, and eased across the line late.
Not pressed early, and allowed to settle towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Came very wide on the turn and ran on fairly, without threatening the first half of the field.
Bumped early, and unsettled when being steadied back to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Only 1 paced to the line.
Pushed forward early from the inside draw to share the lead, 1 off the fence. Lead at the 400m, but never responded to pressure in the straight and not pushed out late.

Fractious in the barrier before bounding out and losing ground. Stuck at the back of the field, 3-4 wide with no cover. Race had been run by the turn, and only plugged away to the line with little urging in the straight.

Slightly tardy into stride, but pushed forward soon after to be handily placed in 5th, but tended to over race and stuck 3 wide with no cover from 800m. Fading before the turn, and dropped out in the straight, easing late.

Broke well from a middle draw, wide in midfield early before parked 2-wide behind runners just worse than midfield, obtained clear run over 250 metres out and ran on under pressure to claim race close to home.
Taken across from a wide gate for rails run towards the rear, remained similar turning in, ran on down the inner of home straight to just fail to get up on line.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on rails, came under strong pressure upon straightening, ran on doggedly to narrowly miss first two.
Worked his way across from a wide gate to lead or dispute lead, fought hard to gain slender advantage briefly 200 metres out but soon swamped.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on rails, quickened to hold some chance inside final 100 metres only to be swamped final few strides.
Tightened at start and dropped to last few, trailed the field most of way down back straight and around home bend, went widest turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Trailed the field before making swift progress down far side to reach midfield 3-wide, came under pressure round home bend and a widest runner into straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track. (Tactic questioned)
Led or disputed lead on rails, unable to sustain effort and retreated inside final 200 metres.
Slightly slow out, soon settled in rear of midfield, kept on same pace in the run home.
Jumped fairly, settled about 2L off the pace in 5th, came under pressure rounding home bend, soon weakened in straight.
Raced wide without cover just better than midfield, gave ground from the 500 metres.
Midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast sectionals, made steady ground 300M to score by narrow margin.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden early, at back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M, run ended 100M.
Pressed forward, 2-3 wide, pace fast, ran on well to the line.
Eased back, benefited by the fast pace, worked around the field 600M in 3-4 wide, made steady ground.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M flattened.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, pace fast, flattened 200M.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 200M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast pace, dropped off 300M.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led at very slow sectionals, hung on strongly to score by a short head.
Eased back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the very slow pace, dashed well for 2nd, missed by a short head.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the very slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, suited by the very slow sectionals, kept on well until weakened concluding stages.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the very slow pace, one paced home.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the very slow pace, made some ground in straight.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, despite suited by the very slow tempo, kept on only fairly without extra acceleration.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the very slow sectionals, unable to make any impression in straight.
Settled midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the very slow pace, never ran on.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, despite benefited by the very slow tempo, faded soon after straightening.
Taken back to the fence from a wide gate, travelled 7Ls behind the leader, hampered by the very slow pace, made minor ground in straight.
At back throughout, never a factor.
Away nicely, taking box seat on settling and stalking leaders to straight. Switched out 300m to challenge, hit front 70m, pulled clear.
Hard ridden to lead 930m but shaded by inside runner 600m. Retook lead passing 400m, battled strongly when challenged, losing in final strides.
Pressed forward, stalking leading pair in one-off position to straight. Threw out strong challenge but unable close gap.
Bumped start, not pressed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Put under pressure on straightening and ran on steadily.
Bumped start, rolled forward, settling one-off, two-back. Switched out in straight and ran on fairly.
Began OK, taken to rail, three-back from leaders. Took inside run in straight and kept on fairly.
First out, led to 930m when passed. Retook lead 600m, collared 400m, kept on well till 100m when flattened.
Began fairly, bumped, then taken to rail towards rear. Found little under hard riding in straight.
Steadied, shifted in, but raced keenly and held wide without cover. Improved around turn but one-paced in straight.
Shifted in from wide draw but no pace and soon at rear away from fence. Found nothing when asked in straight.
Began awkwardly, lost ground and last on settling. Never in the hunt.
Jumped straight to the front when gates opened and made all. Swung wide entering straight but kept finding when challenged.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling 3-back along rail. Made ground around turn, got rails run in straight, finished strongly to just fail.
Pressed forward to sit outside hindquarters of leader. Swung wide entering straight, battled strongly but unable close gap.
Away nicely, grabbed box seat and tailed leader to straight. Got clear run when leader swung wide but unable close gap.
Began OK, ridden to hold forward position 2L from leader but wide. Taken wider around turn, boxed on in straight without looking dangerous.
Began awkwardly, crowded, dropping to rear. Hugged rail around turn, making up some ground, ran on fairly in straight.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in but unable find cover and held three-wide at rear. Ran on fairly in straight.
Began well, urged forward but wide, settling one-off, two-back. Lost some ground around turn, one-paced in straight.
Restrained, shifted across behind runners from wide draw, dropping to last approaching turn. One-paced in straight.
Bumped start, urged forward, settling one-back, one-off. Under pressure soon after straightening and gave ground gradually.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide before easing back at turn. Found nothing when asked in straight.
Bumped start, ridden to hold midfield position between horses, checked around turn, faded gradually in straight.
Travelled just in front of midfield, 3L off on the rail, suited to the slow pace, found an extra gear near 200M for the win.
Pushed forward to grab box-seat, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader, suited to the slow pace, ran on well for 2nd.
In midfield along the rail, 4-3/4L off the pace, finished off well once cleared passing 200M.
Rolled forward into the lead and led by 1-1/2L at slow sectionals, kept on until headed and weakened passing 200M.
Prominent, 2-3/4L off the pace 2 wide and without cover, benefited by the slow pace, found little for the final 200M.
Towards the rear and raced on the rail, 9-1/2 off the pace, not suited to the slow tempo, dashed well and made good ground.
In midfield along the rail, 6-1/2L off the pace, not suited to the slow pace, improved slightly only.
Raced behind midfield, 7-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, made slight ground down the outside straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, 4-3/4L off 3 wide without cover, ran on until 250M then weakened.
Fractious and missed start, remained at the rear, did not run on.
Always at the back, never a factor.
Sat just behind midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, finished tailed out.
Pressed forward to sit outside hindquarters of leader on settling. Shaken up entering straight, hit front 200m, pulled clear final stages.
Quickly away, settling one-back, one-off. Rolled forward on straightening, looked to overhaul leader 200m but one-paced final strides.
Began well, taken to rail two-back from leader and settled. Took inside run in straight and kept on well to the line.
Checked shortly after start, refused to settle and checked again around turn. Switched out in straight and finished strongly.
Hampered shortly after start, dropping towards rear close to fence. Well back entering straight, switched out 200m, ran on well.
Bumped start but soon in front, setting steady pace. Collared passing 200m but kept on well till flattened 50m.
Steadied soon after start, ridden to find cover, settling at rear. Came off fence around turn, ran on steadily between horses in straight.
Snatched up on jumping and taken to rail behind runners, settling four-back from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but one-paced in straight.
Ridden along from outside draw but unable find cover and held three-wide behind midfield. Wide throughout and one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward but travelled keenly between horses 3L from leader. Found little in straight. Lost left hind plate 900m.
Bumped start, rolled forward, taking box seat and trailing leader to straight. Hard ridden to hold position to 200m before fading.
Steadied soon after jump but refused to settle and gradually lost touch with field, finishing tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Settled down in 5th 4Ls off the pace, driven out nearing 400M, swiftly moved up to join leader 200M, gained narrow advantage under strong ride, held sway at the finish.
Strolled to the lead as expected, took them along evenly, fought on gamely when joined by eventual winner 200M, unable to match strides late but was clearly 2nd best.
Tracked pace along the inside, chased first 2 passing 250M but always held, faded late.
Held up behind midfield 7-8Ls off the pace, stayed on moderately for non-threatening 4th.
Not hurried, settled down near the rear 8-9Ls behind leaders, ran on mildly on straightening, no threat to leaders.
Restrained to race near last, 10Ls off the pace in first half, kept to inside entering straight, made some progress without threatening.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, 6-7Ls off the pace middle stages, bustled along 450M, stayed on mildly.
Caught wide early, used a bit to go forward finding the lead, emptied passing 250M and weakened.
Travelled 2-wide in midfield, didn't respond to urging 400M, eased when beaten.
From widest barrier soon taken across behind runners, settled last over 10Ls off the pace, not found much when pushed along, soon beaten.
Began awkwardly, tracked leaders and remained in touch to 400M, dropped away when placed under pressure, weakened rapidly. (No Vet findings)
In midfield and saved ground along the fence, gave way passing 300M, eased.
