Pressed forward from a wide gate, remained wide rounding first bend and far side, obtained position outside the leader passing the 1000 metres, hit the front 350 metres out, hung on well.
Ridden from the one draw, settled about 2L off the pace on rails, gained closer and switched off rails to challenge turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards the rear, baulked for a run early in straight, switched and produced good late finish inside final 200 metres.
Broke well, settled in forward of midfield, came under pressure entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield or just worse, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Soon took up running and led the field to the 350 metres, folded up quickly.
Slowly away, quickly crossed to rails and picked up to midfield, saved ground turning in, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Travelled wide in midfield from the widest gate, dropped towards the rear from rounding home bend, made up late ground under pressure in the run home.
Settled well behind, saved ground turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Never far off to straight, soon weakened.
Always in last few.
Always well behind.
Settled wide in midfield, lost position approaching home bend, made no show in straight.
Ridden from a wide gate travelling wide prominently, drifted steadily backward to midfield far side, soon weakened in home straight.
Pushed forward to cross, led at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Pushed forward, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on until 250M flattened.
Midfield, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in final stages.
Behind midfield, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Hard ridden forward, benefited by the slow pace, ran on until 200M flattened.
Behind midfield, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Failed to muster, at back, not suited by the slow pace, no progress in straight.
Never improved at rear.
Never competitive behind midfield.
At rear, trapped very wide, never a factor.
Settled midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader, closed off well to take the victory by only a short head.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader, ran on strongly for 2nd, just beaten by a short head.
Rolled forward to take the outer fence and led by 1L, kept on strongly for 3rd in a tight finish.
Rolled forward to settle 1L behind the leader, hung out and proved difficult to ride most trip, kept on one pace to the line for 4th.
Prominent, kept on steadily to the line without threatening.
At rear throughout, unable to show any acceleration when asked.
On jumping was bumped, consequently raced back in the field, never a factor.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Began well, not pushed, hugging rail 2-back from leader. Pressed forward on straightening, took over lead passing 250m, held off late challenge.
Jumped OK, badly hampered near 1000m dropping 2-back along rail. Tracked eventual winner to 200m, switched out and finished strongly to just fail.
Jumped with field, ridden but didn't muster, dropping to rear. Held position around turn, swung wide into straight, ran on strongly under the whip.
Bumped on jumping, no pace, dropping to last before turn. Well back entering straight, taken to centre track, kept on well.
Ridden forward to find cover, bumped 1000m, then held 3-wide in midfield. Put under pressure on straightening and boxed on gamely.
Away quickly, holding rail before settling in box seat. Bumped and unbalanced top of straight, boxed on to 200m before tiring.
Taken quickly to fence but outpaced, dropping to rear. Held up top of straight, switched in and out to get run, crowded out 150m, finished off nicely.
Bumped start, pressed forward, settling one-off, two-back. Ridden to hold position turn, one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, bumped and unbalanced, bumped again 1000m. Crowded 900m, tightened 600m, checked 350m. Boxed on.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, then slowed pace. Overtaken passing 250m and faded. Had substantial amount of mucus in trachea.
Pressed forward from outside draw, settling 1L behind leader. Bumped and taken out 400m, checked 200m when giving ground. Minor wound on right hind paster.
Crowded out start, pressed forward but held wide without cover 2L from leader. Severely checked top of straight and faded. Had substantial amount of blood and mucus in trachea.
Began well, ridden forward settling 1L from leader. Shuffled back to 3rd passing 650m, rolled forward turning for home, hit front 300m and pulled clear.
Pressed forward from outside draw settling 3-back but wide, then hard ridden to take over lead passing 650m. Caught 300m out but kept on well.
Bumped start, ridden to hold rail 2-back from leader. Shuffled back around turn, held for run 400m, finished strongly when clear.
Began OK, crowded out 900m, dropping to last entering turn. Took inside run in straight and finished strongly.
Began fairly, restrained to find cover, dropping to rear. Bumped and carried wider around turn, kept on fairly in straight. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began awkwardly, ridden to hold midfield position between horses. Improved around turn, kept on well to 200m before turning one-paced.
Jumped well, ridden forward, settling in one-off position 2L from leader. Lost position around turn, lay out under pressure in straight, one-paced.
Began fairly, bumped, dropping behind midfield but difficult to settle. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced.
Began well, quickly taking box seat, tailing leader. Got shuffled back around turn, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Ridden forward from outside draw but held wide and lost position around turn. Gave ground soon after straightening.
Ridden but unable find cover and held wide behind midfield. Made some progress around turn but tired soon after straightening.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, crossing to fence 900m. Overtaken approaching 650m, gave ground quickly in straight.
Raced outside the leader, 1-1/4L behind, suited to the slow tempo, finished off nicely for the win.
Pushed forward from a wide barrier to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L through slow sectionals, kept going until 150M headed, held on for 2nd.
Travelled in midfield, 4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited to the slow pace, closed off nicely, just missed out on 2nd.
Sat in front of midfield along the rail, 2-3/4L off the pace, suited to the slow tempo, finished off one paced.
Ridden forward to get box-seat, 1-3/4L behind the leader, suited to the slow pace, couldn't keep on passing 150M.
At rear, 6-3/4L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow tempo, made steady ground down the outside Straight.
Sat towards the rear, 5-1/2L off the pace 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, made marginal ground only.
At rear, 8-1/2L behind, not suited to the slow pace, not competitive.
Sat in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 3 wide and without cover, despite suited to the slow tempo, found nothing after straightening.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, not suited to the slow tempo, not competitive.
Towards the rear along the rail, 5-1/2L off the pace, did not run on.
In midfield along the rail, 4L behind the leader, weakened after straightening.
Bounded in the air at start, ridden to make up ground, settling 4L from leader at turn. Taken wide entering straight, finished strongly down centre track to win on line.
Jumped with field, not pressed, racing in midfield between horses. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 200m, pipped on line.
Began fairly, sifted across behind horses to find cover at rear. Switched out turning for home, very wide in straight, finished strongly.
First out, not pushed, settling 3L back but 3-wide before turn. Rolled forward entering straight to look chance 200m, battled to line.
Jumped well, pressed forward 2L from leader in one-off position. Urged forward on straightening, hit front 300m, battled to 100m when flattened.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail, steadied 1200m but held on to box seat. Urged forward top of straight, inconvenienced passing 300m, boxed on.
Away nicely, rolled forward to hold rail 2-back from leader. Improved around turn, took inside run in straight, kept on fairly.
Quickly away, ridden along between horses 3L from leader. Began forward move 500m, inconvenienced 350m, kept on to 200m, then one-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, settling at rear but away from fence. Hard ridden from 900m but only one-paced.
Slow, then crowded, taken to rail behind midfield. Travelled keenly from 1200m, switched out 400m to make run but one-paced.
Reared start losing considerable ground, last on settling. Made up some ground around turn but one-paced in straight.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind horses, settling behind midfield. Dropped to last around turn, found nothing in straight.
Pressed forward from inside draw to take lead on settling, pulling 2L clear entering turn. Collared passing 300m and faded quickly. Rider reported abnormal breathing noises.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide 4L from leader. Lost position around turn, tired quickly in straight.
Restrained to a 3-wide position behind midfield, quickened to lead 250M, shifted inwards under left hand whip but continued on well to hold persistent runner-up.
Saved ground on the fence tracking leaders, steadily progressed to 2nd 150M, pushed winner to the line.
Held up 3-wide in mid-division but never far off from leader in a compact field, loomed a threat 300M, kept on steadily to the line, not pace of first 2 final stages.
3-wide no cover chasing leaders, loomed a strong chance early straight and briefly led passing 300M, kept on evenly but not finishing pace of first 2 final 200M.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, reserved in the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, brought wide 400M and stayed on moderately.
Travelled mid-division along the fence, stayed on fairly entering straight, not reach leaders.
Held up 2-wide behind mid-division, 4Ls off the pace 400M, ran on only fairly, no threat to leaders.
Prompted the pace on outside, driven out 450M, battled on at the same pace, faded mid-straight.
Led evenly, couldn't sustain run entering straight, headed inside 300M, weakened towards finish.
Not hurried early stages, eased back to rear group 5-6Ls off the pace, saved ground but couldn't find the necessary response when asked passing 400M.
Failed to muster speed, ended up on outside of rear trio, swung wide leaving 500M but found little under urge, never involved. (No Vet findings)
Settled down 2-wide in midfield 3Ls behind leader, weakened 350M, first to be beaten.
Bumped, unbalanced after start but soon in front, crossing to fence 1000m. Joined 500m, kicked ahead 350m, held off late challenge.
Bumped, unbalanced after start, eased back towards rear but 3-wide. Taken wider around turn, finished strongly down centre track to just miss.
Began well, pushed forward but wide, settling 1L behind leader. Joined leader passing 500m, kept on well to 200m, no extra final strides.
Ridden along one-back, one-off to 800m before edging forward 3-wide around turn. Looked chance 200, one-paced final strides.
Had legs off ground at start, then crowded and lost ground, dropping to rear. Made ground turn, taken wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Not pushed, settling four-back along fence. Stayed on fence around turn, took inside run in straight, boxed on steadily.
Began well, ridden along in midfield between horses but travelled keenly after 1000m. Improved around turn, got close 200m, then one-paced.
Not pressed, dropping to rear in one-off position. Stayed at rear around turn, ran on fairly in straight between horses while hanging in under pressure.
Bumped shortly after start, pressed forward, settling two-back from leader. Shuffled back around turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped well but shifted in and bumped. Ridden to hold rail inside leader before taking sit entering turn. Gave ground soon after straightening.
Began OK but no pace, dropping to rear along fence. Never in the hunt though ran past tired horses final stages.
Pressed forward from an outside draw but held 3-wide in midfield. Kept on well early in straight before tiring final 200m.
Outpaced, shifted in to rail, and last on settling. Lost touch with main field around turn and finished well back.
Quickly into stride, tailing leader in one-off position. Kept wide turning for home and gave ground quickly in straight, finishing tailed off.
Began well, but not used up early and taken to sit in midfield, 3 wide with cover. Ran strongly to the line despite a tendency to lay in, and pulled away in the last 100m.
Taken forward early to be handily placed 3-4th on the rail, trailing the leader. Ran strongly to the line, but couldn't kick with winner. Just took 2nd late.

Pushed forward to be handily placed early, 3 wide with no cover. Pressed forward from the 700m, to sit outside the early leader. Pushed to the line, but easily beaten by winner and peaked late to lose 2nd.
Dropped back early from the wide barrier to sit worse than midfield, 3 and 4 wide with limited cover. Came wider on the turn and ran strongly to the line.

Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, 3-4 wide. Near last on turn, and came very wide in the straight. Finished off strongly with the 2nd fastest last 400m, but had too much to do late.
Pushed forward from the kick to go to the lead, before slowing the tempo in the back straight. Led at the 250m, but peaked soon after and dropped out late.
Didn't kick early from the inside draw and sat midfield on the fence early. Ran on steadily in the straight, but lacked a big kick and never threatened a place.

Briefly crowded on jumping and awkward on heels early before finding a position midfield early. Checked out of run at 700m and dropped back. Took the shortcut along the rails turning for home, but didn't kick in the straight.

Began awkwardly, dropping back to last early, keen and on heels. Keen up the back straight before becoming unbalanced at 700m. Last on the turn, but ran steadily to the line and picked up some slower ones late.
Taken forward early to sit just outside the early leader in 2nd. Dropped out in the straight, and not pushed out to the line late.

Raced tight early and dropped back to his usual position towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Not suited to the slow pace in the back straight and pressed forward 800. Only fair to the line.

Pushed forward from the wide barrier, but stuck 5 wide around the first turn. Eventually sat forward of midfield, 4-5 wide with no cover. Race was run by the turn, and dropped back quickly in the straight.
OK away and found a spot around midfield, 1 off the fence. Under pressure before the turn, and dropped out quickly in the straight. Eased to the line late.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently in 2nd, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to get 2nd.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 7 lengths back at rear, angled out turning in, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line.

Began well from gate 2, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, no daylight early in straight and severely affected by the fallen HARD BALL GET, made good progress thereafter to make frame.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents)
Jumped with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Raced at tail for the majority of the race, taken wide in straight and made reasonable progress to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, positioned 1 out 1 back, same position on turn, raced tight early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced 3 wide with some cover in midfield, bumped near 700M, 4 wide with no cover on turn, kept on well until near 150M, weakened closing stages.
Began well from a wide draw, slotted in to race 3 lengths back on rail, kept to inside after straightening, no daylight until after 300M, finished off one-paced.
Average to begin, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back at rear, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off one-paced, never a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, 3 wide with cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Placing: FE
Comment: Jumped with them, raced prominently, 3 wide with no cover after 1000M, raced tight early in straight, severely checked and fell near 300M.

Broke well from the one draw, taken back just off the pace over 800 metres out, tracked leader into straight, hit the front under pressure 150 metres out.
Moderate start, soon recovered to midfield, took closer order rounding home bend and snuck up to 3rd on rails turning in, sustained progress in straight to be nearest at finish.

Moderate start, soon recovered to join the leaders, hit the front at the 800 metres gaining rails run, kicked over 1.5L clear turning for home but unable to sustain effort and headed by the winner 150 metres out.
Broke well from a wide gate, settled just over 2L off the pace in 7th, lost position coming onto home bend, made modest headway under pressure in straight.
Began well, soon dropped to last few, ran on in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled behind midfield, saved ground entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to the rear, remained well behind to straight, made steady progress after straightening but baulked for a run inside final 200 metres.
Amongst leaders, raced keenly before successfully taken back for cover after first 400 metres, found nothing from 2.5L 5th into straight.
Taken back from a poor draw, trailed the field to straight, only ran past beaten horses.
Jumped fairly from a middle gate, shared pace when very wide far side before shifted 2L back, widest runner entering straight, never recovered.
Broke well, amongst leaders 4 wide early, taken back passing the 1000 metre bend, hampered and shuffled back to just worse than midfield 600 metres out, faded further after straightening.
Broke well from the widest gate, raced wide and with leaders throughout far side, faded rapidly under pressure inside final 400 metres.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, improved along the fence, lack room 300M, closed off strongly to score.
Took rail behind the front runners, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide off the good pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain box seat, lack room 300M, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, pushed to keep up behind midfield, 2 wide, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 2-3 wide in midfield, ran on well to the line.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, hung on well until 200M emptied.
Dropped back, took rail, improved steadily 300M, dashed well 150M.
Behind midfield along the fence, ran on only fairly in straight.
Trapped 2-3 wide at back, never progressed.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, reduced 300M.
Eased back, raced very wide, never competitive.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly to hold off all the challengers by a nose in a bunched finish.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, dashed strongly to get 2nd in a bunched finish.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, closed off well for 3rd in a bunched finish.
Prominent, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on well for 4th in a bunched finish.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, held up until 150M, stormed home for 5th in a bunched finish.
Sent forward to take the fence and led at good pace, kept on steadily until 100M weakened.
Settled midfield early, moved forward gradually 700M, kept on one pace to the line.
At back, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Rolled forward to occupy a prominent spot on the fence, crowded early straight, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, kept on only fairly until weakened final 100M.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Started well, bustled at first to settle 1 off with cover fore of midfield, niggled 600m, 3 deep under pump 400m, dour progress to lead 190m, edged ahead readily.
Settled back rail near rear, ridden 360m, strong closer to 2nd 150m, fought on but always held.
Decent start, settled rail back of midfield, shifted 1 off on turn & driven into stretch, closed soundly to 3rd but well held.
Broke ok, sat midfield 1 off with cover, wide final turn, shaken up 300m, boxed on without threatening.
Broke well but outpaced & squeeze out, shuffled to behind midfield 1off, in pocket turning in, driven 210m kept on evenly.
Tardy start & taken back to 1 off near rear, bumped into 1st turn, shifted 3 deep 800m, driven wide into stretch, stayed on for minor headway.
Taken back to last, shifted 3 wide 900m, back to 1 off 700m, checked turning in when wide but in pocket, switched back & widest 210m, kept on for minor inroads.
Smart break, pushed forward from widest to press lead 1st turn, 2nd & ridden 400m, handed lead 270m, all out & headed 190m, faded out.
Held up at start, caught 3 wide no cover back of midfield, wide & driven into stretch, one-paced in tepid run home.
Broke ok & bustled to rail fore of midfield, niggled 500m, shifted 1 off & driven 400m, bumped turning in, switched out 250m, found nil & tapered.
Fast start & bustled to lead, pushed 1L clear & to rail 1150m, driven final turn, shifted out 300m, emptied & headed 270m & faded tamely.
Broke ok, rousted initially, soon parked 1 back on rail, crowded & bumped turning in, in pocket until shifted out 250m, found nil & weakened.
Tardy early, bustled & rolled wide to park 2nd outside leader 1200m, niggled 450m, hard-ridden 350m, responded to lead 210m, drew clear.
Broke fast to lead, 0.5L up & driven under pressure 350m, all out & headed 210m, boxed on to hold 2nd.
Broke well & camped handily 1 off with cover, driven turning in, progress to 3rd, boxed on to wire without threatening.
Sharp start, slotted 1 back on rail, locked in pocket into stretch, switched out & driven 160m, limited response in one-paced run home.
Smart start, taken back to 1 off near tail, niggled for progress 450m, switched off heels 300m & driven, closed centre track for solid gains.
Slow start, bustled to rail & settled near tail, advanced a spot 800m, driven into stretch, stayed on for late gains.
Sluggish start & bustled, parked rail behind midfield, hard-driven into stretch, lacked toe but stayed on dourly to wire.
Broke fast, restrained to midfield, settled 3 wide no cover midfield, advanced on outer to sit 3rd 700m, niggled 600m, under pump 380m, tapered gradually to wire.
Broke well, settled rail midfield, ridden 350m, shifted off fence, crowded 150m, one-paced in tepid stretch run.
Good start, handy when restrained 1620m to midfield 1 off with cover, niggled & edged 3 wide with cover 900m, advanced a spot 700m, under pump 600m, one-paced in run.
Broke ok, raced wide with cover behind midfield, niggled 680m, driven home turn, lacked pace & struggled in run home.
Veered left start, lit up & crossed track to main group, over-raced 3 wide with cover, settled at tail, ridden 380m, found nil.
Slotted into midfield along the rail 3-1/4L behind, taken to 2 wide around turn, found break at 150M and finished off nicely for the win.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, remained on the inner Straight after turn, kept going until headed by a strong finishing effort at 50M.
Parked outside the leader, kept challenging until the final 100M when couldn't find extra, just hung on for 3rd.
Sat towards the rear, 5-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, made nice ground to come home for 4th.
Raced prominently, 1-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hard ridden but couldn't find any in the straight.
Jumped well, ridden forward and took box-seat after deciding not to lead, lost ground around turn, finished off only one paced.
Ridden forward to sit 2L behind the leader but wide, little dash after straightening, one paced home thereafter.
Slow to begin and had to be ridden along at the rear to keep up with the field, made ground steadily in the straight.
Travelled just behind midfield, 5-1/2L off 3 wide with cover, ridden from 400M to maintain position, made marginal ground in the straight.
In midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, taken widest after turn, did not improve.
Always at the rear, never a factor.
Jumped slowly but showed good speed to settle in midfield, hampered and lost ground at around 600M, did not run on.
Began well, taken to fence 2-back from leader and settled. Switched out 300m to get clear running and finished strongly to win close home.
Away nicely and soon in box seat trailing leader. Moved up sharply turning for home, hit front 250m but run down 50m out.
Hard ridden from wide barrier, steadied 1000m to find cover but left wide from 700m. Switched wide in straight and finished off strongly.
Pressed forward but held 3-wide before easing back and getting cover 900m. Taken to rail around turn, ran on well in straight.
Began well, ridden to hold forward position, settling one-off, one-back. Kept on well to 200m before turning one-paced.
No early pace, settling behind midfield along fence. Improved around turn, switched out in straight to make run but only one-paced.
Began well, taken forward, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced under pressure.
Hard ridden from widest draw to go forward, settling 2L behind leader back stretch. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Ridden along between horses behind midfield to straight, took inside run but found little under hard riding. Lost left front plate on jumping.
Bounded in air as gates opened and lost several lengths. Trailed field to straight before running past beaten horses.
Began awkwardly, restrained and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear in one-off position. Never in the hunt.
Quickly in front and then raced keenly in the lead, pulling 3L clear around turn. Overhauled passing 250m and faded.
In 4th place 3-4Ls behind runaway leader, pushed along 450M, progressed to the lead inside 200M, driven clear and continued on well to the line.
Began only fairly, held up towards the rear 6-7Ls off the good pace, not much room early straight, closed off well when switched out 200M, got up for 2nd near line.
Began awkwardly, strode forward to sit 2nd behind runaway leader, moved up to the lead 350M, not finishing pace of winner 150M, held 2nd till late stages.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, moved into contention 300M and loomed a threat mid-straight, kept on under pressure, beaten to 4th late.
Held up in midfield along the inside, crept closer to pace 400M, kept on one paced under pressure.
Taken across behind runners, at the rear 10Ls off the pace middle stages, stayed on moderately over final 300M but always held by leaders.
In touch, on heels of weakening leader home turn, badly held up to 250M, couldn't pick up the pace thereafter.
Restrained to near the rear, well off the pace behind runaway leader early and middle stages, driven out nearing 400M but gave limited response, flattened 100M.

Went forward early but caught wide, was steadied to obtain a position behind midfield but lost cover again 900M, pushed wider home turn, kept on fairly in straight but not a bad run considering tough trip.
Not hurried early stages, got shuffled back to the rear about 8Ls off the pace from runaway leader, keeping on fairly entering straight, never a threat.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, about 6Ls behind leader making the turn, mild effort early straight, weakened 200M.
Set good pace first 800M, opened up 3Ls lead mid-stages, caught by rivals 350M, weakened rapidly in straight.

Jumped moderately but soon gained narrow advantage on rails, ceded lead passing the 1200 metres to sit one back, renewed effort to gain upper hand over 100 metres out.
Pressed on from a wide gate, gradually worked his way up to lead on rails passing the 1200 metres, fought on under pressure only to be outlasted close to home.
Taken back from a wide gate, waited with, snuck up on rails turning in, sustained progress under pressure, nearest at finish.
Ridden early, settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, did not find much room early in straight, quickened quite well inside final 200 metres.
Ridden early, settled towards the rear on rails, awkwardly placed behind runners approaching home turn and found no daylight early in straight, finished race off well.
Moderate start, soon picked up to 4th just over 2L back, settled in the similar position to straight, one-paced under pressure.
Taken back from a wide gate, waited with, switched wide entering straight, made modest headway down the centre of the track. (Lame)
Moderate start, raced keenly in forward of midfield, came under pressure to challenge entering straight but had nothing to give.
Ridden from the one gate, settled over 3L back in 5th on rails, faded under pressure shortly after straightening.
Began well from a wide gate to race handily, disputed lead entering straight but faded under pressure inside final 250 metres.
Held back in last few, raced keenly around the bend, in similar position entering straight, ran home at the one pace.
Travelled keenly behind midfield, in similar position entering straight, one-paced before fading inside final 200 metres.
Moderate start, soon picked up to just worse than midfield racing keenly at times, dropped out after straightening.

Placing: PU
Comment: Took no part.
Occupied a more prominent spot on the fence, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear and scored.
Settled just off the leaders 2 wide, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Took rail easily and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed early but not muster, at back, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Awkward away, at back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Pushed forward, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
Sent forward to cross to the outer fence, kept on strongly to score comfortably by 2-1/4Ls.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, ran home well for 2nd.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader grand side, blocked from 100M - 50M, stormed home for 3rd.
Ridden forward to share the lead grand side, kept on steadily until weakened final 200M, hung on for 4th.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, kept on one pace to the line without extra acceleration.
Settled midfield, 3Ls behind the leader middle track, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader middle track, one paced home.
Settled midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader middle track, ran on fairly.
Settled midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader grand side, never ran on.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Showed good early pace to settle in front, kept on until weakened badly final 150M.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls off the leader grand side, never ran on and was badly interfered over the concluding stages.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Settled midfield in the middle part of the track, faded quickly when asked near the course proper.
Speed to lead & bustled initially, to rail 1300m, narrow lead & shaken up 400m, kicked clear & held advantage to wire.
Tardy break, bustled up 3 wide to press lead 1200m, settled 2nd & 1 off at 1000m, niggled 750m, driven 430m, fought on but no appreciable gains on winner.
Taken back to race 3 off near rear, progress from 600m, shifted out on turn & driven, closed off centre track to nick 3rd late.
Started well, raced handy 3 deep & lost cover 1000m, close up 3rd & driven 360m, battled evenly in pursuit but all out & lost 3rd late.
Sharp break to press lead into 1st turn, raced close 3rd 1 off until settled 1 back on rail 1000m, niggled 500m, driven 400m, boxed on evenly.
Snagged back behind runners & scooted to back of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep for progress 1000m, driven wide final turn, kept on evenly.
Fast start, over-raced 1 back on rail, shuffled back 1050m & switched 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, outpaced & plugged home dourly.
Slow start & raced last pair on outer, niggled forward 650m, advanced on turn, crowded 350m, boxed on one pace.
Broke well, sat midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in, outpaced & plodded on tamely.
Good start but rousted initially, camped rail midfield, niggled 750m, checked & lost place 700m, soon under pump, found nil in weak run home.
Smart break, taken back to rail near rear, over-raced 830m, shuffled back 650m, switched out 500m & ridden, never a factor.
Good break, snagged back 1550m to race 3 deep with cover behind midfield, rowed along 1050m & pushed 4 deep no cover, shuffled back, driven 600m, widest into stretch, no impact.
Taken back from widest to race last pair on rail, last & driven 610m, found nil & finished adrift.
Slow start, camped rail back of midfield, shaken up 350m but crowded & bumped, driven 300m & quickened to lead 170m, drew clear.
Taken back at break, niggled along rail near rear, slid to last trio on turn, not clear run & shifted out 350m for progress, shaken up 240m, quickened to 2nd close home.
Early pace to dispute lead, eased back 1150m & sat 1 back on fence, shifted out 420m & driven to grinding lead 210m, all out & headed 170m, tapered.
Started well, restrained to 3 wide with cover midfield, driven into stretch, closed centre track until flattened out final 100m.
Decent break, worked up to lead 1020m & to rail, shaken up 420m & kicked on, all out & headed 210m, tapered to wire.
Broke ok & bustled forward to race midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, hard-ridden final turn, shifted out 300m, plugged on evenly.
Broke well, raced handy 1 off with cover, ridden turning in & edged out, boxed on one pace until emptied 150m & faded.
Slow start, driven forward to fore of midfield on inner, ridden into stretch, switched out 350m, outpaced & tapered in run.
Slow start, restrained & fought for head, raced rail last pair until shifted 1 off 1000m, driven wide turning in, plodded on same speed.
Broke well, snagged right back to 3 wide with cover near rear, driven wide into stretch, found little in tame run home.
Broke well, taken back to 1 off near rear, driven 400m, one-paced in tepid stretch run.
Taken back from wide gate to last pair on outer, widest & driven into stretch, struggled in run to wire.
Smart start widest & rolled to dispute lead, settled close 2nd 1 off 1000m, shaken up 530m & soon driven, emptied 280m & faded.
Tardy start, rolled forward, soon prominent, settled back fore of midfield 3 wide no cover, driven turning in but emptied & faded tamely.
Settled in midfield along the rail, 2-1/2L behind the leader, despite held up until 200M, finished off with ease without being under a whip.
Pushed forward to sit outside the leader, 3/4L off, closed off well for 2nd when under pressure from 300M.
Raced in front of midfield, 2L behind 2 wide with cover, kept going and found extra near 150M to finish 3rd.
Initially in worse than midfield, 3-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, improved slightly around turn, under pressure after straightening, finished off okay.
Jumped well and took box-seat from barrier 1, sat 1-1/4L behind, little dash in the Straight.
In worse than midfield, 4-1/2L behind the leader trapped 3-4 wide, swung widest after turn, finished off only one paced.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led by 3/4L at slow tempo, hung on until 150M when headed and emptied.
Jumped well but steadied to look for cover, then trapped wide in about midfield 2L behind, remained wide in the Straight, not competitive.
At rear, lost ground when checked and taken wide near the 900M, did not run on.
Sat in front of midfield, 2L behind however 3 wide without cover, kept going until dropped off near the 250M.
Sat towards the rear along the rail, proved difficult to settle throughout, not competitive.
Always at the back, never in contention.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear. Shifted ground and bumped 300m, switched in, finished strongly to win close home.
Began well, not pushed, settling close to outer fence behind midfield. Started forward move 500m, blocked for run until 120m, finished strongly.
Jumped with field, gradually motored forward to join leaders 400m, took clear lead 200, but run down final 50m.
Began awkwardly, steadied 700m, switched in passing 400m to move forward but had to switch out when baulked 180m, ran on well.
Began OK but outpaced and shuffled back along fence to behind midfield. Steadied 300m when making ground, kept on steadily to line.
Began awkwardly, steadied, dropped to last one away from outer fence. Switched to centre track passing 400m, finished off nicely between horses.
Checked on jumping, taken to outer fence, settling at rear. Shifted in to centre track passing 600m and ran on steadily.
Began well, pressed forward down centre track 3L from leaders. Looked chance passing 200m but flattened final 50m.
Jumped with field, ridden forward between horses 3L from leader. Steadied 500m, blocked for run till 200m when bumped, one-paced.
Quickly into stride, pressed forward along centre track to lead 800m. Joined upfront 400m, badly unbalanced 200m, faded. Rider dropped left rein 200m.
Began well, raced with leading pack to 800m before settling 2L back. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Crowded out start, pressed forward to lead before settling 2nd passing 800m. Kept on well to 200m when unbalanced, dropping back sharply. Lame right front leg.
Not much speed, taken to outer fence but towards rear. One-paced final 400m.
Began well, pressed forward between horses 2L from leader. Kept on well to 200m when crowded out and faded. Had substantial amount of mucus in trachea.
From wide barrier taken across behind runners, settled down 6Ls off the pace near the rear, confidently waited with, made a sustained run from 350M on wet slow track, got up near line.
Tracked leaders, poised to strike leaving the bend, wrestled the lead near 150M, kept on well to line only to be caught by fast finishing winner closing stages.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, pushed along home turn, stayed on moderately to get up 3d just in time, not reach top 2.
Soon crossed to the fence and tracked the pace along the inside, 4th leaving the home turn, kept on steadily to the line, never on terms with first 2.
Led as expected from draw 1, set good pace on wet-slow going, kept on well early straight, headed near 150M, faded and dropped to 5th close home.
Sat one out one back from the beginning, not quickened to challenge leaders passing 350M, kept on one pace to the finish.
Began awkwardly, 3-wide on the first turn and gradually dropped back to a rearward position, driven wide 500M but picked up only fairly, not reach contention.
Held up in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inside, gave limited response when driven out 400M, lost touch with leaders from 200M.
Eased back on jumping, in the rear group and over 7Ls off the pace in middle stages, plenty to make up 400M but not picked up pace to challenge, ran past well beaten runners only.
Not hurried early stages, dropped back to the rear over 7Ls behind leaders, didn't respond to riding passing 500M, never involved.
Caught wide no cover in midfield from draw 11, outpaced from 450M, soon beaten. (No Vet findings)
Began awkwardly, chased leaders along the 3-path and no cover throughout, on the retreat from 500M, weakened rapidly. (No Vet findings / Unacceptable Performance)
Began OK, ridden along in midfield, swung wide into straight, finished strongly to win close home.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind horses, settling three-wide at rear. Swung wide entering straight and finished strongly.
No early speed but held rail four-back from leader. Had to switch out in straight to get clear run and finished strongly.
Began well, racing with pace before losing position 800m. Rolled forward from 600m, hit front 250m, no extra when passed final stages.
Quickly in front, crossing to rail 1200m, then took sit 1100m, shuffled back to 3rd 700m. Badly held for clear running 400m to 110m, boxed on.
Began well, pressed forward, holding rail 2-back from leader. Had to switched ground in straight to get run, boxed on.
Shifted out on jumping, unbalancing jockey. Outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Switched out in straight and ran on fairly.
Pressed forward, settling 2L behind leader 800m. Rolled forward turn, became unbalanced when shifting out 300m, kept on to 150m before tiring.
Pressed forward from outside draw, taking over lead 1200m and crossing to fence. Overtaken 250m and faded.
Badly crowded on jumping, dropping to rear. Took closer order around turn but bumped and unbalanced 300m when improving, boxed on.
Began OK, ridden along between horses in midfield to 800m, lost position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Badly crowded out on jumping, dropping to last. Never in the hunt.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover 3L from leader. Kept wide around turn, gave ground quickly in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground start, dropping to rear. Last into straight and finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Cruised up from the inside draw to be well place 4th/5th on the rails, 2L behind the leaders. Still cruising at the 400m, and worked on from the 300m, pulling well clear and being eased late.
Pushed forward from the wide draw, but never got cover and stuck 3-4 wide in 3rd place. Couldn't kick with the winner in the straight. Not pushed out late when easily clear for 2nd.
OK away and cruised forward early to sit around midfield, on the rail. Plugged away until the 150m, kicking from that point and just nabbing 3rd on the line.
OK away and being pushed forward early. Lost a run 1200m and sat midfield, 1 off the fence. Bumped slightly 550m, but maintained momentum. Came out under pressure 200m, but strong to line late.
Dropped back early to be worse than midfield, 3 wide. Ran steadily in the run home, and just missed 3rd in a tight place finish.
OK away and cruised up early to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Awkward on heels and unbalanced at 550m. Ran steadily to the line, but never kicked and not pushed to the line late.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to lead early. Leading at 250m, but already fading fast. Dropped back quickly from that point.

Fairly away and dropped back early to towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Steadied off heels 550m. Dropped off side rein at the top of the straight, and ran OK to the line without ever threatening.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to challenge the leader up front, 1 off the fence. Didn't respond to riding from the 300m, and dropped back quickly from that point.

Dropped back early from the wide barrier to sit last, 10L off the leader and 2L off the 2nd last horse. Caught up to the field by 600m, and came widest down the straight. Ran steadily to the line late.
Fairly away and found a position around midfield, 1 off the fence. Didn't run on in the straight and tended to lay in, in the straight. Only went to the line fairly late. Unacceptable performance.

Dropped back from the wide draw to eventually sit 2nd last, 8L off the leader. Held up in the straight until the 200m, and looked to progress before being held up again over the last 100m and never fully tested.
Began well and taken forward to be handily placed 3rd/4th 2L off the leaders. Began to fade by the 600m, before dropping out in the straight and eased over the line late.
Pressed forward early to sit forward of midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Well positioned on the turn, but gave nothing in the straight. Dropped out quickly from the 200m.

Broke well, settled wide in midfield, fought on under pressure in straight to hit the front close to home.
Jumped fairly, settled in one-out-one-back position, fought on steadily in straight but unable to peg back winner throughout.
Ridden from the start, soon obtained lead on rails, kicked over 1L clear after straightening, unable to sustain effort and headed close home.
Broke well from a poor gate, disputed lead throughout far side, held similar position just outside the leader rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening in the run home.
Broke well, settled just better than midfield in 5th, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure in the run home.
Began from a wide gate, settled towards the rear, ran on steadily under pressure in straight.
Slowly away, soon recovered to rear of midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled one back on rails, made no impression in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Slow into stride, remained in similar position towards the rear throughout.
Taken back from the widest gate, remained in similar position well behind to straight, fought on steadily, never nearer.
Jumped fairly, gradually dropped to tail-end, detached from field from approaching home bend.
Took rail and led easily, drifted away 200M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well for 2nd.
Slow away, pushed forward to obtain box seat, just held ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, checked 750M, settled behind midfield, made some ground 200M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, held ground in straight.
Bumped start, at back, trapped 3-4 wide, little dash 200M despite negative racing situations.
Bumped start, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, no turn of foot.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, never improved.
Midfield 2 wide, dropped off steadily 600M.
Pushed early, midfield along the fence, checked 750M, reduced 250M.
Bumped start, trapped 3 wide at rear, no progress.
Never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well to score comfortably.
Eased back from a wide gate, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, switched wide turning in, and stormed home for 2nd.
Missed break, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, swung widest turning in, and dashed well for 3rd.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, ran on gradually until weakened final 50M.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led at fast sectionals, kept on until weakened final furlong.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader at fast pace, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast sectionals, made no impression in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast pace, unable to run on.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast tempo, never ran on.
Pushed forward to share the lead, however, tapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened soon after straightening.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, checked rounding the Home Turn, eased down thereafter. (substantial amount of blood in its trachea)
Restrained, shifted across behind runners, dropping to last pair. Started long forward move back stretch, circled field to lead 400m, kept finding when challenged.
Bumped start, then steadied before first turn, settling one-back, one-off. Travelled comfortably to straight, shaken up 400m but unable haul in winner.
Bumped start, pressed forward but wide, settling 6th 4L from leader. Shaken up on straightening and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Got off OK, ridden to find cover, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Switched out entering straight and ran on steadily.
Began fairly, tightened before first turn, then taken to fence. Got shuffled back around home turn, stayed on fence in straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, made use of inside draw to hold box seat, travelled keenly back stretch. Remained in contention to 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward from outside draw to lead on settling. Set steady pack back stretch but collared before entering straight. Kept on gamely until flattened 150m.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, dropping to rear. Lost ground approaching home turn, boxed on one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden from inside draw to hold rail position, two-back from leader. Hard ridden turning for home, hung in under pressure in straight, giving ground.
Quickly away, pressed forward, settling outside hind-quarters of leader. Under pressure turning for home and faded gradually. Substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Slow into stride, hampered, dropping to last but kept away from fence. Never likely.
Bumped start, outpaced, dropping to rear along fence. Never in the hunt.
Jumped well, led for a few strides before sliding into slipstream of leader. Rolled forward entering straight, hit front 250m, kept on strongly.
Quickly into stride before settling two-back along rail. Took inside run in straight but forced to switch out 100m when tightened, boxed on.
Began well, raced with leading pack to 1000m before settling in one-off position 3L from leader. Urged forward entering straight, hit front 250m, no extra final stages.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling behind midfield along rail. Shaken up entering straight and kept on steadily without threatening first three.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling at rear but wide. Taken wider around turn, wide in straight, kept on fairly.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, settling one-back, one-off but 3L from leader. Kept on fairly to 200m before turning one-paced.
Ridden early to stay close to pace before easing into one-off position 4L from leader. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Ridden forward from an outside draw and held wide behind midfield, and left without cover from 900m. One-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw, dropping to rear along fence. Made turn awkwardly and never in the hunt.
Shifted out abruptly at start, hampered, dropping behind midfield. Never likely thereafter. Jockey said hung out throughout and not properly tested. Unacceptable performance.
Began awkwardly then badly hampered, dropping to last. Never likely.
Hard ridden to lead passing 1000m, pulled 2L clear 800m travelling keenly, collared 250m and faded quickly.
Raced in midfield along the rail, 5-3/4L behind, niggled rounding turn, dashed well from 200M to score.
Raced in front of midfield, 4-1/2L off on the fence, remained on inner track, kept pushing and finished well for 2nd.
Sat behind midfield along the fence, 8-1/4L behind the leader, taken wide in the straight, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Travelled in midfield, 6L off the 2 wide with cover, ran on until 150M when weakened.
Pushed forward to lead at quick sectionals, did not show a turn of foot and headed at 150M.
Raced towards the rear along the rail, 10L off the pace, made ground steadily in the straight.
Sat behind midfield, 9L behind 2 wide with cover, made slight ground and kept pushing to the line.
In midfield, 7-1/2L behind 2-3 wide with cover, taken widest after turn, ran home only one paced.
At the rear, 10-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, made slight progress in the straight only.
Slotted into box-seat, 3-1/4L off the pace, weakened passing 200M, did not run on.
Raced in front of midfield 5L off 2 wide without cover, dropped off rounding turn, not competitive.
At the rear and gave ground rounding turn, never a factor.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, then set steady pace under tight hold. Shaken up 250m when challenged, battled strongly to hold on for narrow win.
Quickly into stride, settling 1L behind leader to turn. Shaken up to go forward from 500m, closed in steadily, just failed.
Began fairly, pushed forward, then travelled keenly from 800m. Urged forward 3-wide around turn, kept chasing in straight but unable close gap to leading pair.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling towards rear in one-off position. Well back on straightening, finished strongly between horses.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling though kept away from fence. Switched very wide in straight and finished off strongly.
Ridden to hold forward position but held 3-wide initially before settling 3L from leader. Ran on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Crowded out shortly after start before settling 2-back from leader along fence. Shifted out turning for home and ran on steadily in straight.
No early speed, settling behind midfield along fence. Momentarily held up around turn, took inside run in straight and ran on fairly.
Ridden along behind midfield early but kept wide, covering extra ground around turn. One-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, ridden along in midfield between horses, crowded for room 700m, kept on one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind horses from an outside draw, settling in last pair along fence. Never in contention.
Began well, crowded out shortly after but soon in box seat trailing leader. Under pressure turning for home and gave ground quickly in straight.
Shared lead early stages, dropped back to 4th entering 1st turn, remained in touch to straight, quickened up to lead near 200M, kept on well enough to hold off rivals.
Restrained to race at the rear, 9Ls off the pace middle stages, saved ground on the inside home turn, closed off strongly up the fence inside 300M, got up 2nd near line.
Shared lead until 1000M then sat in 3rd chasing the pace, ran on inside 300M, briefly dueled with winner mid-straight, was held over final 100M, lost 2nd late. (Lame RH.)
Slow to begin, taken to the rails and settled down 5-6Ls behind midfield, angled out 500M, stayed on moderately down outside.
Reserved in midfield along the fence, waited with till 350M, ran on one paced in straight and no serious threat to leaders.
In mid-division and settled down 3-4Ls behind leaders along the 2-path, driven out passing 500M, kept on fairly final 300M.
Always prominent, took over the lead entering back straight, led to near 200M, faded towards the line.
Taken across behind runners, reserved near the rear 7Ls off the pace, ran on mildly leaving the bend, awkwardly placed 100M and not ridden out to the end.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, 5Ls to make up leaving 400M, responded fairly under pressure early straight, awkwardly placed final 100M and not able to be ridden out to the finish.
Settled 2-wide behind midfield, in 9th 6Ls off the pace halfway, brought wide into straight, kept on same pace only.
Fractious in stalls, failed to muster speed, caught wide no cover behind field from 1400M, strode forward to track leader, no extra and gave way 250M.
Never far off the pace, couldn't sprint with them passing 400M, dropped out of contention quickly. (No Vet findings)

Moderate start, settled in last few, not much room upon straightening, obtained clear passage inside final 300 metres, ran on well to assert authority close to home. (Blood in trachea)
Handy on rails, baulked for a run until the 250 metres, quickened well to hit the front over 100 metres out only to be caught close home.
Waited with, baulked for a run upon straightening, finished off race well.
Broke well from a poor draw, travelled keenly just outside the leader, yielded ground gradually after straightening.
Ridden along 3-wide in midfield, switched wider into straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Slightly slow out, soon driven up to midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, tight between runners early in straight, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Settled well behind, did not find much room early in straight, finished off race quite well inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well from the widest gate, obtained rails run in the lead after first 250 metres, narrowly headed approaching home turn, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Soon picked up to midfield after a sluggish start, remained similar entering straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled just worse than midfield and wide without cover from a poor draw, remained similar turning for home, one-paced.
Never far off the straight, faded gradually.
Handy early, improved steadily leaving back straight to join the leader rounding home bend, held slender advantage upon straightening but soon dropped out of contention. (Lame)
Raced keenly just worse than midfield, beaten when forced to check 350 metres out.
Soon in rear, responded to early reminders to pick up on rails to rear of midfield, lost position rounding home bend but saved ground turning in, faded steadily in straight.
Midfield, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Box seat, lack room 4-2, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Settled in front, 2 wide, favoured by the slow pace, just held ground for 3rd.
Pushed to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Very slow away, at back, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Pushed early, behind midfield 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Failed to muster at back, 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
At back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Never competitive at tail.
Trapped very wide at rear, never a factor.
Sent forward to take the fence and raced behind the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, hit the front 200M, hung on to score by a neck.
Pushed forward from a wide gate, obtained a prominent spot with cover, enjoyed the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd, missed by a neck.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led at slow tempo, headed 200M, hung on for 3rd.
Taken back to rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, stormed home for 4th.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace to the line without serious threat.
Eased to midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, one paced home.
Taken back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Rolled to settle in a prominent spot along the fence, despite suited by the slow tempo, one paced until weakened 100M.
Settled midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, ran home fairly.
Bumped start, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never improved.
Raced midfield, however trapped very wide without cover throughout, never ran on.
At back, travelled ungenerously rounding the first turn, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Hard ridden early to hold midfield position away from fence. Made progress around turn, got clear passage 370m, hit front 200m, pulled clear.
Jumped OK, pressed forward between horses to settle one-back, one-off. Three wide turning for home, ground forward gradually picking up momentum final stages.
Began fairly, crowded and lost ground 1300m dropping towards rear. Made progress but wide final turn, ran on steadily in straight.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, slowed pace first bend before pulling 2L clear final turn. Caught passing 200m and faded gradually.
Quickly away, trailing leader first bend and back stretch. Looked chance top of straight but only one-paced final 200m.
Away OK, not pushed, settling between horses behind midfield. Took inside run final turn and made progress to 200m before turning one-paced.
Bumped start, bumped again 1500m and taken wider, dropping behind midfield. Hung in straight when pressed forward, shifted in abruptly 100m, one-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw but held wide at rear. Allowed to improve from 1000m, circling field to within 2L of leader passing 200m before flattened.
Slow into stride and then difficult to settle, dropping to last pair. Taken out turning for home, made some progress initially before tiring final 200m.
Slow to move, ridden but failed to improve, dropping to last back stretch. Had clear running in straight but only plodded to line.
Pressed forward from an outside draw and raced mostly 3-wide first turn and back stretch 3L from leader. Gave ground steadily in straight.
Jumped best, bumped, but pressed forward holding box seat 3L from leader first turn and back stretch. Under pressure turning for home and weakened gradually.
Hard ridden to stay close to pace, then niggled to hold position back stretch. Under pressure from 600m but did not respond. Unacceptable performance.
Bumped on jumping, ridden but didn't muster, settling close to rail behind midfield. Lost position around turn and tailed off in straight. Unacceptable performance.
Began well, ridden to hold rail inside leading pack before easing 3L back first turn. Began forward move 3-wide from 750m, hit front 300m, pulled clear final 50m.
Jumped well, not pushed, dropping two-back along fence first turn, not much room top of straight, got clear 280m, finished off strongly.
Began fairly, taken in to one-off position in midfield and switched off. Lost position back stretch, rolled forward from 700m, wide into straight, finished strongly final 200m.
Jumped with field, holding midfield position to back stretch. Got shuffled back approaching final turn, taken wide entering straight and finished strongly.
Hard ridden 3-wide to lead passing 1400m, crossing to fence 1300m and slowing pace. Under pressure 400m, joined up front 300m, gave ground gradually.
Pressed forward 4-wide from outside draw before settling 1L behind leader. Looked chance when joining leaders 300m but only one-paced final stages.
Bumped start, shifted across behind runners to rail and pressed forward 4-back 1300m when checked. Kept on steadily in straight.
Ridden to find cover but held 3-wide behind midfield and left without cover back stretch. Held wide throughout and one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from jump, settling one-back, one-off. Kept tabs on leaders, swung wide into straight, found little under pressure final stages.
Jumped OK, outpaced, dropping to rear. Switched out approaching final turn but made little headway under hard riding.
Hard ridden to hold rail, settling in box seat first turn. Took inside run in straight, kept on well to 100m before tiring. Substantial amount of mucus in trachea. Lame left hind leg.
Began OK, outpaced, dropping to last pair first turn. Clear last passing 800m, swung wide into straight, found nothing under hard riding.
Ridden along to find cover, dropping to rear in one-off position. Taken to rail back stretch, wide into straight, found nothing and eased final stages. Unacceptable performance.

Placing: PU
Comment: Began well and gradually taken to fence 3-back from leader first turn. Broke down left fetlock 1300m and eased out.
Pushed forward and parked outside the leader 3/4L behind, suited to the slow tempo, closed off well to score.
Travelled in midfield 3-1/4L off, however trapped wide, despite not suited to the slow tempo, finished off nicely for 2nd.
Pushed forward to take the rail and led through slow sectionals, headed at 100M, held on for 3rd.
Slotted into front of midfield, 2L behind 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slow tempo but finished off only one paced.
Raced in midfield, 3-3/4L off 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, couldn't find clear running until 250M, did not improve. (Questioned for choice of running in the straight)
Travelled at the rear on the rail, 6L behind the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, held up until 250M, improved only slightly.
Rolled forward and took box-seat, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader, benefited by the slow pace, did not run on.
Sat just behind midfield along the rail, 4-1/4L off the pace, not suited to the slow tempo, did not improve.
In worse than midfield, 5-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, not competitive.
Sat in front of midfield along the rail, 3L off the pace, not suited to the slow pace, dropped off significantly near 250M.
In worse than midfield, 4-3/4L 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, couldn't find any in the straight.
Always at the back, never a factor.
Pressed forward from outside draw, settling one-back, one-off. Bumped turn, started forward move 400m, hit front 200m, pulled clear.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Switched wide entering straight and finished strongly to nail 2nd place on the line.
Crowded and lost ground start, then ridden to hold one-off position in midfield. Had to shift several times in straight to get clear passage, finished off well.
Began awkwardly, raced fiercely early stages before clipping heels and blundering 800m dropping to rear. Taken wide in straight and ran on well though hampered 200m.
Inconvenienced at start, pressed on in one-off position close to pace though difficult to settle. Ran on steadily in straight though hampered passing 200m.
Hard ridden from widest draw, surging forward to lead 900m, pulling 4L clear at turn. Collared passing 200m, kept on gamely to 100m, then swamped.
First out from gates, leading to 900m before taking sit on tearaway leader. Urged forward top of straight to look a chance 200m before running out of steam.
Began well, quickly taken to rail to hold box seat. Shifted out 500m and bumped, kept on fairly in straight before tiring final stages.
Outpaced, dropping to last pair but holding rail. Stayed on fence around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Outpaced, dropping to last and trailing field to 200m before running past beaten horses.
Began OK, ridden along holding rail three-back from leader. Had clear running in straight but only one-paced.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold one-off position two-back from leader. Kept on fairly to 300m, checked 200m when tiring. Lost right hind plate near 900m.
Unhurried after the start, confidently ridden in a position behind midfield, driven out inside 400M, hit top gear mid-straight, sprinted to lead passing 100M and won going away.
Began only fairly, moved up to track leaders, held up until 300M, ran on well up the rails, briefly led near 100M but no match with winner late stages, clear 2nd best.
Soon led from draw 2, joined by rivals making the home turn, kicked 1L clear leaving 400M, headed 150M, held on for 3rd just.
Restrained in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, held up for clear run until 300M when switching back to inside, ran on steadily for 4th.
In mid-division, commenced to race keenly 950M, shifted out to 3-wide entering home turn, closed off well down the outside final 300M, narrowly missed out on a minor placing.
Niggled along to hold a forward position early stages, sat back in 6th entering turn, had every chance final 400M, loomed a threat 250M, turned one pace closing stages.
Caught 4-wide no cover in midfield, inclined to lay out making the home turn, kept on well chasing leader early straight, run peaked 150M and was out finished late stages.
Prominently early, eased back to midfield before home turn, responded only fairly in straight, never going the pace to challenge leaders.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along from the start, ended up near last 6Ls off leaders, closed off moderately over final 300M but never a serious threat to leaders.
Hard ridden to obtain a forward position, joined leader entering home turn, kept on same pace early straight, faded from 200M.
Dropped back to the rear 7Ls off the pace, brought wide 400M, ran on fairly over possibly inadequate trip and never reached contention.
Tracked leaders on jumping from draw 1, unable to keep up with rivals inside 400M, weakened rapidly.
Made early use to go forward from draw 14, sat 3-wide outside lead home turn, no extra 350M, dropped away rapidly.
Switched off to the rear 7Ls behind leaders, gave no response and got left behind 350M, tailed off.
Began well, racing with pacemakers before being eased to sit one-off, two back first turn. Moved forward passing 700m, hit front 250m, kept finding when challenged.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling midfield along fence. Lost position back stretch, got clear rails run in straight, shot to the front 300m, joined 250m, battled to line.
Began well but eased, slipping towards rear between horses. Had to be niggled at when pace slowed 1200m, shifted twice in straight to get clear run, finished well.
Snagged back soon after start but unable to find cover settling wide at rear. Rolled forward but wide back stretch, 4-wide final turn, kept on well in straight.
Bumped start and then crowded for room, dropping to rear. Last turning for home, switched wide entering straight, ran on nicely.
Ridden to hold fence 2-back from leader entering back stretch. Lost position around final turn but stayed on fence and kept on steadily in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, not pushed, settling between horses behind midfield. Switched out turn to make run but only one-paced in straight.
Got off well but restrained, dropped to rear in one-off position. Made up some ground final turn but only one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward to share lead first turn before easing back to 4th passing 1550m. Rolled forward 3-wide final turn, joint leader 400m, collared 300m, faded.
Slow then outpaced, dropping to rear close to fence. Made up some ground early in straight before running out of stamina and fading.
Jumped well, pressed forward 5-wide to first turn, led into back stretch before being passed and holding box seat. Tired soon after straightening.
Pressed forward on jumping but travelled keenly outside leader around first turn and back stretch. Hit front 400m but soon under pressure and faded.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling 3-wide behind leading trio back stretch. Kept wide and lost position final turn. No extra in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced start, rolled forward 5-wide first turn before taking lead 1550m. Crossed to fence 1300m and slowed pace. Caught 400m out and faded.

Pushed forward from the wide draw to eventually settle in 2nd, 1L behind the leader. Grabbed a share of the lead by 300m, but was challenged all the way down the straight, only clearing out in the last 75m.
Pushed forward early to set the tempo up front. Challenged for the lead at 300m, but kicked and worked down the straight. Came to the end of his run over the last 75m, still holding 2nd late.

Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field, 3 wide with cover. 2nd last at the 400m, before coming wider in the straight. Ran strongly in the straight with the fastest last 400m, and closing in quickly and the first 2.
Steadied back early from the wide draw to sit midfield, 3 wide with cover. Ran on well early in the straight, but couldn't get to first 2. Ran flat late, but holding 4th.

OK away finding an early position midfield. Became unsettled at 1300m, checking off heels before bumping and unbalanced at 1200m. No run in the straight until reefing off heels at 200m, closing quickly when clear.
OK away, but didn't settle and initially midfield before dropping back towards the rear of the field. Awkward on heels 1000m, before racing tight 700m. Ran on steadily in the straight.
Pressed forward early before dropping back and sitting better than midfield, 3 wide with no cover. Kicked initially in the straight, before running flat from the 250m and fading back.
Took time to settle before finally finding a position 1 off the fence in midfield at the 1200m. Only ran fairly in the straight, and dropped out late.

Slowly away and dropped back early to sit last, on the rails. Held up behind runners when looking for a run early in the straight, only getting clear after the 200m. Ran home fairly, but not pushed out late.
Not used up from the inside draw to sit midfield, on the fence. Held the rail, but only dawdled home 1 paced in the straight.

Fairly away dropping back to be worse than midfield, on the rail. Awkward on heels 1500m. Came wider early in the straight looking for a run, before awkward on heels 250m and switching back to rail. Eased to line.
Taken forward early to sit 4th, 2.5L off the leader. Ran flat in the straight, and eased out late.
Pushed forward to lead early before being crossed at 1200m, and sitting 3rd with cover. Under pressure on the turn, and faded in the straight before easing out late.
Dropped back early to sit at the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Never showed any sign of running on in the straight, and eased out when well beaten in the straight.
