Settled in 3rd just off the leading pairs, commenced move coming onto course proper, hit the front over 200 metres out, won readily.
Settled just inside the narrow leader near stands rails, came under pressure to challenge passing the 200 metres, failed to quicken to threaten.
Soon took up running on stands rails holding a narrow advantage, unable to sustain effort and faded inside final 200 metres.
Made no show.
Soon outpaced.
Pushed to take rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well to score.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 350M for 2nd.
Slow away, hard ridden at back, favoured by the fast tempo, blocked 4-2, made good ground when clear.
Slow away, hard ridden at back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
At back on the rails, suited by the fast tempo, held up 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up at rear, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Behind midfield 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 300M, on heels 200M, ran on ok.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide no cover, harmed by the fast pace, flattened 300M, hampered 200M.
Pressed forward along the fence, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, on heels 500M, emptied 200M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, reduced quickly 300M.
At rear, never improved.
Trapped 3-4 wide behind midfield, never a factor.
Trapped 4 wide throughout, never competitive at rear.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, travelled 4Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed strongly to score when clear 200M.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, finished off well for 2nd.
Taken back from a wide gate, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well for 3rd when clear 200M.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung widest turning in, made plenty of ground to finish 4th.
Sent forward to take the lead along the fence, kept on until headed 150M.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
Missed break, then rolled forward to obtain the box seat, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, settled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on until 300M faded.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, emptied 250M.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never ran on.
Hard ridden forward to settle in a prominent position, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, dropped off soon after straightening,
Smart start, bustled to front rank & found rail, narrow lead 800m, shaken up 420m, tight duel & headed 200m, rallied to lead 120m, drew ahead.
Led at break, headed 1000m & raced in leading trio 1 off no cover, head 2nd & driven 420m, edged lead 200m, headed 120m & no extra.
Taken behind from widest gate to race at tail, progress from 550m, checked out 400m & driven, closed through field to nick 3rd at wire.
Broke ok, raced 1 back on rail, ridden turning in, boxed on to 3rd 120m, tapered & edged out of frame last stride.
Prominent at break, taken back & niggled 3 wide with cover midfield, wider progress 550m & ridden, 5 deep turning in, boxed on evenly.
Broke ok, settled 1 back 1 off, shaken up 400m & switched out to go 3rd 350m, emptied 150m & tapered.
Moderate start, sat 3 wide with cover midfield, shuffled back 800m, soon 3rd last under pump, driven into stretch, stayed on for solid headway.
Slow start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, shifted out & driven centre track, tepid run home.
Moderate start, pushed on to handy 3 wide with cover, switched 4 deep home turn & driven, one-paced, emptied 150m & faded.
Broke ok, raced rail midfield, shifted out turning in, driven 350m, outpaced & plodded home tamely.
Broke well, bustled initially to lead 1000m, raced 3 wide no cover & headed 800m, 0.5L 3rd & driven 500m, soon emptied & faded.
Lacked pace, raced 2nd last on fence, to tail 550m, driven into stretch, found nil & eased when no extra 300m.
Broke with others, camped rail fore of midfield, shifted out & niggled for progress 520m, 4L back & shaken up 400m, gradual advance to lead 80m, kept on to line.
Slow start, raced 2 wide with cover last pair, shifted 3 deep & niggled for progress 550m, 9L back centre track & driven 400m, rattled home to nick 2nd at wire.
Broke ok, settled midfield 1 off with cover, progress to 4th 750m, niggled 500m, closed strongly to lead 250m & driven, all out & headed 80m, tapered.
Broke well, settled back near rear 1 off, 7.5L back & ridden into stretch, shifted out for progress, closed centre track for solid gains.
Sharp start, raced 3rd 1 off with cover, led chasing pack 3L back of lead, niggled 550m, driven 400m, shifted out 300m, boxed on one pace.
Started well, rousted initially to race back of midfield 1 off with cover, bustled 500m, hard-ridden into stretch, stayed on for dour minor inroads.
Taken back at start, raced 3 wide with cover back of midfield, niggled 550m, widest into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Taken behind at break to rail near rear, off heels 890m, under pump final turn, boxed on evenly, shifted out 200m, stayed on to line.
Broke with others, bustled initially to settle rail back of midfield, over-raced 900m, edged out & driven turning in, plugged on one pace.
Fast start & shared early lead, snagged rail & settled 4th, shifted out & driven turning in, not clear run 300m & checked inside, clear 200m, one-paced.
Fast break to share lead, crossed to rail 1200m, outright lead 1000m & soon 3L clear of pack, pressed & driven 420m, all out & headed 250m, faded tamely.
Sharp break & immediately restrained to tail, rousted a touch 1250m, off heels 880m & niggled a long, outpaced &driven into stretch, plodded on past beaten rivals.
Broke ok, restrained to fore of midfield but trapped 3 wide no cover, niggled 650m, unable to hold spot under drive 500m, emptied turning in & faded tamely.
Started ok, bustled forward to share lead on outer, settled close 2nd 1000m & daylight to 3rd, pressed lead & shaken up 420m, emptied 350m & dropped out quickly.
Sent forward to lead from barrier 1, raced centre track, pushed to the line and scored by a short head.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/2L behind on the middle track, responded well when asked at 400M, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Raced handy on the outer fence, 2-1/4L off the pace, kept going and finished off well for 3rd.
Travelled in midfield, 3-1/4L behind grand side, ran home okay to finish 4th.
Raced slightly in front of midfield, 3L off grand side, kept on one paced to the line.
In behind midfield, 4-1/4L behind the leader grand side, held up until 250M, improved slightly thereafter.
Settled in worse than midfield, 4-3/4L off on centre track, made slight ground only.
Raced behind midfield along the outer fence, 4-1/4L behind the leader, did not improve.
At rear, 8L off the pace initially along the outer rail, passed tiring runners inside the final 150M only.
Travelled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind on the centre track, couldn't find extra to run on near 300M.
Towards the rear on the middle track, 7-1/2L off the pace, not competitive.
Raced behind midfield along the outer rail, 4-1/2L behind, did not run on.
Always at the rear, not a factor.
Pushed forward to race prominently, 1-1/2L grand side, weakened badly passing 300M.
Hard ridden early to hold rail two-back from leader then switched off 800m. Had to shift twice in straight to get run before fishing strongly under hands and heel riding.
Pressed forward to lead from wide draw, crossing to fence 1000m. Caught passing 200m but fought back gamely to hold second.
Hard ridden from widest draw to sit second, 2L behind leader at turn. Rolled forward on straightening, hit front 200m, run ended close to line.
Ridden forward, settling one-back, one-off. Moved forward 3-wide turning for home to look a chance 200m, one-paced final stages.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling between horses behind midfield. Switched out entering straight to make run and finished off fairly.
Ridden early to hold forward position but got close to heels 1000m, settling one-off, two back. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Shifted in shortly after start but unable to find cover at held 3-wide at rear. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Began well, pressed forward, holding box seat. Got shuffled back around turn, stayed on fence but only one-paced in straight.
Got off with field, shifted in but unable find cover and held three-wide in midfield without cover. Covered extra ground around turn, one-paced in straight.
Outpaced early and held wide without cover at the rear. Found nothing when put under pressure in straight.
Began OK, taken to fence but outpaced, dropping towards rear. Shaken up top of straight but found nothing.
Bumped inside of gate at start losing ground and then trailed field throughout. Never in the hunt.

Caught wide on jumping from 14, strolled forward to track leader entering home turn, took over 350M, kept finding in the lead under 10 lb claimer, fought off nearest challenger inside 100M, continued on well to line.
Reserved along the fence, settled down 3Ls off the pace ahead of midfield, came through to challenge winner 250M but always held, faded late stages.
Began awkwardly, failed to muster speed, detached from the field 10Ls off the pace, brought wide 450M, closed off strongly outside, almost claimed 2nd at the finish.
Pushed forward early, stopped pursuing for the lead after 1500M, sat behind leaders 3-wide without cover, fought on steadily in straight but always held by leader. (Jockey questioned re tactics.)
Settled down in 11th place about 5Ls off the pace middle stages, difficult obtain run early straight, stayed on moderately over final 300M.
Prominent from the start, tracked leaders in 3rd making the turn, had every chance entering straight, kept up with the pursue until 150M when flattened.
Restrained in mid-division along the 2-path, into clear inside 400M, ran on well to 150M but couldn't sustain run late stages. (Lame LF leg)
Began awkwardly, sat behind midfield 5Ls off the pace along the rails, kept on same pace final 350M and made little impression on debut.
Urged along on jumping from wide barrier, crossed to the lead before home turn, soon tackled by rival leaving the bend, fought on briefly then gave way 250M.
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, 6Ls off the pace middle stages, responded well early straight but run ended passing 200M. (No Vet findings)
Dropped back to near the rear 7-8Ls off the pace, brought wide 500M, made limited progress down the outside lane, well held by leaders final 200M.
Caught 4-wide in midfield, lost cover entering home turn, kept on same pace early straight, no extra inside 200M. (Lost right front plate)
Up with early pace, sat 2Ls behind leader making home turn but failed to keep up with rivals passing 450M, soon weakened entering straight.
Held up 3-wide in mid-division, gave no response when driven along nearing top of straight, soon out of contention, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable performance)
Restrained on jumping, taken to fence, then switched off 1400m. Switched out 600m, switched in 250m to get run, finished strongly to win close home.
Rolled forward from an outside draw to lead on settling. Harassed by another around turn, kicked ahead on straightening, run down close to line.
Outpaced, settling towards rear but wide. Well back entering straight, switched to centre track and finished strongly while hanging in under pressure final 200m.
Began well, rolled forward stalking leader before shuffled back to 3rd passing 1000m. Urged forward on straightening, hit front 200m, no extra close home.
Jumped with field, then taken to fence 2-back from leader. Switched out turning for home, made ground to 200m, one-paced final stages.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling towards rear away from fence. Taken wide in straight and ran on steadily.
Ridden early to hold rail, settling four-back from leader. Came off fence turning for home and battled on gamely under hard riding in straight.
Bumped start, pressed forward, grabbing box seat. Lost position turning for home, stayed on rail, one-paced.
Jumped well, travelled keenly from 1500m when unable find cover. Allowed to roll forward to eyeball leader 1000m. Kept on to 200m before tiring.
Shifted across behind runners from widest draw and last on settling. Ran past beaten horses in the straight.
Began well, ridden forward but kept wide in midfield without cover from 900m. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Bumped start, pressed forward, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Turned wide, gave ground steadily from 300m.

Slightly bumped on jumping before easing forward to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wide down the straight for clear running. Ran strongly late, and stuck the nose in front right on the line to win in the tightest of finishes.

Began OK and settled midfield, 3 wide with limited cover before being forced wider at the 800m with no cover. Kicked from 150m, but lay in late and forced to put the whip away, losing by the barest margin on the line.

Cruised forward from the inside gate to be handily place 4th/5th, 2L off the leader on the rail. Ran well in the straight and stepped up from the 150m. Nosed in front at 30m, before being rolled late.

Bumped on jumping before being steadily taken forward to sit 3rd, 3 wide with no cover. 2nd at the 200m, and best placed to take on the weakening leader, but swamped late in a tight finish to miss a place.
Taken forward early to set the tempo in front. Still in front at the 30m, but weakening and was swamped late in a big finish.
Pushed forward early from the wide draw to sit a 0.5L behind the leader, 1 off the fence. Well placed at the 150m, but peaked soon after and dropped out of the tight finish.
Fairly away, then steadied and taken back to be 3rd last, 1 off the fence. Improved to the turn and ran on steadily in the straight, without threatening a place.
Settled forward of midfield, on the rail. Plugged on OK late, and held up slightly concluding.
Allowed to press forward early to sit 4th, 1 off the fence. Awkward on heels at 900m and lost some ground. Ran OK early in the straight and well placed at 200m, before dropping out from that point.

Taken back early to sit worse than midfield, on the rails. Moved from a rails run to 5 wide in the straight. Crowded at 300m and taken wider from there looking for a run. Ran on OK, but never a threat to place.
Dropped back early to sit 2nd last, 1 off the fence 7L off the leader. Stayed on OK in the straight, and still gaining some ground late.
Slow to begin and only fairly into stride, sitting last early almost 10L off the leader. Still trailing on the turn and only fair in the straight, picking up a couple easing out late.
Began well and pushed up to sit just behind the early leader, on the rail. Became unsettled and had to check off heels 900m. Under pressure before the turn, and dropped out quickly from the 300m.
OK away, dropping back early to be worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, but never responded to urging and was eased up a long way from home.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 to 3 lengths back in midfield, carried wider turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to score with something in hand.
Jumped with them, positioned a length the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, kicked clear 300M, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in 5th, same position on turn, angled out near 500M, finished off well to get 3rd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back in 8th, angled out turning in, no daylight early in straight, made reasonable progress when clear to make frame without threatening the first few.
Began fairly away from gate 13, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover, 4 lengths back, still no cover on turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, peaked early in straight and headed near 300M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 4 wide with cover at rear, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back at rear, same position turning, taken widest in straight and finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, travelled wide with no cover throughout, peaked after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle near 800M, angled out turning in, finished off one-paced.
Slowly away, recovered to race 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race prominently, bumped near 1000M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight and weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced 4 to 5 lengths back at rear, difficult to settle near 800M, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Fairly away from gate 1, raced 5 to 6 lengths back at rear, last turning in, eased early in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Jumped best from a wide gate to lead early stages, settled for 2-wide position outside the leader from the Rock, asserted authority under pressure 150 metres out.
Never far off mainly in 5th within 3L of pace on rails, made steady progress without threatening from a similar position into straight.
Broke well, amongst leaders early before settling in 3rd just off the pace, fought on steadily in straight but never threatening.
Taken back to 10th towards the rear from a wide gate, finished off race well, nice run.
In rear of midfield to straight, came under pressure turning in, made up good ground under pressure down the centre of the track.
Began well from a wide-ish draw, settled one-out-one-back just over 2L back, one-paced without quickening in straight.
Used the low draw to gain narrow advantage on rails after a moderate start, held lead to the 150 metres, folded up quickly. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in forward of midfield, forced to switch inside for a run upon straightening, ran home one-paced.
Raced wide without cover in midfield, remained similar to straight, ran home one-paced.
Lacked early pace, settled at the back, only ran past well-beaten horses.
Jumped fairly, settled just worse than midfield on rails, soon faded in straight.
Soon dropped to the rear, made no show.
Eased to sit just off the leader 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leaders, 2 wide, just held ground in final furlong.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early but not muster, took rail in midfield, little dash 250M.
Eased back, 2 wide, ran on ok in final stages.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, on heels early, raced greenly, dashed well 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, but trapped 2-3 wide, lack turn of foot.
Raced 3 wide throughout in midfield, emptied 300M.
Eased to rear, 2-3 wide, never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slightly fast sectionals, dashed well to score by 1L.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slightly fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slightly fast tempo, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased to rear from a wide gate, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the slightly fast tempo, closed to the line well for 4th.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slightly fast sectionals, ran on nicely.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, harmed by the slightly fast tempo, blocked early straight, found the line only fairly when clear 200M.
Taken back from a wide gate, 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly fast tempo, made some ground over the latter stages.
Pushed to settle midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slightly fast tempo, never ran on.
Hard ridden along to park outside the leader at slightly fast tempo, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Failed to muster speed despite hard ridden along in the early stages, 5Ls off the leader, never a factor.
Camped handy, harmed by the slightly fast sectionals, emptied soon after straightening.
Pushed forward to take the fence and share the lead at slightly fast tempo, weakened soon after straightening.
Not pushed, settling towards rear in one-off position. Urged forward 750m, swung wide into straight, finished strongly to win close home. Rider fined for excessive use of whip.
Bumped start, pressed forward in one-off position, 2-back from leader. Put under pressure 700m, four-wide into straight, rolled forward to share lead 150m, run down.
Bumped and unbalanced start, pressed forward first turn, settling 1L behind leader. Dropped back to 3rd final turn, rolled forward on straightening to share lead 150m, run down.
Began fairly, ridden forward, settling two-back from leader back stretch. Rolled forward entering straight to look a chance 200m, no extra final stages.
Outpaced and last on settling. Began forward move final turn, hampered 350m, taken to centre track and finished off nicely.
Hard ridden early but slow to muster, settling along rail behind midfield. Lost position around final turn but ran on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide to take lead before first turn. Set good pace until collared 150m and faded.
Allowed own pace from jump, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Turned a little wide but only one-paced in straight.
Pushed early to stay with pace but overraced and allowed to improve to sit outside leader approaching final turn. Kept tabs to 200m before tiring. Small laceration right hind leg.
Ridden to stay close to early pace but left wide without cover from 1200m. Kept on fairly in straight before tiring final 200m.
Pressed forward from wide draw, crossing to fence first turn and taking box seat back stretch. Kept on fairly to 200m before fading.
Outpaced, dropping to last-but-one along rail back stretch. Dropped to last around final turn, found nothing in straight under hard riding.
Jumped with field, shifted across behind runners to rail at rear. Started forward move 450m, taken to centre track on straightening, powered home for easy win.
Got off well, taken to rail, settling 3-back entering back stretch. Got inside run in straight, hit front 150m, unable match winner final strides.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Trailed field to 200m before finishing off well final stages.
Began well, pressed forward to hold one-back, one-off position. Looked chance 200m when urged forward but only one-paced final stages.
Ridden early to hold rail, settling in box seat back stretch. Rolled forward entering straight but only one-paced final 200m.
Bumped start, pressed forward to lead on settling despite jumping shadow 1400m. Kicked clear entering straight but ran out of stamina 150m and faded.
Outpaced early, settling at rear in one-off position. Swung wide into straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Pressed forward from outside draw to race outside hind quarters of leader along back stretch. Left flat-footed top of straight and faded.
Ridden to get forward position settling 2-back but 6L from leader. Kept on fairly in straight but blocked for run 50m and not properly tested.
Slow into stride, not pushed, settling along rail towards the rear. Put under pressure entering straight but found nothing.
Ridden along 4-wide to hold forward position before settling in one-off positon 4L from leader back stretch. Kept on fairly to straight before tiring.
Aggressively ridden but slow to muster and left wide from 1200m, 6L from leader. Tired quickly in straight and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, boxed-in until shifted out to get clear running at 250M, ran on strongly to score.
Ridden forward to take the rail and led by 1L, headed just passing 100M, finished off nicely for 2nd.
Held back just as its last start, settled in midfield 5-1/2L off 3 wide with cover, closed off well and just got ahead for 3rd.
Travelled in midfield, 4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, no dash but ran on okay for 4th.
Remained prominent from barrier 12, 1-1/2L off the pace, however finished off only one paced.
Parked outside the leader throughout, bumped at 250M, ran on till 150M when couldn't find extra.
Fractious in the barriers before being reloaded, raced in midfield along the rail, 3L behind the leader, slight dash early only.
At rear throughout, 10L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, improved slightly only.
Rolled forward to sit in front of midfield, 3L off the pace 3 wide with cover, dropped off rounding turn, not competitive.
Raced towards the rear along the rail, 6-1/4L behind, did not threaten.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, never competitive.
At rear throughout, never in contention.
Ridden to find cover, settling in one-off position four-back from leader. Began run 500m, taken to centre track on straightening, finished strongly to win close home.
Hard-ridden to hold fence 3L from leader. Closed in turning for home, came off fence 250m to pass tiring runner but caught close to the line.
Jumped well, hard ridden to hold fence inside pacemakers, gradually working to the front passing 600m. Kicked ahead entering straight but swamped final 50m.
Jumped with field but outpaced, settling behind midfield along rail. Improved turning for home but no clear run up the straight and not properly tested concluding stages.
Pushed along three-wide from jump, racing outside leader before eased back to 3rd 600m but without cover. Kept on gamely to 100m before flattened.
Hard ridden to lead soon after jump but passed by another 600m taking the sit. Put under pressure turning for home, kept on well to 100 before tiring.
Began well, restrained, shifted across behind runners, settling in one-off position towards rear. Switched out entering straight and ran on fairly.
Ridden didn't muster, dropping back last but one. Put under pressure on straightening, switched out abruptly 200m to get run, kept on fairly.
Bumped start, pressed forward 4-wide outside pacemakers, but eased to 4th 800m. Bumped, unbalanced and taken wider 550m, widest into straight, one-paced.
Slow into stride and distant last on settling. Trailed field to straight before running past beaten horses.
Quickly out, sharing early pace before settling 5th, 2L from leader at 800m. Found little in straight and gave ground quickly. Irregular heart rhythm, substantial amount of mucus in trachea.
Jumped OK, rolled forward but hard to settle passing 600m. Shifted out 550m, still hard to settle and eased down, finishing tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Settled down in 4th never far off from leaders, quickened to lead 150M and drew clear towards the finish.
In 5th place 3-4Ls behind leaders, saved ground along the fence but badly held up on straightening until 150M, ran on mildly when clear but not making headway on winner.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, 5Ls off the pace in middle stages, stayed on to chase winner over final 300M but always held, beaten to 3rd narrowly near line.
Forwardly placed in 2nd, shaken up nearing top of straight, briefly led 200M, turned one pace final stages and lost 2 placings inside 50M.
Began awkwardly from wide barrier, soon taken across behind runners, last of 10 6-7Ls off the pace, finished off moderately final 300M.
Reserved near the rear, waited with till 400M, kept on without seriously threatening.
Towards the rear along the 3-path, 5-6Ls behind leader middle stages, brought widest to straight, stayed on without threat.
Tracked the pace in 3rd, improved along the fence to join leader 350M, fought on till no extra 150M.
Used early to find the lead, took them along at steady tempo, headed 250M, weakened towards the line.
Caught 4-wide early, improved to a 3-wide spot entering back straight but remained without cover, didn't respond to urging 400M, first to be beaten.
Began well, ridden to hold rail, settling in box seat 3L from leader back stretch. Left fence 400m, rolled forward to lead passing 100m, held off late challenges.
Began well, not pushed, dropping back to be last on settling. Trailed field to straight, took rails run, blocked momentarily 150m, finished strongly when clear.
Bumped start, restrained, shifted across to one-off position towards rear. Got inside run in straight, bumped and unbalanced 250m, finished strongly.
Jumped OK, ridden between horses, settling midfield 4L from leader. Switched out in straight and finished well down centre track.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, set steady pace to straight, kicked ahead 350m, run down in shadows of the post.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward 4-wide behind pace 1200m. Rolled forward to sit outside leader 950m, boxed on well but not ridden out final stages when close to heels.
Got off OK, taken to rail 3-back from leader. Swung wide into straight, kept on well under hard riding to be closest at finish.
Shifted across from wide draw to fence towards the rear soon after start. Took inside run in straight and kept on fairly until tiring final 150m.
Ridden along behind midfield but kept three-wide mostly. Took run between horses in the straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward, racing with pace before being eased to 4th back stretch. Put under pressure turning for home but found little and faded.
Hard-ridden to share early lead before eased back to 3rd back stretch. Lost position around turn and faded in straight.
Blundered start, pressed forward but wide 2L from leader 1400m. Left wide without cover 1000m, gradually dropping back. Finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.

Broke well, settled just over 2L back in 4th on rails before gaining 3rd approaching home bend, commenced move soon after straightening and gained upper hand about 100 metres out.

Settled in forward of midfield on rails, took closer order coming onto home bend, shared 4th entering straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish. (Jockey lost whip passing the 100 metres)
Soon took up running on rails attempting to make all but only to be overhauled inside the final 100 metres.
Ridden early before settling in forward of midfield, commenced move on top of home bend and making steady headway down the straight until finding no extra inside final 100 metres.
Worked his way across from a wide gate before settling in 1.5L 3rd, drifted back to 4th over 2L back around home bend, one-paced before fading gradually inside final 200 metres.
Settled well back, snuck up on rails turning in, kept on same pace without quickening from midfield into straight.
Never better than midfield, came under pressure early in home bend but could only run home at the one pace.
Began from the widest gate, settled for rear of field position out wide before dropping to tail-end halfway out, produced late impression running past beaten horses in the straight. (Lame)
Began from a wide-ish draw, settled wide behind midfield, made no impression in straight.
Jumped fairly but soon dropped to worse than midfield, gave further ground from a similar position into straight.
Pressed on from a wide gate, circled the field around stables bend to gain to 1L 2nd turning into back straight, held similar position to top of home straight, dropped out tamely.
Settled well back from a wide gate, never a factor.
Began awkwardly losing ground, remained in last few throughout.
Began fairly settling 3-wide in midfield, gave ground rapidly from approaching home turn.
Eased to rear, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased back, along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Eased early, raced keen, moved forward 1000M, led 400M, overhauled 150M, ran on for 3rd.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, made some ground 200M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Soon after the start ridden along to the outer fence, led all the way and scored by 1-3/4Ls.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader grand stand, ran on gradually for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader in the middle part of the track, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Sent forward to race outside the leader, kept on one pace to the line without any extra acceleration.
Raced midfield, travelled 3ls behind the leader grand stand, ran on steadily.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader in the middle part of the track, kept on one pace until weakened final furlong.
Showed good early pace as usual along the outer fence early, eased to settle 2L behind the leader mid stages, crowded 300M, kept on one pace to the line thereafter.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, ran on fairly.
Niggled along in the middle part of the track, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader in the middle part of the track, one paced home.
Sent forward to settle 1L behind the leader, found nothing when asked, dropped off 250M.
At rear throughout, never looked competitive.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Failed to muster in the early stages, never looked likely.
Pushed to lead on settling, then set steady pace to straight. Put under pressure from 400m but kept finding more for narrow win.
Jumped OK, ridden forward but didn't settle until turn when two-back and one-off. Checked approaching 700m, had clear run in straight and ran on strongly.
Began well, restrained, shifted across behind runners dropping to rear. Hampered and taken wider 720m, swung wide and finished strongly down centre track.
Began well, then ridden to hold fence two back from leader. Stayed on rail up the straight and ran on steadily to just miss a placing.
Pressed forward but wide before settling 1L behind leader in one-off position. Looked a chance when urged forward top of straight but swamped final stages.
Jumped with field, taken to box seat and kept tabs on leader to straight. Shaken up 450m, kept on well till swamped last few strides.
Steadied soon after jump and taken to fence in last place. Made ground along rail around turn, kept on steadily in straight to be closest at the finish.
Began well, ridden to find cover but held wide, slipping behind midfield. Put under pressure final 300m but only one-paced.
Began well, not pushed, dropping to behind midfield. Severely checked approaching 700m, taken wide entering straight, boxed on one-paced.
Bounded in the air at start, ridden forward but wide, badly hampered approaching 700m and taken wide. One paced in straight while hanging in.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping towards rear but wide. Hampered approaching 700m, found nothing in straight under hard riding.
Pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off. Took turn a little wide, started to give ground soon after straightening.
Began fairly, pressed forward, making ground along rail to be two-back at turn, Blocked for run in straight until 280m, then gradually overhauled leader for narrow win.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling. Set good pace to straight, kicked ahead 400m but run down close to the line.
Began OK but beaten for early speed, dropping to rear. Checked passing 880m, stayed on rail around turn, kept on solidly in straight.
Pressed forward three-wide before taking sit behind leading pair entering turn. Wide into straight, boxed on steadily without looking dangerous.
Pushed to go forward, settling outside leader back stretch. Shaken up top of straight and kept on gamely to 200m before flattened.
Began well but unable handle early pace, dropping back to behind midfield. Taken to centre track on straitening and ran home steadily.
Ridden early but unable hold position dropping to midfield. Took closer order around turn, but one-paced in straight. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began awkwardly, crowded out and lost ground, dropping to last. Switched out turning for home, ran on fairly to 200m before finishing one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, dropping towards rear. Shuffled back to last turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Shifted in soon after start but held 4-wide at rear. Pushed forward 3-wide around turn to get within range of leaders at 400m before tiring.
Ridden forward from a wide, settling 4L from leader but wide. Ran very wide passing 500m and bumped another, faded quickly in straight.
Pushed forward from an outside draw to get ideal position behind leading pair back stretch. Lost position around turn and faded in straight.
Settled in midfield along the rail, 3-1/4L behind the leader, nice dash after 300M and scored impressively by 3-1/4L.
Sat outside the leader, 1-1/4L off, ran on to the line, beaten by an impressive winner only.
Raced midfield, 4L behind 2 wide with cover, held up until 250M, ran on well thereafter.
Ridden forward and sat box-seat, 1-1/2L off, directed out slightly near 250M, kept on okay for 4th.
Settled in midfield, 4L behind 3 wide with cover, slight dash near 350M before finishing off one pace.
Taken back to obtain cover from a wide barrier, 5-1/4L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, improved steadily in the straight.
Slow to jump, raced toward the rear 5-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, steadied when crowded passing 300M, dashed slightly thereafter.
Raced in behind midfield along the rail, 4-3/4L off, finished off only one pace.
Settled in front of midfield, 2-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, not fully tested until 300M when held up, little response when asked.
Initially in midfield but stayed 4 wide, near 800M was then allowed to improve slightly to race 3 wide without cover, found no extra near 300M and eased down.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 4-1/2L but 4 wide with cover, dropped off soon after straightening.
Punched forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, kept on until 350M weakened.
At rear, niggled at 800M to keep up, never a factor.
Began well, racing with leaders but wide before eased back to midfield with cover 1500m. Pressed forward from 400m, joint-leader 100m, just made it after nose-to-nose finish.
Began fairly, pressed forward to hold one-off position three-back from leader. Improved position 1200m, swung wide into straight, hit front 300m, battled gamely only to be nosed out.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind runners, settling four-back, one-off. Improved position around turn, taken to centre track in straight and finished off nicely.
Ridden forward to settle behind leader in one-off position. Got cover passing 1100m, rolled forward entering straight, hit front 350m, battled gamely until flattened 50m.
Got off OK, not pushed, settling in midfield in one-off position. Hampered 1400m, taken to rail four-back from leader. Kept on fairly in straight under hard riding.
Began fairly, made up ground along rail, steadied 1400m, settling 3-back before turn. Switched out entering straight and boxed on fairly.
Hard ridden to lead on settling. Passed by another passing 1200m but retook lead 800m. Kept on early in straight while laying away from rail before tiring final 200m.
Shifted in behind runners shortly after start, settling at rear in one-off position. Made up some ground around turn, wide in straight, boxed on one-paced.
Bumped shortly after start, ridden while edging closer to rail at rear. Switched out entering straight but only one-paced.
Flat-footed at start, losing ground, and last on settling. Raced fiercely after being steadied 1300m, made up some ground around turn, one-paced in straight.
Restrained on jumping and shifted across behind runners but kept 3-wide at rear. In last pair around turn, found little in straight.
Ridden to hold forward position but held 4-wide on settling. Allowed to roll forward to race outside leader, led narrowly 1200m to 800m. Spent force on straightening and faded.
Shifted in shortly after start but unable to find cover behind midfield. Left without cover from 1200m and never likely thereafter.
Ridden along to hold box seat, bumped and unbalanced 1600m, travelled keenly, checked 1400m, lost position turn and finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
From wide barrier unable to get close than 3-wide, no cover in midfield from 700M, 3Ls to make up 400M, quickened up well to take narrow lead 100M, held sway at the finish.
Emerged as leader passing 1000M, continued on well when placed under pressure leaving the bend, headed by winner 100M but refused to give in, fought all the way to the line.
Began only fairly, pushed along to hold its position in 5th 3Ls off the pace, kept up the chase on leaders in straight, went 3rd 150M, held towards the line.
Taken back and shifted across to the fence, held up behind mid-division, kept to inside on straightening, ran on steadily chasing leaders but not properly tested final stages. Sound debut.
Began well from draw 1, chased leader along the fence, switched out to challenge passing 450M, kept on same pace and held final 200M.
In mid-division much further back than usual, made only limited progress on straightening, no threat to leaders.
In pursuit of leader, held 2nd till 250M, no extra final stages.
Taken back from wide barrier, in rear pair over 7Ls off the pace, stayed on only fairly in straight passing well beaten horses.
Towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, kept on same pace entering straight, never troubled leaders.
Dropped back to the rear 7-8Ls off the pace, made no progress entering straight, never involved.
Settled down behind midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, not quickened entering straight, well beaten.
Chased leaders in 4th place, didn't find much in reserve when driven out 500M, soon weakened.
Shared early pace before eased two-back, one-off passing 1200m. Rolled forward on straightening, hit front 150m, kept finding when challenged final 100m.
Began awkwardly, ridden to make up ground settling 3-back along rail. Switched out 350m to get run, looked a chance 200m, unable match winner final strides.
Began OK, pressed forward settling three-back, one-off. Switched out on straightening and ran on well to be closest at finish.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Shaken up entering straight and finished off nicely to just miss a place.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. Taken to rail and improved around turn. Switched wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Hard ridden early to hold box seat but shuffled 2-back passing 900m. Closed in top of straight but not much room to 250m. One-paced when clear.
Pressed forward on jumping, settling 2L from leader in one-off position. Allowed to move forward to race outside leader at turn, hit front 450m, caught 250m and faded.
No early pace, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Well back entering straight, switched out 250m but no run and switched out again 100m. One-paced.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start and last on settling. Trailed field to straight, taken to centre track and made up some late ground.
First out, led to 1150m before taking sit, 2L behind leader. Shifted out on straightening but found little under hard riding and faded final 200m. Unacceptable performance.
Outpaced, dropping towards rear on settling. Shuffled back to last around turn, boxed on one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK but outpaced, dropping behind midfield along rail. Held position around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners soon after start but held wide at rear. Left without cover from 1000m, found nothing when asked in straight.
Hard ridden from outside draw, sharing early pace before pulling ahead passing 1150m and crossing to fence 900m. Collared on straightening and faded.
Began well before easing back to be handily place 5th, 1 off the fence. Stoked up from the 300m, easily passed early leader 100m and only had one challenger late.
Began OK, and steadied early to sit midfield, on the fence. Ran solidly in the early part of the straight before kicking from the 200m. Finished off strongly, and just held out late.
Pushed out early to take a big early lead, 2.5L ahead of 2nd. Still ahead at 100m but already weakening noticeably and faded late, and easily taken by first 2, but holding the place.
Away OK before dropping back to sit worse than midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran OK in the straight before looking to have peaked at 200m. Found a second wind at 100m, and finished well.
Pushed forward from the wide barrier to sit 2nd, on the rail 2.5L behind the leader. Well placed on the turn, and ran OK in the straight but never produced a big kick.
Lifted front feet on jumping and was slow to begin, settling last, 10L off the leader. In the last couple on the turn, but finished off OK late.
Worse than midfield early, on the rails 7L off the leader. Looked to run on from the turn, but 1 paced in the straight and only eased to the line late.
Dropped back early to sit 3rd last, 3 wide. Came widest on the turn, but only went to the line fairly and was eased late.
Pushed forward early to be handily placed 4th on the rail, 4L off the early leader. Didn't respond in the in the run home, drifting back in the straight.

OK away and initially stuck 3-4 wide with no cover, forward of midfield before moving forward at 800m to be 3rd, 1 off the fence. OK early in the straight, but tapped out at the 200m and dropped back.
Fairly away and got back early to be 2nd last, 1 off the fence. Under pressure before the turn, ran flat in the straight and never made an impression.
Began OK and taken to sit worse than midfield, 3-4 wide with limited cover. Didn't have much in the tank by the turn, never responded to riding in the straight and dropped out quickly.

Gradually shifted across to settle just outside the leader, became 3rd approaching home bend, renewed effort entering straight, quickened well to hit the front over 100 metres out.
Broke well, settled just off the pace on rails, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily but unable to peg back the winner the length of straight.
Niggled at early, settled in 2L 5th far side, lost position when pace quickened entering straight, produced good impression to do best work late.
Settled worse than midfield on rails, soon came to challenge upon straightening, briefly baulked 200 metres out, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled about 3L off the pace around midfield on rails, switched out to challenge upon straightening, made modest progress under pressure early in straight.
Jumped best to lead attempting to make all, dictated pace from middle stages, kicked about 2L clear upon straightening but soon flattered, swamped inside the final 200 metres.
In last few early, made headway from approaching back straight to reach midfield 3-wide, similar position entering home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Niggled at early stages settling in midfield and 2-wide, shifted widest entering home straight, kept on steadily down the centre of the track without threatening.
Settled behind midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, found no response under pressure in the run home.
Gradually taken back from a wide gate for rails run in last place, next to last rounding home bend, made no impression in the run home. (Jockey warned for choice of tactic)
Began from a wide gate, travelled 3-wide without cover in midfield before taking closer order down far side to join the leader, dropped out tamely in the run home.
Well behind, never seen with a chance.
Took rail and led easily at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well to win.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide just off the leader, benefited by the very slow pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, favoured by the very slow pace, just held ground for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the very slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, harmed by the very slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the very slow pace.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the very slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, harmed by the very slow pace, flattened 150M.
Very slow away, took rail at back, not suited by the very slow pace, ran on ok.
Eased at start, at rear, armed by the very slow pace, ran on fairly.
Very slow away, at rear, harmed by the very slow pace, no progress.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at fast sectionals, kept on gamely to hold off the challengers by a short head.
Camped handy, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, accelerated strongly for 2nd, missed by a short head.
Eased to settle worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, closed off well for 3rd.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, however, unable to find a day light most straight, ran on well for 4th when clear 100M.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at fast pace, kept on one pace to the line.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, stayed on one pace until weakened final stages.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, ran home strongly.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the fast tempo, never ran on. (Substantial amount of mucus in its trachea)
Always at rear, never a factor.
Raced midfield, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, gave ground soon after straightening.
First out, taken to rail and set slow quarters to straight. Put under intense pressure final 300m but battled gamely and just held.
Began well, crossed to fence to sit at the back of the speed. Took inside run on straightening, ran on strongly but just failed.
Jumped with field but crowded for room and shuffled towards rear in one-off position. Swung wide into straight, switched to centre track 250m and finished strongly.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, ridden forward settling 3-back, one-off. Switched out in straight, bumped and unbalanced 250m, finished off well.
Began OK, ridden to hold rail but 4L from leader back stretch. Took inside run in straight and ran on well.
Slow, then shifted across behind runners to rail at rear. Brushed rail and unbalanced around turn, shifted out in straight and ran on steadily.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing wide before shifting in to settle 1L behind leader. Boxed on gamely in straight until swamped final strides.
Crowded out on jumping, pressed forward in one-off position at midfield. Taken wide in straight, hampered passing 250m, kept on fairly.
Jumped OK, not pushed, settling along fence four-back from leader. Stayed on rail in straight and ran on fairly to be closest at finish.
Shifted across from wide draw soon after start, settling at rear in one-off position. Stayed at rear throughout, finished one-paced in straight.
Began well, pushed to stay with early pace before dropping one-back, one-off back stretch. Kept on fairly in straight until flattened 100m.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Hard ridden back stretch but continued to lose ground, finishing tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Ridden but didn't muster, dropping behind midfield. Left 3-wide without cover 1,500m and allowed to edge forward. Began run 600m, hit front 300m, kept finding to the line.
Began well, pressed forward, holding one-off spot behind leader. Eased one-back, one-off back stretch, took inside run in straight, finished strongly but just failed.
Given reminders at start, pressed forward to one-off spot in midfield. Lost position back stretch, took off from 500m circling field to within 1L of leader at 200m before run ended.
Began well, pushed along 3-wide outside leader before cutting to rail in box seat 1500m. Got inside run in straight and kept on well to the line.
Began fairly, taken to fence, 4-back from leader. Switched to one-off position back stretch, swung very wide into straight, ran on well down centre track.
Began fairly, pressed forward to hold rail 3-back from leader. Made home turn awkwardly, had open run in straight, kept on fairly.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold one-off position in midfield. Lost position turning for home but kept on steadily in straight.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind runners to rail 3-back from leader. Dropped further back passing 1200m, stayed on rail in straight and ran on fairly.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing 3-wide to 1600m when allowed to roll forward to sit outside leader. Hit front soon after straightening but ran out of stamina and faded.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Trailed field to straight and ran past beaten horses.
Steadied and shifted across behind runners, settling at rear but wide. Allowed to roll forward from 1200m to within 3L of leader passing 400m before tiring and dropping back.
Surged to the front on jumping, set steady early pace to 1400m before slowing to a crawl. Joined up front 400m and tired quickly final 300m. Had post-race distress.
Ridden forward and sat outside the leader, ran on nicely and held off late challenge to score.
Rolled forward, raced one-off one-back, kept on pushing to the line and lost out only by a nose.
Pressed forward to cross, took the rail and led, maintained lead until 100M when headed, ran on for 3rd.
Raced in front of midfield, 3-1/2L behind but trapped wide, no dash but kept on to the line.
Travelled in midfield along the rail, 3-3/4L off the pace, dropped off slightly after straightening, slight dash near 150M to run on.
Settled in worse than midfield, 5-3/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed near 200M to make ground.
Rolled forward to take box-seat, 2-1/2L off the pace, kept on one pace to the line.
Taken back, raced 6-3/4L behind the leader, made ground steadily in the straight.
Raced in midfield, 4-3/4L off the pace 2 wide with cover, ran home one pace.
Slow start, raced just behind midfield along the rail, 5-1/4L behind, dropped off near 150M.
Sat towards the rear, 7-1/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not competitive.
Ridden all the way but stayed back, never a factor.
Began well but unable match pace, dropping three-back along fence. Lost position turn, not much room top of straight, switched in 180m to surge through gap and just held on line.
Outpaced, dropping to last 10L from leader back stretch. Steadied 500m, checked off heels home turn, switched out 300m and finished strongly to just miss.
Aggressively ridden to lead on settling, setting good pace to 900m when passed, taking sit behind leading pair. Switched out entering straight and ran on strongly to just miss.
Got off well, ridden along one-off to hold midfield position back stretch. Urged forward turning for home, taken wide in straight and ran on strongly.

Fractious in gate and lost ground start. Ridden to make up ground but reluctant to stretch out and taken wide around turn. Blocked early in straight but finished strongly. Racing manners unacceptable.
Ridden vigorously to obtain forward position but unable to cross to rail and held wide without cover from 900m when 3L from leader. Kept on gamely in straight.
Pressed forward from outside draw racing 3-wide till getting cover behind midfield back stretch. Urged forward passing 550m, blocked for run 200m, boxed on.
Began well, raced fiercely when taken outside leader, dropped back to 3rd passing 900m. Went forward again to eye-ball leader around turn. Kept on to 200m before flattened.
Began OK but no early speed, dropping to rear along fence. Stayed on rail around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden to hold fence, settling in box seat back stretch. Shuffled back around turn but came again in straight to get to within range 150m before run ended.
Pressed forward from an outside draw but trapped 3-wide behind the pace. Allowed to roll forward taking over lead 900m. Collared passing 250m and faded.
From draw 11 caught 3-wide no cover on midfield, urged along 500M and moved into contending position top of straight, led inside 150M and drew readily clear, eased towards the line.
Soon led under 7lb claiming rider, took them along at a sound pace, headed inside 150M but held on for 2nd well.
Chased leaders, moved out to clear 400M, kept on steadily when driven out, held towards the finish.
In touch, had every chance entering straight but unable to draw level with leaders, lost 3rd near line.
Began awkwardly and slowest away, settled down 5Ls back towards the rear, closed off well final 300M making late impression.
Held up in midfield along the fence, 3Ls to make up 400M, kept on one pace in straight not making progress on leaders.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, settled at the rear 6Ls behind leader, kept on fairly along inside final 300M, never seriously threatened.
Not mustered the pace to go forward, ended up behind midfield much further back than intended, brought wide 350M making limited progress.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, driven along 450M, stayed on same pace, no impression on leaders.
Pushed forward to race outside the pace, had little left leaving the bend, soon on the retreat.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover early stages , eased back to the rear approaching home turn, not picked up the pace to challenge, soon left behind.
Raced 3-wide behind mid-division, came under pressure 500M, dropped away entering straight.

Moderate start, soon driven to midfield, showed a great turn of foot inside final 250 metres to soon take charge, won well.
Broke well from a poor gate, settled in 2nd just off the rails, came under pressure soon after straightening but outsprinted by winner closing stages.
Settled 3-wide in midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, joint 5th about 3L back entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled in rear on rails, produced good late impression closing stages.
Prominent, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.
Attempted to make all, came under pressure to hold place early in straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped closing stages.
Moderate start, settled just worse than midfield, came under pressure around home bend, made modest headway early in straight but never threatening.
Lacked early pace, ridden to midfield on rails, snuck up to joint 5th about 3L back turning in, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace on rails, similar turning in, ran home one-paced.
Settled in midfield on rails, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped towards the rear, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from a poor draw, never seen with a chance.
Began from the widest gate, soon dropped well behind.
Lacked early pace, made short-lived effort around the bend, soon weakened under pressure.
Eased to find cover early, however trapped wide in the lead, took rail 700M and led at fast sectionals, drifted away 400M to score.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
At back, 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 350M.
Eased to rear, 3-4 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 350M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, lack room in straight, made some ground.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no turn of foot.
At rear, on the rails, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok in straight.
At back, along the fence, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Very slow away, raced 4-5 wide, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, reduced 350M.
Shared the lead at fast sectionals, faded 400M.
Missed break, then rolled forward to settle midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off strongly to score by 3-1/4Ls.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly until weakened final 100M, beaten by an impressive winner.
Pushed to settle in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Rolled forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on steadily to the line for 4th.
Prominent, however, trapped wide without cover throughout, kept on steadily to the line without extra acceleration.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, ran on gradually.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on gradually until final 150M when crowded.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, unable to find a day light early straight, one paced home when clear 200M.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until faded 200M.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
At back throughout, never looked likely.
Jumped slowly, at rear throughout, never ran on.
Raced midfield, gave ground rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Began fairly, settling towards rear along rail. Shaken up 600m, switched to centre field 350m, picked up momentum gradually to just hit the line in time.
Began well, pressed forward but wide, before slipping behind midfield at turn. Turned wide, picked up momentum from 300m, just failed.
Ridden along in one-off position at midfield, urged forward at turn but not much space, took run between horses in straight and finished strongly to just miss out.
Pressed forward and caught wide without cover outside leading pair from 1000m. Urged forward 400m, broke clear 200m, swamped on line.
Quickly into stride, racing outside leader to turn. Joint leader 400m, kept on well to 200m when shifted out under pressure, then one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear away from fence. Shaken up 500m but didn't respond until given reminders 200m, finished strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair along rail. Switched out entering straight and finished off nicely final 200m.
Ridden early to hold forward position 3-back from leader. Made ground around turn, looked chance 400m, one-paced.
Shifted across behind horses from outside draw, settling at rear but wide. Taken even wider in straight and kept on fairly.
Beaten for early pace, dropping 4-back along rail. Took inside run in straight but only one-paced.
Crowded out start, pushed forward but raced keenly, settling behind leading trio to straight. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
First out, setting even tempo along rail to straight, Collared soon after straightening and faded.
Ridden forward, settling in one-off position 3L from leader. Lost ground around turn and faded in straight.
Blundered on jumping, almost dislodging rider, then allowed to trial field without being asked for an effort.
Jumped OK, rolled forward gradually to sit outside leader 1900m. Shaken up passing 600m, hit front 400m, broke clear 200m, held off late challenge.
Began well, taken to box seat 1900m, dropping 3-back 1700m. Lost position turn, blocked early straight, switched in 250m to get run and finished strongly.
Restrained after start and shifted to one-off position at rear. Began forward move 800m, circled field to look chance 300m, then one-paced.
Began well, rolled forward gradually, sliding into box seat 1700m. Tailed leader to straight, shaken up 300m but only one-paced.
First out, then set even pace to straight. Collared soon after straightening but boxed on gamely to 150m before tiring.
Tightened shortly after start, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Got shuffled back rounding turn, switched out straight, one-paced.
Began well, taken forward settling one-out, one-back. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced, tiring final 100m.
Got off OK, not pushed, last on settling. Moved up 1700, taken wider 1500m, surged forward from 800m but run ended 400m, faded.
Steadied after start, taken to rail, ridden but didn't improve, settling at rear. Shuffled back to last around run and finished tailed out.
Settled just in front of midfield, 2L off 2 wide with cover, ran on nicely and held off a late challenge to score by a head.
Travelled at the rear, 5-1/2L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, taken widest after turn, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Rolled forward to take box-seat from barrier 1, once straightened shifted away from the rail, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Ridden forward and sat outside the leader, no dash and kept on one pace to the line.
Sat in midfield, 2-1/2L behind trapped 4 wide when unable to obtain cover, closed off one pace.
Raced in worse than midfield along the rail, 4L behind the leader, slight dash near 150M, found nothing thereafter.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 5L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed after 400M to make steady ground, one pace from 200M.
Niggled forward to take the rail and led by 1/2L, did not respond when under pressure, not competitive.
Sat towards the rear, 4-1/2L behind the leader but trapped very wide, improved past some tiring runners only.
Raced in midfield, 3-1/2L off the pace 2 wide with cover, dropped off at 250M.
Raced slightly behind midfield, 4L off and 4 wide with cover, not competitive.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 3-1/2L behind 3 wide with cover, did not look likely.
At the rear throughout, never a factor.
Settled in front of midfield, 1-1/2L off 3 wide without cover, weakened soon after straightening.
Snagged back at start, shifted in, settling at rear. Shaken up 600m to go forward, taken to centre track and finished powerfully to win close home.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide outside leading pair. Rolled forward turn, led passing 400m, pulled clear but drifted out 200m, run down on line.
Began well but unable match early pace, dropping behind midfield. Crowded out 500m, swung wide into straight, finished off strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Made up ground around turn, taken wide in straight and finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Began OK, ridden to hold rail, grabbing box seat. Tailed leader to straight, switched out 450m to make run, ran on steadily.
Pressed forward from outside draw but kept 4-wide back stretch. Wide without cover around turn, taken to centre track 400m, one-paced.
Bumped start, ridden forward then steadied 1100m to get trailing position 3L from leader. Kept on well early in straight turning one-paced final 200m.
Pushed up inside leader to 1200m before taking sit in one-off position 1L behind. Moved up turning for home, hit font 400m, boxed on to 200m before tiring.
Lost ground at start, dropping to rear. Made up ground around turn, kept on fairly early in straight turning one-paced final 200m.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail 3-back from leader back stretch. Improved around turn but one-paced final 200m.
Began well, ridden but unable to hold position, dropping to last pair. Never competitive.
Hard ridden to lead, then set steady pace to turn. Collared soon after straightening and faded. Had small cuts to lift hind cannon and right hind pastern.
Began fairly, ridden but didn't muster, settling towards rear. Shuffled back to last around turn and finished tailed out. Barrier manners, performance unacceptable.
Pressed forward, settling one-out 3L from leader. Lost position around turn, and faded quickly, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Reserved in mid-division 4Ls off the good pace, handled the yielding track well and travelled strongly into straight, quickly asserted nearing 300M and pulled 5Ls clear approaching 150M, won impressively.
Raced in 2nd last 8Ls off the pace early stages, patiently waited with till 400M, stayed on to go 2nd inside 100M, not reached runaway winner.
Settled down 4 wide in mid-pack with cover, 3Ls off leader making home turn, nudged along 600M, stayed on moderately to go 3rd near line, no threat to runaway winner.
Saved ground from draw 1, tracked leaders along the fence, took over 350M but soon caught by winner, kept on steadily to line, beaten to 4th over final 100M.
Not hurried early and middle stages, settled at the rear over 8Ls off the pace, driven widest 600M, ran on for non-threatening 5th.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, 5Ls behind leader middle stages, wide bid from top of the bend, ran on moderately over final 400M, no serious threat.
Caught wide early stages, strode forward to race outside the lead entering back straight, led 500M out, caught by rivals from 350M, kept on one pace towards the finish.
Prominent early, eased back to midfield middle stages, shuffled further back leaving home turn, stayed on passing beaten horses only.
Caught 4-wide without cover in the group chasing leaders, found little when placed under pressure 400M, soon weakened and dropped away.
Held up in midfield along the fence, 4Ls off the pace entering home turn, not picked up under pressure, faltered 300M.
Chased leaders, unable to hold its position 600M and soon on the retreat.
Prominent early stages, remained in touch making the turn for home but didn't respond to pressure 500M, beaten early straight.
Caught wide 1st turn, strode to the lead 1300M setting good pace, gave way from 500M, eased when well beaten. (Unacceptable Performance)
Began well, pressed forward, 2-back along rail. Switched out turning for home, began run 300m out, finished strongly to win on line.
Steadied after start, dropping back and taken to fence. Improved around turn, switched out wide in straight and finished strongly to just miss.
Driven forward to lead then set steady pace to straight. Fought off early challenge passing 300m but swamped by first two final strides.
Bumped from behind at start, pressed forward to sit 1L behind leader back stretch. Rolled forward to join leader 350m, kept on gamely until flattened 100m.
Began OK, taken to fence 4-back from leader. Made up ground around turn, switched out halfway up the straight and ran on steadily.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair along fence. Taken out entering straight and kept on fairly.
Ridden to hold one-off position behind midfield, switched out around turn to make run but only one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from widest draw and last on settling. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Began well, pressed forward but kept wide without cover 2L from leader. Covered extra ground turn and tired quickly after passing 200m.
Pushed forward from inside draw to hold box seat. Kept tabs on leader to straight but gave ground quickly from 200m.
Ridden to hold midfield position back stretch and turn but tired soon after entering straight.
Lost ground start, ridden but didn't muster, settling towards rear in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Began well, pressed forward one-back, one-out but unable hold position around turn and shuffled back. Found nothing in straight.
Restrained, shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling towards rear. Dropped to last entering turn and never competitive.

Began awkwardly, and dropped back to sit 2nd last before pressing forward along the rail from the 1000m to be handily placed 4th/5th by the 600m. Pulled away from 400m and only had one challenger late.

Steadied from the kick to sit last in back straight, 2L behind the 2nd last horse. Took short cut through worse going on the turn. Weaved through runners in the straight, closing on the winner, until both ran flat in last 100m.
Eased forward early to sit midfield, on the rail. Had open ground, and well placed to chase at the 300m, but couldn't muster a big kick and only OK to the line.

Cruised forward early to find a position midfield, 4 wide. Stayed wide when pushing forward at 600m, and went for the better ground up the middle of the straight. Ridden positively, but didn't have a big kick in the straight.
Bumped on jumping, then pressed forward to be well placed 1L off the leader, 2nd/3rd 1 off the fence. Ran on OK early in the straight, but looked to struggle in the conditions and fading late.
Had to push forward early from the wide draw to eventually sit 2nd 1L off the leader, 1 off the fence. Didn't have a lot left in the tank in the straight and went to the line 1 paced.

Pushed forward from the inside draw to be an early leader, before dropping back to 4th on the fence. Came off heels, and switched run towards the fence at the top of the straight, but only ran fairly.
Dropped back early sitting just worse than midfield, 3-4 wide. Came widest on the turn, and only battled on fairly to the line.

Lost both front plates early and was stuck midfield 6 wide early, after not being able to muster speed from the wide draw. Didn't respond in the straight and only went to the line fairly. Jockey stated didn't handle track.
OK away and taken forward early to sit just forward of midfield, 3-4 wide. Came wider on the turn for firmer track, but never ran on in the straight and eased out late.
Eased forward early, initially sitting around midfield. Dropped back toward the rear by the 800m. Only plugged away in the straight, and never ran on.
Eased back early to sit worse than midfield, 3 wide. Last on the turn, never ran on in the straight and was eased out late.
Pushed forward early from the wide draw to be an easy 1L leader by the 1200m. Keen in front and was burnt out in the straight, and never ran on.
Dropped back early and sat 2nd last by the 1200m mark. Held the rail and looked to run on from the 300m, but never responded to urgings and was eased out from the 150m.
