Began well, raced keenly one back on rails within striking distance, hit the front upon straightening, won readily.
Began well, settled in 4th or 5th within 3L of pace on rails, came under pressure when pace quickened around the bend, fought on steadily without threatening from 4th into straight.
Settled in midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Not far off, disputed lead halfway down far side, unable to sustain effort and faded inside final 300 metres.
Settled towards the rear, made modest progress under hard driving in straight.
Trailed the field in the early stages, improved to one from last passing the 800 metres, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily down the inside of the straight.
Midfield throughout, saved ground turning in, one-paced under pressure.
Soon took up running, joined halfway down back straight, weakened noticeably shortly after straightening.
Towards the rear throughout.
Midfield throughout, came under pressure around home bend, wide entering straight, no dash.
Never a danger.

Placing: PU
Comment: Not far off to home bend, dropped out from approaching 400 metres.
Pushed to cross in front, took rail and lead, traveled strongly as usual ,drifted away 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, ran on strongly 200M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, just held ground in final stages.
Behind midfield, along the fence, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at back, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, lack turn of foot in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, reduced 200M.
Very slow away, at rear, raced 2-4 wide, no progress.
Very slow away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot, trapped 3 wide, emptied 250M.
Never a factor.
Ridden forward to settle outside the leader, ran on strongly to take the victory.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader along the fence, finished off nicely when clear over the final furlong.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed well for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
Taken back as usual, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground without any serious threat.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on until weakened final 200M.
Eased to rear from a wide gate, 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground along the inside track.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made no impression in straight.
Always at back, never a factor.
Rolled forward to settle in a prominent position, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Pushed to midfield from a wide draw, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, swung widest turning home, never ran on.
Started ok, bustled along to race 4th 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, grinding progress to lead close home.
Ridden wide to lead 1000m, clear & crossed to rail 780m, extended & 3L clear turning in, driven 300m, all out & shortening stride final 200m, headed close home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on rail, slightly improved on turn, finished off very strongly in straight to get 3rd.
Rousted to lead 1100m, headed 1000m, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, driven in pursuit final turn, closed dourly but no extra closing stages.
Speed to lead on rail at break, eased & headed 1100m, shuffled to 5th, switched out & driven turning in, boxed on evenly.
Moderately away from the widest gate, raced 2 to 3 wide with some cover at rear, similar position on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress without threatening.
Smart break & bustled to race midfield 1 off with cover, hard ridden turning in, one-paced in run home.
Crowded out start, recovered to race in midfield on rail, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, bumped near 900M, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Speed to press lead, snared rail 850m & sat 1 back from 780m, ridden along 500m, weakened in run home.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail throughout, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, steadied near 850M, well back on turn, emptied early in straight and eased, never a threat.
Broke well, soon parked 5th 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep for progress 450m, ridden into stretch & quickened to lead 250m, pressed to wire, held on.
Tardy start & bustled, niggled along back of midfield on rail, shifted out 460m, swung wide into stretch & driven, closed to wire, just failed.
Rousted from gate to soon settle 1 back on rail, niggled 360m, driven into stretch, boxed on evenly down fence.
Taken behind at start, raced rail near tail, niggled 550m, shifted centre track on straightening, stayed on for minor inroads.
Moderate break & niggled along, raced midfield 1 off with cover, some progress when driven widest into stretch, kept on to wire without threating.
Started ok, midfield on rail & checked off heels 1520m, driven into stretch & shifted out, kept on one pace.
Broke well, snagged to race at tail, progress on turn, driven turning in, kept on moderately.
Trapped 3 wide no cover midfield until slotted 1 off behind midfield 1100m, driven 350m & stayed on one pace centre track.
Speed to lead & soon snared rail, 1L clear & driven turning in, found little & headed 250m, weakened to wire.
Started ok, raced 1 off with cover, under pump 500m & last at 400m, plugged on past fading rivals.
Broke well, raced 2nd 1 off until snagged to 1 off 1 back 1250m, over-raced a touch backstretch, under pump 360m, found nil & weakened.
Good start wide, pressed lead 3 deep no cover 1st turn, settled 2nd 1 off no cover 1200m, driven into stretch, emptied 300m, faded tamely.
Ridden forward and led along the rail by 3/4L, ran on nicely to the line and scored in a tight finish.
Pushed forward and settled in box-seat, kept on nicely and pushed the eventual winner to the line.
Ridden forward to sit one off one back, found extra while laying in under pressure at 200M, finished off well.
Raced in front of midfield, 3-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, ran on well and made nice ground inside the final 100M.
Raced behind midfield after checked near 1000M, 5-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, improved gradually in the straight.
Sat in midfield after steadied near 1000M, 4-1/2L behind the leader along the rail, little response and finished off one pace.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/2L off the pace 2 wide after taking cover near 700M, did not improve in the straight.
Punched forward and parked outside the leader, stayed competitive until bumped at 200M, did not run on thereafter.
Raced in just behind midfield along the rail, 5-1/2L behind the leader, never looked likely.
Sat towards the rear along the rail, 6-3/4L behind the pace, not competitive.
Travelled towards the rear, 7L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest after turn, did not run on.
Taken back and remained at the rear. Never a factor.
Began awkwardly, ridden forward, settling one-off 3L from leader entering back stretch. Swung wide into straight, hit front 200m, pulled clear.
Away nicely, pressed forward outside leader before taking over 1280m and crossing to fence. Collared passing 200m but kept on gamely and held on for second.
Jumped well, ridden to hold rail 3L from leader. Eased slightly along back stretch, tightened 450m, held for run 250m, finished off nicely.
Began OK, didn't stretch out and had to be ridden 1200m to hold position. Put under pressure 500m, got clear run 300m, kept on steadily.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing wide till settling 1L behind leader in one-off position 1200m. Lay in under pressure in straight and boxed on one-paced.
Quickly away, leading field to first turn before taking sit on leader. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Got off OK, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Ridden to circle field final turn, getting to within range 300m, before turning one-paced.
Ridden to hold rail ahead of midfield, checked off heels 1400m. Lost position back stretch, shaken up 450m but only one-paced. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea, lame right front leg.
Began awkwardly, dropping back, taken to rail but checked 1350m. Bumped running rail and unbalanced. Made up ground early straight before turning one-paced final 200m.

Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners towards rear but wide. Steadied top of straight when blocked for run, turning one-paced. Found to have continuous epiglottic entrapment, lame right front leg.
Steadied and shifted across behind runners soon after start, settling last. Bumped running rail and unbalanced first turn, found little in straight.
Hard ridden early to hold forward position but held wide without cover 5L from leader. Wide into straight, faded gradually.
Tracked leader, moved to the front 200M and continued on under maximum pressure, held off fast finishing 2nd just.
Held up behind midfield, 5Ls to make up on leader 400M, picked up strongly passing 200M, motored home and was just denied narrowly.
Began awkwardly, went forward tracking leaders along the inside, kept up the chase entering straight, held final 100M.
Settled down 5-6Ls at the rear, saved ground on the inside, gradually improving over the home bend, came home strongly final 200M, nearest finish.
Checked 1100M and pushed very wide by rivals, dropped back to the rear for cover, had plenty to make up 400M, closed off well down the outside making good late impression.
Driven forward from wide barrier, crossed to the lead 1000M, headed 200M, faded towards the finish.
Eased back on jumping, settled behind midfield along the 3-path, ran on mildly over final 300M but never a serious threat to leaders.
Sat 4Ls back behind mid-division, kept on same pace entering straight, no impression on leaders.
Began well, eased back to sit in midfield but remained in touch, driven along 400M but failed to pick up speed on his first run at the Valley.
Crowded for room 1100M and pushed to a wide no cover position, strolled forward to chase leaders but had little left passing 250M.
Bounded in the air lost ground, hampered at 1100M and taken wide by rivals, at the rear 5Ls off the pace, became detached 600M out, soon out of contention. (Lame next day)
Badly crowded for room 1100M, hung out and raced keenly after the incident, made the home turn awkwardly, gave ground from 400M and eased early straight. (Lame next day)

Jumped quickly to soon take up running on stands rails, held narrow advantage until headed slightly passing the 400 metres, renewed effort to assert authority over 100 metres out, hung on under pressure.

Dipped jumping out of the highest draw near stands rails, soon recovered and hit the front passing the 800 metres, came under pressure to resist challenge coming onto course proper only to be outsprinted final stages.

Broke well from the two draw near the centre of the straight course, restrained to just behind first few before let down to issue serious challenge passing the 300 metres, held every chance until run ended about 100 metres out.
Moderate start from the one draw near the centre of the straight course, trailed the field before going past one after the first 200 metres, kept on same pace in the final stretch without quickening.
Jumped fairly but lacked early pace, tailed-off from the 800 metres but picked up quite well inside the final 200 metres for a good closing.
Slow out, soon recovered to race keenly just off the pace, tight between runners 400 metres out, weakened noticeably passing the 300 metres.
Well there to halfway mark, yielded ground from approaching course proper.
Pushed early to keep up in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, made ground 250M.
Behind midfield, along the fence, pace good, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Box seat, pace good, just held ground in final stages.
Pressed forward, pace good, led 400M, flattened 200M.
Eased back, took cover, pace good, raced flat until 150M to make some ground.
Eased at start, took cover at back, 2 wide, pace good, ran on only fairly.
Very slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, pace good, no dash.
Pressed forward to lead at good pace, emptied 200M.
Very slow away, at back along the fence, no progress.
Eased to rear, never competitive.
Failed to muster, never a factor at rear.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, enjoyed the fast tempo, finished off strongly to score by 2-1/4Ls.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at fast sectionals, kept on strongly until headed by the winner final 150M, held on for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, ran on steadily for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, ran on gradually.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, swung wide turning in, ran on only fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast sectionals, found nothing when asked.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast pace, made no impression in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened badly 300M.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Pushed forward from a wide gate, however, trapped 3 wide without cove throughout at fast sectionals, faded soon after straightening.
Pushed forward to settle in a handy position, however, harmed by the fast sectionals, weakened soon after straightening, tailed out.
Always at rear, finished tailed out.
Bumped start, raced handily 3 wide with cover, shifted 4 deep for progress to lead 1200m, clear & to rail 920m, rolled 5L clear, shaken up 400m & kept on for clear win.
Restrained last pair 1 off, driven wide final turn, chased leader centre track & battled to 2nd last stride.
Taken back to rail behind midfield, shifted out on turn, shaken up 400m, driven to 2nd 80m, lost place final stride.
Taken back to tail on rail, shifted out final turn but crowded, driven 300m, switched out 200m, stayed on centre but just missed frame.
Raced 1 back on rail, over-raced 1500m & shuffled to midfield 1300m, crowded into stretch, not clear run 300m, shaken up 220m, stayed on to just miss frame.
Started ok & raced 1 off 1 back, shuffled to midfield, niggled 700m, driven 450m & shifted out, quickened to vie for 2nd, tapered & swamped final 150m.
Disputed lead on rail until settled 1 back 1300m, 7L 4th & shifted 3 deep 600m, hard-ridden in pursuit to brief 2nd, emptied 300m & faded.
Bumped start & battled to lead 1st turn 1 off, worked to rail 1300m & niggled when pressed soon after, driven 750m, boxed on until faded out final 300m.
Rolled forward from wide gate to press lead 3 wide, to 1 off 1250m, 3rd & driven 530m, found nil & tapered to wire.
Well away, dropped in 1 off with cover behind midfield & niggled along, shifted 3 wide 800m & soon under pump, last turning in, soon emptied & faded.
Fast start to lead, soon headed & sat 1 back on rail, under hold & in pocket in stretch, switched out 250m, quickened to lead 150m, drew clear, in command.
Lacked early toe & bustled, raced rear 1 off, advanced a spot 850m, caught in traffic & shifted out on turn, driven 350m to challenge lead 150m, no match for winner.
Prominent initially, 1 off 1 back & over-raced 900m, shuffled to midfield 1 off, not clear run in stretch, shaken up 250m, boxed on late.
Tardy start widest, raced 3 wide with cover at tail, minor advance 850m, driven very wide into stretch, stayed on centre track for solid headway.
Moderate start, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, niggled 800m, under pump 700m, wider on turn, grinding run to 2nd 250m, peaked 160m & tapered.
Started well, pushed on to race 1 off 1 back, shifted out final turn & driven to challenge lead, tapered final 150m.
Smart start, taken back to rear, last & ridden 500m, switched out for running 250m, shifted wider 100m, boxed on for minor headway.
Pushed wide to lead & crossed to rail 1000m, headed 800m, regained lead 720m, 0.5L up & shaken up 350m, all out & headed 150m, tapered.
Sluggish start & rousted on rail to settle behind midfield, niggled on turn, crowded & buffeted in stretch, driven in clear 180m, kept on one pace.
Outpaced early & raced rail at rear, not clear run into stretch, driven 320m, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Broke well, settled back 1 off with cover, niggled 500m & driven wide into stretch, crowded & bumped 220m, tepid run home.
Broke ok, trapped wide in midfield, rolled forward to edge lead 1 off 800m, headed 720m, driven 400m, all out & weakening when hampered 200m, no extra.
Started ok & bustled along to race handily, caught 3 wide no cover, under pump 550m, driven 4 deep final turn, found nil.
Retrained to midfield 4 wide, over-raced early, no cover from 900m & minor progress, forced widest final turn, driven but found nil.
Ridden forward to take the rail and led through slow sectionals, kept pushing and battled off a strong challenge to score.
Pushed forward and sat prominently, 1-1/2L off 3 wide without cover, benefitted by the slow tempo, challenged strongly to the wire.
Rolled forward and occupied box-seat from barrier 1, suited to the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Travelled in midfield, 2L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited to the slow tempo, finished off nicely for 4th.
Stride forward and parked outside the leader, benefited by the slow pace, stayed likely until 200M, missed 4th in the last stride.
Raced in behind midfield, 3-1/4L behind the leader, took rail from 800M, not suited to the slow pace, ran home one pace.
Settled in midfield, 2-1/2L off 4 wide without cover, finished off only one pace.
Initially in behind midfield but was niggled along to improve around turn, couldn't keep on in the Straight.
Sat towards the rear, 4-1/2L behind the leader 4 wide with cover, swung widest and made minor progress only.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3-3/4L off 3 wide with cover, kept pushing but dropped off near 250M.
Travelled in midfield, 2-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, did not threaten.
Always at the back, never a factor.
Sat towards the rear, did not improve.
Remained at the rear, no progress.
Slow, taken to fence and last on settling. Trailed field to straight, switched to centre track 400m and finished powerfully, going from last to first in final 300m.
Ridden to hold rail behind leaders but allowed to slip back behind hot pace passing 1000m. Left fence 600m, 4-wide into straight, rolled forward to hit front 100, run down.
Pressed forward from wide draw to share pace before easing back 3L from leaders. Urged forward top of straight, hit front 150m before run ended.
Ridden early but found pace too hot and settled behind midfield away from fence. Lost position around turn, taken wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Unable to match early pace, slipping behind midfield. Took inside run in straight but checked 300m and shifted out. Finished off nicely.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing wide till getting cover 3L from leader at turn. Battled gamely in straight though severely checked 100m.
Outpaced early, settling at rear close to fence. Switched out turning for home and ran on fairly.
Hard ridden from widest draw to stay with leaders but 3-wide without cover. Battled on gamely to 200m before tiring.
Hard ridden to stay with pace, keeping tabs on leading trio to straight. Crowded out 400m, checked 300m, one-paced.
Ridden early but didn't muster, dropping to rear away from fence. Made up some ground around turn, but one-paced in straight.
Steadied shortly after start, dropping back towards rear in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing wide but with cover 3L from leaders. Blocked for run early in straight, kept on fairly to 200m before fading.
Pushed forward to contest lead, taking over before final turn but unable to kick clear. Caught 250m and faded.
Hard ridden to lead and then engaged in cut-throat battle with another runner to straight. Collared 300m and faded. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea, lame right front leg.
Settled in 4th, well placed to strike turning in, quickened past leader 200M, produced the fastest finish of the day and proved too classy for rivals, won by extending 2Ls at the line.
Tracked leader in 3rd, responded well when driven out 400M, went 2nd 120M but no chance with the classy MAURICE.
Held up in mid-division 3Ls behind leader, ran on well on straightening, got past higher rated rivals to go 3rd 50M, career best performance.
Not hurried early stages, 6Ls back towards the rear, swung home 3-wide, hit the line well over final 300M.
In mid-division tracking the path of race favourite MAURICE, had every chance in straight, kept on steadily without threatening.
Soon led, took them along at slow sectionals in first half of the race, quickened up tempo 500M, headed 200M and faded towards the finish.
Towards the rear 5Ls back, travelled keenly after 1400M, ran on final 400M without threat to leaders.
Dropped back to the rear 6-7Ls behind leader, brought wide home turn, made limited progress only entering straight. (No Vet findings)
Tracked leader 2-wide, not quickened turning home, dropped out of contention from 250M.
Restrained on jumping from wide barrier, 6-7Ls off the pace in the rear group, had plenty to do turning in, ran on final 400M but not reached contention.
Sat 3-wide no cover in midfield, moved into contention 550M, ran on same pace entering straight, out of contention 250M.
Held up behind mid-division along the fence, not picked up when pushed along 450M, weakened passing 300M.
Began awkwardly, taken back, settling at rear. Left fence approaching 700m, switched out to make run from 400m, hit front 200m, pulled clear.
Jumped well, ridden to hold rail, taking lead on settling. Set strong pace to straight. Joined up front 300m but kept battling to hold on to 2nd placing.
Away nicely, rolled forward, sitting outside hindquarters of leader. Urged forward top of straight, looked chance 300m but unable to get ahead.
Hard ridden to get forward position, settling between horses 3L from leader. Blocked for run from 400m to 200m, finished off nicely when clear.
Got off OK but held wide behind midfield and allowed to roll forward from 800m, racing 4-wide around turn. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
First to jump but unable to clear inside runners and kept 3-wide without cover 1L from leader. Kept on well to 200m before turning one-paced.
Began fairly, then difficult to settle, dropping behind midfield. Stayed on rail in straight, checked 200m, then raced tight and not properly tested.
Began OK, racing behind early pace before easing back approaching turn. Shaken up entering straight but only one-paced.
Jumped well but eased out of speed battle and taken to box seat 3L from leader. Steadied soon after straightening, no clear run from 300m and not properly tested.
Away nicely but outpaced, dropping to last on settling. Trailed field thereafter.

Pushed forward from wide draw, coming off heels 1200m.Sat handily placed in 5th, 2L off the leader and 3 wide with cover. Worked up early in straight before kicking clear at 150m. Hands and heels to line, easing late.

Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field early, 2-3 wide with cover. Ridden for luck early in the straight, but kicked well from the 200m. Big effort late, and ran onto heels of easing winner on the line.

Pushed forward initially before easing back to a position in midfield, 2-3 wide with cover. Came wide on the turn, and looked gone at 300 before kicking. Went to the line strongly, and almost claimed 2nd late.

Began well and pushed forward early to be well position on the leaders rump, along the rail. Battled along the rail in the straight, finally handing up the lead at 200m. Kept plugging along late and just held 4th.
Began OK and taken forward early to sit 4th, 1 off the fence. Held up early in the straight, before coming off heels to run on from 250m. Slightly 1 paced to the line when clear late.
Slow into stride. Dropped back early onto rail, and pushed up to sit midfield. Came wider on the turn to get clear space, but only went to the line fairly.
Pushed forward early to sit 1/2L off the leader, but stuck 3 wide with no cover. Nosed in front at the 200m, but couldn't maintain momentum and went to the line 1 paced late.

Pushed forward early to ensure he led, but unable to get to the rail. Still in front at 300m, but beginning to fade. Kicked again slightly late when well out of place position, and came off heels 50m.
Began well and eased forward early to be placed just forward of midfield, on the rail. Held up for the entire length of the straight, and was never tested.
OK away but only fairly into stride, sitting midfield, 1 off the fence. Only fair in the straight, and never looked to threaten.
OK away and pushed up to be just behind midfield. Over raced and got his head up from the 1200m, and lost ground. Started running straight from the 400m, but only fair to the line.
Dropped back from the wide draw and stuck wide with no cover, eventually settling last by the 800m with cover. Came wider on the turn, but only ran fairly to the line.
Fairly away, and dropped back early to sit in the last couple, 2-3 wide with cover. Went for a run at 350m, but horse never responded and went flat to the line.

Steadied back from the wide draw to eventually sit towards the rear of the field, 3-4 wide with limited cover. On heels at 900m.Never responded to urgings of the jockey, and was eased out a long way from home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on strongly in straight to score.
Slightly slow out, raced 5 lengths back at 9th, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just missed.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the challengers late.
Began well from gate 7, raced prominently, found cover on turn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Moderately away from gate 12, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, similar position on turn, closed respectably given workload.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, improved on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, carried wide turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, raced 3 lengths back on rail, difficult to settle near 850M, angled out turning in, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Taken back to race 9 lengths back at rear, slightly improved on turn, made minor headway in straight without posing much of a threat.
Jumped well, raced 2 lengths back on rail, easy run on turn, no daylight early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made minor headway in straight.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced 5 to 6 lengths back on rail in 10th, there to turn, failed to closed off in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, showed no early speed, raced 10 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, failed to closed off in straight, never competitive.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race 2 wide, 4 lengths back in 7th, same position on turn, showed no response to riding in straight, finished last.

Jumped well, took up running passing the winning post the first time, obtained rails run passing the 1200 metres, set sedate pace down back straight, kicked clear after home turn, hung on well under pressure.
Jumped well, with leaders 3-wide early stages before settling just over 2L off pace in 4th, fought on steadily to reach 2nd passing the 150 metres but never threatening.
Poor beginning, soon recovered to better than midfield in 5th on rails within 3L of lead, similar turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.

Began from the widest gate, settled wide in rear of midfield, commenced move passing the Rock gaining to 4L 6th rounding home bend, similar when wide turning in, fought on steadily down the centre of the straight.
Began awkwardly, soon picked up to handy position on rails, settled one back in 3rd from the 1200 metres, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Settled at the back from a wide draw, remained similar on rails to straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Broke well from the middle draw, raced wide in prominent position around stables bend, settled just off the pace in 2nd far side, faded under pressure after straightening.
Jumped well, travelled keenly in midfield, switched out for a run upon straightening but failed to quicken under pressure. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Sluggish at start, tightened on rails when towards the rear past the winning post the first time, raced keenly in midfield when pace slackened far side, found nil in straight.
Jumped fairly, never better than midfield, wide into straight, one-paced under pressure.
Moderate start, soon dropped to tail-end, never a danger.
Jumped fairly, always in last few.
Settled just off the leader, 2 wide, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Behind midfield, along the fence, lack room 300M, dashed strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide just off the leader, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, trapped 3 wide, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Bumped start, hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide throughout, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, hung on until 200M emptied.
At back, trapped 3 wide, lack turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden to occupy box seat, reduced 200M.
Never better than midfield.
Bumped start, never a factor.
Eased at start, never competitive.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, switched out turning home, ran on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Half missed on jumping, shifted to the fence and travelled 3Ls behind the leader, ran on well for 2nd.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung widest 250M, dashed well for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on nicely along the inside for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily without serious threat.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on until headed final 150M.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, blocked early straight until final 150M, made some ground thereafter.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, one paced home.
Sent forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on fairly until weakened over the last furlong.
Camped handy, however travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until weakened final 200M.
Pressed forward, was steadied 1200M, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, weakened badly soon after straightening.
Failed to muster despite ridden along throughout, detached from the field, tailed out.
Broke well, parked close 2nd outside leader, bustled a touch 550m to close, driven to vie for lead turning in, quickened to grab lead 220m, drew clear.
Speed to lead on rail, pressed & shaken up 380m, maintained narrow lead into stretch, headed 220m, no extra & boxed on.
Smart start & prominent, soon snagged to 1 off 1 back, under pump from 500m, kept on dourly centre track to edge 3rd late.
Broke ok, raced rail 1 back, ridden 450m, clear 3rd when switched to centre track 180m, no extra & tapered to wire.
Fair start, raced rail near tail, advanced a spot 900m, shifted out final turn, switched centre & shaken up 250m, stayed on for minor headway.
Bustled at break to park midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, under pump 500m, swung wide into stretch & hard-ridden, boxed on to wire.
Started ok, sat rail mid rank, rolled on a spot 900m, 5th & ridden 400m, edged centre, switched back inside 120m, one-paced.
Lacked toe, raced near rear 1 off with cover, driven 550m to hold position, widest into stretch, ran home evenly.
Taken back at start, raced keenly & restrained to tail on rail, continued to over-race, driven 250m, outpaced in run home.
Broke ok, rolled to stalk 1 back on rail, switched out & shaken up 320m, driven to lead 150m, drew clear.
Taken back at start to 1 off with cover near rear, checked off heels 600m & shuffled back, niggled along, driven into stretch, strong closer centre track to nick 2nd.
Speed to lead on rail, driven into stretch, soon all out & headed 150m, tapered & mugged at post for 2nd.
Smart start to press leader initially, settled 1 off 1 back, switched out & ridden 400m to challenge lead on outer, always held & tapered final 100m.
Broke well & bustled initially to race handily 1 off with cover, shuffled back 700m, niggled 550m, driven 400m & widest final turn, boxed on one pace.
Sluggish start, taken to rail & raced near rear, progress to sit back of midfield 600m, driven into stretch, stayed on dourly.
Smart start, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield until slotted 1 off 550m, driven into stretch, boxing on for minor inroads when hung in late & corrected.
Broke well, 1 off with cover midfield, edged to rail 750m, shifted out & driven final turn, plugged on one pace.
Broke ok widest & rowed long initially, trapped 3 wide no cover near rear, niggled 550m, driven turning in, boxed on evenly centre track.
Unable to slot from wide, taken back to last pair 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide with cover 620m, driven turning in, plugged on tepidly.
Bustled forward wide, worked to brief lead 850m, snagged to 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden 400m, all out & emptied 300m, faded.
Outpaced at break, raced last pair on rail, ridden along 450m, found nil & soon beaten.
Pushed forward to cross from a wide barrier and led by 3/4L, ran on nicely to score.
Ridden up and sat one off one back, driven and closed off well to come home in 2nd.
Raced in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/4L off 3 wide without cover, finished off the race fairly.
Settled in behind midfield, 6-3/4L behind and 3 wide prior to the first turn, swung widest and made good ground.
Slotted into box-seat just before the first turn, kept on one pace to the line.
Began well and raced on the rail inside the leader, kept on until 150M and faded gradually thereafter.
Ridden up to take spot in front of midfield along the rail, 4-1/4L off the pace, weakened badly near 250M.
At rear throughout, improved only slightly.
Always towards the rear, never a factor.
Remained at the tail, not competitive.
Raced in worse than midfield initially, however went wide around turn and then faded gradually.
Worked way to the front soon after start then set steady pace to straight. Kicked 3L clear passing 200m and never threatened.
First out but didn't press forward, settling in slipstream of leader to straight. Angled out 300m to make run but unable close gap.
Crowded on jumping, losing ground, then close to heels 1000m, dropping to rear. Improved into tight running 700m, not much room early straight, finished off nicely.
Began well, hard ridden to go forward, settling one-off, one-back passing 800m. Swung wide into straight, ridden but unable to close gap to winner.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across, settling in last pair away from fence. Urged forward from 550m, taken to centre track in straight, boxed on fairly.
Jumped well but eased, settling on fence two-back from leader. Stayed on fence in straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Pressed forward from outside draw, racing 3-wide 2L from leader. Allowed to roll forward around turn, 2nd into straight, then one-paced. Lost right front plate near 1000m.
Steadied on jumping, crossed to rail, settling in last pair. Began forward move passing 500m, made ground to 250m, then one-paced.
Began awkwardly, ridden forward between horses in midfield before moving 3-wide around turn. Gave ground gradually in straight. Confirmed roarer.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing 3-wide behind midfield to turn when lost position, dropping back. Found nothing in straight when asked.
Outpaced, dropping to rear but 3-wide. Lost touch with main field around turn and found nothing in straight. Lame left front leg.

Placing: PU
Comment: Ridden to obtain forward position, settling behind early pace. Left wide 900m, gave ground abruptly from 500m and pulled up. Bled from both nostrils.
In rear group early stages, moved closer to pace down the back straight, travelled strongly over the home bend, quickened up well to lead nearing 50M, comfortably.
Went forward, steadied the race tempo once in the lead, pressed by rivals nearing 600M, kept on well under pressure, headed 50M and was always doing enough to hold 2nd.
From draw 1 obtained a trailing position just off the pace, saved ground and travelled well into straight, kept up the chase over final 300M, not pace of winner late stages.
Slow to begin, towards the rear early, switched wide 850M and strolled to join leaders 4-wide, kept on steadily entering straight, one pace final 150M.
Caught wide early stages, no cover from 1200M and strolled forward to join leader, battled on entering straight, gave way to pursuers 100M out.
Slow to begin, taken back from wide barrier, raced as the back-marker for much of the way, closed off fairly down the inside on straightening, never a serious threat.
In midfield early stages, shuffled back to rear down the back straight, hampered by beaten rival home turn, stayed on fairly over final 300M, not reached leaders.
Held up in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, proved very difficult to settle when race tempo slackened 900M, given reminders passing 500M, took time to get going, did best work final 200M.
Never far off from leaders, shifted out to 3-wide 800M when pace slackened, gave limited response under pressure, out of contention 200M. (No Vet findings)
Prominent, caught 3-wide until 1100M, shuffled back a bit entering home turn, struggled to keep up and gave way from 500M.
Towards the rear early stages, strode forward along the 3-path when pace slackened middle stages, with leaders making home turn but had little left entering straight, soon beaten and eased.
Blundered at the start, in mid-division, proved difficult to settle especially middle stages when race tempo slackened, eased early straight. (Jockey : not able to see out the distance)

Pressed on from a poor draw, amongst leaders before settling in 1L 2nd one off the rails, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening and hit the front over 150 metres out, readily.
Raced wide throughout after breaking well from the widest gate, gradually settled in rear of midfield, circled the field approaching home turn, sustained progress in straight but never threatening.
Settled in last few, commenced move rounding home bend and taken widest entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Niggled along for early position, restrained to one back on rails, no clear run early in straight, kept on well closing stages.
Settled just worse than midfield, slightly further back entering home straight, made steady progress on inside to be nearest at finish.
Given reminders for early position, obtained rails run in front coming out of back straight, led until finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Broke well from a poor draw, settled wide in forward of midfield, made short-lived effort to join 3rd briefly rounding home bend, one-paced in the run home.
Began well, settled mainly in 5th just better than midfield, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres. (Blood in trachea)
Sluggish at start, trailed the field far side, passed one horse rounding home bend, went past a couple under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Wide throughout, moderate start, gradually recovered to rear of midfield under urge, made no impression in straight.
Always in rear, never seen with a chance.
Soon picked up from a slow start to rear of field on rails, closest when midfield rounding home bend, faded shortly after straightening.
At back as usual, trapped 3-4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 200M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Trapped 3 wide in front of midfield, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, emptied 200M.
Eased to sit just off the lead, trapped 3 wide, ran on until 200M flattened.
Very awkward away, at rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 100M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not tested.
Bumped start, at back 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, held up most straight, ran on ok.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, made early move 600M, flattened 200M.
Bumped start, at rear, raced 2-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Behind midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Bumped start, failed to muster despite vigorously ridden along, checked early, never improved.
Eased at start, never a factor.
Camped handy, travelled 1L behind the leader along the outer fence, ran on strongly to score by a head.
Rolled forward to share the lead along the outer fence, kept on gamely until headed by the winner over the last stride.
Sent forward to share the lead grand side, kept on nicely to the line for 3rd.
Eased back, travelled 4Ls behind the leader middle of the track, ran on gradually for 4th.
At rear, travelled 5Ls behind the leader stand side, finished off well over the latter stages.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader middle of the track, made minor ground without threatening.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader stand side, one paced home.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader middle of the track, never ran on.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader stand side, found nothing when asked.
Broke well, taken back to midfield & caught 3 deep no cover, advanced from 700m to 3rd turning in, driven 430m & ground to narrow lead 280m, fought on to line.
Nudged along wide & prominent, eased to 1 back 1 off 1150m, shifted 3 deep 600m & nudged to 2nd at 500m, battling stretch duel but always held.
Missed break & bustled to last trio on rail, advanced a spot 850m, checked 700m, shifted out & driven 430m, strong closer, just failed.
Slow start, raced last trio 1 off, over-raced 1280m, clear last 800m, 2nd last & driven turning in, stayed on for solid late headway.
Taken back & bustled along behind midfield 3 wide with cover, 4 deep & driven 550m, ran on centre track for minor headway.
Quickly taken behind & raced 1 off behind midfield, shuffled back a spot 950m, 3 wide on turn, ridden 500m, stayed on for minor headway.
Taken back from widest gate to last trio 3 wide, advanced a spot 850m, niggled 600m, last turning in, ran on stands' side for minor late gains.
Settled 1 off with cover midfield, shuffled back a spot 1100m & over-raced a touch, shifted deeper on turn, bumped & unbalanced 550m, boxed on evenly.
Dropped in at rail midfield, shifted 1 off 600m, driven & switched 4 deep home turn, plugged on dourly.
Speed on rail to take slender lead, advanced 1L clear 850m, shaken up under pressure 430m, all out & headed 280m, faded out.
Eased back to rail behind midfield, edged 1 off 660m, rear rank & driven 400m, stayed on one pace.
Front rank 1 off initially, soon eased back to midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m & edged out, shifted wider & bumped rival 550m, one-paced & tapered late.
Pushed on to 4-wide front rank, vied for lead & edged to 1 off 1150m, 1L 2nd & niggled 650m, under pump 550m, faded tamely in stretch.
Pushed on to front rank 1 off until snagged to 1 back on rail 1300m, ridden 550m, found nil in weakening run home.
Pace widest to vie for lead, settled 2nd 1 off, niggled to close 500m, driven into stretch, grinding effort to nick lead at line.
Vied for lead, snared lead 980m & set tempo, strode 1.5L clear on turn, driven into stretch, battling all out when headed 120m, rallied, just failed.
Pace to lead, soon headed & raced 1 back on rail, niggled along, switched 3 deep 550m, driven 400m, grinding run to lead 120m, no extra & edged out final strides.
Broke well, raced 5th 1 off with cover, shuffled back on turn, checked off heels 700m & niggled, ridden into stretch, kept on without threatening.
Taken back to 3 wide with cover near rear, niggled 800m, driven 500m, lacked toe but stayed on gradually to make eye-catching late gains.
Settled 1 back 1 off, niggled under pressure & 4 wide no cover 550m, close 4th & hard-ridden 350m, every chance, tapered closing stages.
Broke ok & settled midfield on rail, driven 430m, boxed on at a consistent pace.
Settled back near rear 1 off, niggled 750m, ridden into stretch, tight for room 350m, checked 280m & switched out, kept on moderately thereafter.
Awkward start & bumped, restrained to midfield 3 wide no cover, gained cover 700m, driven into stretch, plugged on tamely.
Broke with others, initially taken back but trapped 4 wide no cover, rolled to share 4th turning in, driven 400m, found nil & weakened.
Slow start & urged to race last pair on rail, driven under pressure final turn, outpaced in tepid run home.
Taken back to last pair 1 off, niggled 550m, hard-ridden turning in, outpaced & never a factor.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 2 wide with cover, driven and held on well for the prize.
Raced in behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hit the line strongly but fell short by a short head.
Rolled forward and settled in box-seat, ran on gamely and closed off well in 3rd.
At the rear and on the rail, 6-1/2L behind the leader, accelerated well and dashed nicely passing 150M.
Raced midfield and on the rail, 3-1/4L off the pace, unleashed after straightening but couldn't find extra passing 200M.
Raced in midfield, 4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, plugged on but only one pace to the line.
Travelled outside the leader and shared lead rounding turn, remained gamely until swapped passing 200M.
Settled towards the tail, 5-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, kept on but made no impact.
Raced in worse than midfield along the rail, 5L behind the leader, did not improve in the straight.
Ridden up and stayed prominent, 2-3/4L off 3 wide without cover, ran on until weakened at 250M.
At the rear and wide throughout, never a factor.
Rolled forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L, faded after losing its running in restricted room near 300M.
Jumped OK, pressed forward, settling half a length outside leader to turn. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 300m, pulled clear for easy win.
Hard ridden to lead on settling, setting hot pace to straight. Joined up front 300m, kept battling but no match for winner.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Switched 3–wide entering straight and finished off strongly final 200m.
Shifted across from an outside draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Swung wide into straight, finished off nicely.
Unable handle hot pace, sliding back towards rear along fence. Stayed on rail entering straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, ridden forward, grabbing box seat. Switched out entering straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Checked shortly after start, dropping to behind midfield along rail. Improved position turn, 3rd into straight, run ended 200m.
Outpaced, dropping to behind midfield in one-off position. Made some progress around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from an outside draw but unable to cross and held 4-wide 2L from winner. Lost position turn and weakened in straight.
Ridden to hold midfield position but wide. Got shuffled back around turn and plodded in straight. Rider reported bit pulled through mouth middle stages.
Hampered shortly after start but pressed forward to settle 3L from leader. Gave ground around turn and faded in straight.
Began fairly, pressed forward racing outside 800m. Bumped and unbalanced turn, hung out, faded badly. Had post-race distress. Unacceptable performance.
Up with early pace, sat behind leaders entering home turn, came through narrow passage to lead 200M, drew away towards the line, won impressively first time on the AWT.
Chased pace, caught 3-wide no cover from wide barrier, challenged for the lead passing 300M, not pace of winner final 150M, held 2nd comfortably.
Held up behind midfield, 7Ls to make up 400M in a strongly run race, closed off well for 3rd but not reached first two.
Settled in mid-division along the 3-path, 5-6Ls off the good pace in mid-stages, stayed on moderately to go 4th near line.
Failed to muster early speed, dropped back to near the rear 7-8Ls away in a strongly run race, driven along 600M, closed off fastest in straight but left with too much to do.
Pressed the pace on the outside, took narrow lead 250M, run ended 200M and faded towards the line.
Reserved in 5th 4Ls off the strong pace in middle stages, stayed on only fairly final 300M, no threat to leaders.
Held up behind midfield, 7Ls to make up leaving the bend, made limited progress only, no impression. (Blood trachea)
Pressed by rival in the lead, set strong pace to straight, collared by rivals 300M, soon gave way. (No Vet findings)
Slowly away and failed to muster speed despite ridden, in rear 10Ls behind leaders turning, made no real progress final 300M.
Switched off to the rear, well off the pace middle stages, driven along 500M but unable to quicken.
Close up behind leaders early stages, brushed running rail and lost ground 900M, didn't travel thereafter, dropped away leaving the bend.
Began well, pressed forward but wide 2L from leader 1000m. Rolled forward 950m, hit front 850m, joined up front 400m, kicked ahead 250m and held.
Jumped OK, ridden forward settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Closed in around turn, rolled forward from 250m but run ended 50m from line.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Shaken up top of straight and finished off nicely to be closest at finish.
Began well, pressed forward but wide 2L from leader. Took closer order around turn to look a chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Ridden forward to sit on the back of the pace before checked 700m, dropping behind midfield. Picked up bridle in straight and ran on steadily.
Jumped best, pushed forward, racing wide until settling outside leader. Shuffled back to 3rd 800m but rolled forward again. Joint leader 300m before tiring.
Began OK, ridden to hold rail at midfield before bumped and unbalanced 700m, dropping back. Urged forward top of straight but blocked 250m, then one-paced.
Jumped with field, ridden along, settling midfield in one-off position. Bumped and unbalanced 700m but held position to straight when one-paced.
Quickly into stride, leading field until overtaken approaching turn, settling in box seat. Under pressure from 500m and gave ground gradually.
Ridden along from an outside draw but tended to over-race, dropping behind midfield. Circled field around turn to be 3rd into straight before tiring.
Began OK, not pushed, racing in midfield but wide. Made progress around turn, 4th but wide into straight before fading.
Outpaced, settling at rear along rail. Shuffled back to last around turn, plodded in straight.
Slow into stride, ridden but unable to hold position, struggling at rear. Never competitive.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Reared and sat down in stall when gates opened and took no part in race.

Dropped back early to sit 2nd last, 9L off the leaders, on the rails with cover. Took a small run at 200m, before running strongly in the latter stages and crossing the line going away from the opposition.

Pushed forward early to be well placed in 3rd/4th, 3L off the leader and 1 off the fence. Looked to be the best of them at the 100m, but taken by the winner soon after. Shifted out under pressure late.
Only fairly away before pushing forward to settle midfield, on the fence. Well placed on the turn, and ran strongly to the line without a big kick.
Began awkwardly and blundered, but still managed to push forward to be the early leader, on the rail. Still in front at 75m, but peaked soon after and was swamped near the line late.
Taken back as usual to sit worse than midfield, on the rail. Held up when attempting a run at 200m, before switching back in and running well late.
Pushed forward from the wide draw early to be one of the early leaders, 1 off the fence. Looked OK at the 200m, but looked to lay out away from the whip and only plugged to the line late.

OK away and cruised forward early to eventually settle midfield, 1 off the fence. Came wider on the turn, and ran on well at the top of the straight, before running 1 paced late and fading out of the finish.

Began well and taken forward early to be handily placed in 5th, 1 off the fence and keen. Began to run on well, before being tightened from the 200m and checked out of run 150m, losing ground. Never recovered and eased to line.
Began well and taken forward early to be handily placed, 4th on the rail. Never responded to pressure in the straight, and dropped out late.

Slowly away and dropped back early to sit at the rear on the field, 9L off the leaders and 1 off the fence. Came widest on the turn, but didn't respond to riders urgings, and only went fairly to the line. Eased last 100m.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, 3 wide with cover. Only went fairly to the line, under hands and heels, in the straight.
Drifted across from the wide draw to sit towards the rear of the field, 3 wide with no cover. Came wider on the turn, but disappointing and quietly ridden in the straight.
Slowly into stride before finding a position behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Didn't respond to urgings in the straight and eased out of the race a long way from home.
Dropped out from the jump, and played no part in the race. Jockey questioned.

Ridden along, prominent early, steadied to midfield approaching home bend, angled off rails for a run 200 metres out, ran on under pressure to hit the front final strides.
Sluggish at start, improved steadily to rear of midfield on rails, similar when 8th turning in, shifted out for a clear run 200 metres out, quickened well to just fail to peg back winner.
Settled in midfield, made steady headway in straight but without threatening.
Began well from a middle gate, amongst leaders far side, taken one back to 3rd on home bend, ran on under pressure to hit the front inside final 200 metres but run ended short of line.
Began from a wide gate, settled wide without cover in forward of midfield, kept on steadily without quickening.
Shared the lead on rails, kept on until folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Settled behind midfield, two from last rounding home bend, shifted out for a run under pressure at the 200 metres, one-paced without quickening.
Given reminders, shared the pace out wide down far side, obtained one-off position coming onto home bend, soon faded under pressure after straightening.
Close up early, settled in 4th about 2L off the pace from the Rock, baulked for a run after straightening, made no show closing stages.
Soon dropped well behind despite ridden along, made no impression in straight.
Settled well behind, never a danger.
Settled wide in rear of midfield, yielded ground from the Rock, no further impression thereafter.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, closed off strongly and drifted away 200M to score.
Settle at back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pressed forward easily and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early, at back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly in straight.
Pushed to sit in midfield 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Trapped 3-4 wide throughout, never competitive.
Sent forward to cross and led on the fence by 1L, kept on strongly and won impressively by 3-3/4Ls.
Hard ridden forward from a wide gate, however, was severely hampered making the first turn, after that travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on well for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made ground steadily for 4th.
Pushed forward, severely checked making the first turn, after that settled outside the leader, kept on only fairly until 200M weakened.
Eased to rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight despite unable to find a run near 200M.
Taken back, traveled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Raced midfield, 3Ls behind the leader, never looked likely.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat, weakened soon after straightening.
Always at rear, never a factor,
Hard ridden forward, severely checked making the first turn, after that travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, flattened soon after straightening.
Speed to lead, to rail 850m, 1.5L clear turning in, shaken up 300m & scooted 2.5L clear, peaked 100m, tapered & just held on.
Broke well but lacked early toe & bustled to settle rail midfield, niggled 500m & stoked up turning in, rattled home down inner, just failed.
Fast start to snag rail, sat 1 back, 1.5L 2nd & driven 350m, unable to close, drifted out under pressure, boxed on to hold 3rd.
Slow start & rousted initially, settled midfield on rail, shifted out final turn, shaken up 300m, progress & switched out 150m, dug in but always held in battle for 3rd.
Tardy start, raced 1 off near rear until checked off heels 850m, shuffled to 2nd last, niggled 600m, ridden turning in, stayed on for moderate headway.
Slow start, soon bustled forward to park midfield 1 off at 800m, niggled 450m & driven into stretch, boxed on evenly.
Sharp break, eased to handy 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven 380m, plugged on one pace.
Started ok, rousted forward to race 2nd 1 off no cover, 3rd turning in & driven, found nil & faded.
Broke well widest & snagged back to 2nd last, minor advance 3 deep no cover to sit back of midfield, driven wide into stretch, tepid run home.
Broke ok, rousted forward to race handily 3 deep no cover, under pressure & shuffled back 450m, forced wide home turn, found nil in labored run home.
Smart break but soon outpaced & slid back to midfield 1 off, checked off heels 850m & shuffled back, niggled 550m, soon under pump, found nil.
Outpaced & raced rail at tail, niggled along 600m, soon driven, plugged on willingly but never a factor.
Speed to lead, raced 1 off & restrained, headed 940m, settled close 3rd 1 off no cover, advanced to narrow lead turning in, kicked on, pressed to wire, held on.
Good break, bustled 3 wide to lead 870m, worked clear to rail 650m, headed turning in & driven, rallied but held in run to wire.
Slow start & raced rear rank 1 off with cover, switched out & driven for progress 400m, rattled home centre track to nick 3rd at line.
Smart start, bustled to rail, edged lead 940m & eased, settled 1 back from 650m, over-raced 450m, shaken up 250m, boxed on evenly.
Broke ok, settled rail fore of midfield, crowded final turn & unable to switch out, driven 250m, kept on solidly without threatening.
Tardy start & bustled to settled back of midfield 1 off with cover, driven forward final turn, shifted out & bumped 300m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Taken back at break to rail at tail of pack, niggled 700m, driven & switched out 300m, ran on for minor headway.
Moderate start, lacked toe & raced rail back of midfield, bustled along, hard-ridden 350m, brief check & switched out 250m, plugged on for minor inroads.
Broke well, raced midfield 1 off with cover, advanced from 500m, 3rd & driven turning in, emptied 200m & faded.
Tardy start & rolled forward to race 3 wide no cover, ridden 420m but one-paced, crowded 150m & no extra closing stages.
Started ok, soon rousted but over-raced 1050m & raced 3 wide with cover back of midfield, niggled 450m, minor bump 300m & unbalanced, found nil in tame run home.
Outpaced at start, soon 6L detached from pack & bustled along, never a factor.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, despite not suited to the quick tempo, unleashed strongly at 150M and closed off with a solid victory.
Sent forward to take the rail and led by 1-1/4L through slightly strong tempo, despite that maintained lead until 150M when headed, beaten only by an impressive winner.
Raced at the rear, 7L behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, suited to the quick tempo, closed off strongly and just missed out on 2nd.
Rolled forward into box-seat, travelled 2L off the pace, harmed by the fast pace, still ran on well for 4th.
Raced in worse than midfield along the rail, 5-1/2L behind the leader, suited to the quick tempo, ran on nicely in the straight.
Travelled at the rear along the rail, 7L behind the leader, suited to the fast pace, improved steadily in the straight.
Slotted into midfield, 4L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, no dash and kept on one pace to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off the pace 3 wide without cover, swung wide and couldn't find any to improve.
Ridden forward and sat 2 wide, harmed by the quick tempo, remained prominent until weakened near 150M.
Inconvenienced at the start, travelled in midfield along the rail, 3-1/2L behind, never threatened.
Awkward start, remained at the tail, never ran on.
Failed to show early speed, raced in worse than midfield 4-1/4L behind 3 wide with cover, did not improve.
Jumped OK, not pressed, sliding back to behind midfield in one-off position. Began run 400m, 4-wide into straight, hit front 200m, kept on strongly while laying in.
Hard ridden to go forward but unable to cross over and allowed to settle 3L from leader. Left wide passing 900m, rolled forward around turn, looked chance 200m, battled on gamely.
Began well, pressed forward, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Shaken up passing 400m, kept on steadily in straight.
Quickly away, taking lead on settling. Dropped back to box seat passing 1000m when crossed, then dropping to 3rd around turn. Boxed on gamely in straight.
Began well, quickly taken to fence, 3-back from leader. Left fence around turn, shaken up passing 300m, kept on gamely.
Pressed forward but three-wide, settling 2L from leader. Left without cover from 900m. Rolled forward to look a chance passing 300m, then one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from an outside draw, settling at rear. Shuffled back to last approaching turn, taken out to make run 300m, one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw and last on settling. Switched out approaching turn but only one-paced in straight.
Began OK, taken in, settling towards rear in one-off position. Raced fiercely approaching 600m then steadied from heels. One-paced in straight.
Bumped start, pressed forward, racing outside leader before taking over 1000m. Joined up front 300m, kept battling until flattened 100m.
Ridden early to hold forward position behind leader but shuffled 3L back passing 1200m. Left flat-footed 400m when pace quickened, then one-paced.
Ridden forward from outside draw, racing wide till getting cover first turn. Lost position back stretch, under pressure from 500m and dropped out quickly.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, in traffic mid-straight, came through a narrow opening inside 150M, dashed strongly to lead near line.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, brought wide 400M, closed off well for 2nd.
Soon led, pressed by rival passing 800M, fought on to maintain narrow lead in straight until headed by winner inside 50M.
Caught wide early stages, moved forward to press leader 800M, fought on well entering straight, not pace of leaders final stages.
Never far off from leaders, 3Ls off the pace 400M, kept up the chase on leaders on straightening but always held.
Chased leaders along the fence but had no clear run on straightening, not properly tested.
Tracked leaders 2-wide, had every chance leaving the bend, flattened out 100M.
Taken back from wide barrier, 2nd last 6Ls off the pace home turn, ran on moderately down outside, encouraging debut.
Held up towards the rear, 5Ls off the pace 400M, gave limited response only. (Lame next day)
Hustled along after the start, not far off, caught 3-wide no cover from 800M, one pace and weakened passing 200M. (Lame LF)
Settled down 3Ls back in midfield, unable to quicken when placed under pressure. (No Vet findings)
Taken back from wide barrier, outpaced in last 7Ls off leaders, didn't find any when asked, never in contention.
