Fast into stride, settling a length outside the leader, shared lead turning in, kicked clear in straight to score easily.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead easily, uncontested until near 400M, headed final 200M, stayed on for 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned a length or so back on rail in 3rd, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight to get 3rd.
Jumped well from the widest gate, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back in 4th, there to turn, ran on steadily to make frame.
Taken back to race 2 wide, 4 lengths back in 8th, same margin back turning, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, unbalanced near 1050M, same position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover in midfield, still 3 wide on turn, closed off one-paced.
Slowly away, lost right front plate near 1100M, raced at rear on rail, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail throughout, taken widest in straight and made minor progress.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 6 lengths or so back at rear, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield, crowded and lost ground near 1000M, similar position on turn, showed no response in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, made all.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, pace good, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to hold a spot 3 back on the fence, pace good, dashed well 200M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide just off the leader, ran on well until 150M flattened.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in final stages.
At back as usual, 2-3 wide, pace good, dashed well 200M.
Very slow away, at rear along the rails, pace good, lack turn of foot in straight.
Behind midfield along the fence, pace good, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up with the pace group, 2 wide, flattened 250M.
Very slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, pace good, no dash.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, pace good, no progress.
At back, trapped 3 wide, never improved.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at fast sectionals, kept on strongly until weakened over the last couple of strides, hung on to score by 1L.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, finished off well for 2nd.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite the fast pace, ran on steadily for 3rd.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, ran home nicely for 4th.
Failed to muster speed despite hard ridden along, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader along the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on fairly.
Pressed forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the fast pace, flattened over the last furlong.
Taken back, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, made some ground in straight. (Questioned for riding in straight)
Dropped out 2nd last, shuffled to tail 550m, switched out 500m & strong advance, quickened turning in, pressed lead 100m, led at line.
Lacked early toe, bustled near rear 1 off with cover, shaken up for progress 500m, driven into stretch, quickened to lead 150m, soon pressed & mugged at line.
Broke with others, raced midfield 1 off with cover, driven home turn, stayed on to 3rd without threatening.
Bustled & prominent, caught 3 wide no cover & niggled along, pushed on to 2nd 1 off 600m, driven to lead turning in, all out & headed 250m, tapered.
Started ok, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, advanced 600m to press lead turning in, driven 300m to lead 250m, emptied & headed 150m.
Moderate start & bustled along rail midfield, ridden turning in, plugged on one pace.
Sharp start & prominent on rail, settled 1 back 750m, shifted out & driven into stretch, one paced in run home.
Lacked toe & bustled early, raced rail behind midfield, behind heels & shuffled to last turning in, kept on moderately.
Led initially, soon headed, snagged 970m to handy 1 off with cover, ridden 400m, found little & soon weakened.
Taken back at start, detached at tail until closed up 700m, minor advance 3 deep 550m, very wide into stretch, found nil.
Broke well, led 3 deep 1000m, soon clear & to rail 750m, driven & headed turning in, weakened tamely.
Moderate start & bustled to settle behind midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 800m, driven 400m, widest into stretch, surged to lead 50m.
Awkward start, advanced wide to lead 1100m, to rail 1000m, 1L clear & shaken up turning in, kicked on, emptied 100m, headed close home.
Moderate start & niggled, settled fore of midfield on rail, niggled 650m, shifted out & driven 350m, stayed on for solid late inroads.
Reared start on rail, vied for lead until settled 1 back 1000m, 3rd & driven turning in, fought on dourly without threatening.
Restrained & bumped at break, raced midfield 1 off, shifted 3 deep 950m & advanced to close 2nd 700m, niggled 450m, boxed on in pursuit, emptied 150m.
Snagged start, trapped 3 wide no cover back of midfield, advanced with cover 950m to handy no cover 650m, 4th & driven turning in, tapered.
Bustled forward at break, sat fore of midfield 1 off with cover 500m, driven turning in, plugged on evenly centre track under.
Rousted start & outpaced, raced midfield on rail, under pump 600m, one-paced in tepid run home.
Taken back from widest, niggled along 2nd last, under pump 600m, kept on same speed.
Snagged early, raced rail near rear, ridden 550m tame run home.
Smart break & rolled to vie for lead, soon settled 1 back 1 off, niggled 5th 520m, found nil in stretch & eased.
Bustled wide initially, soon taken back, niggled at tail, tailed off turning in, no impression.
Initially behind midfield, strode forward to lead at 700M when pace slackened, ran on with ease to score.
Sent forward to take box-seat, shifted out away from the rail near 500M, kept pushing and took 2nd prior going to the line.
Rolled forward to share the lead, moved away from the rail to 2 wide at 900M, kept on well until headed inside 50M.
Eased back and travelled towards the rear, 4-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, made nice ground in the Straight.
Slotted into midfield along the rail, 3-3/4L off the lead, kept on one pace and did not seriously threaten.
Steadily eased to worse than midfield, 5L behind along the rail, slight dash after straightening, weakened 150M.
Raced in midfield, 2-3/4L off and went 3-4 wide and without cover near 800M, did not threaten.
Taken back and raced on the rail, 6-1/4L behind the leader, same pace and only ran past some tiring runners.
Eased back and raced at the tail, 4-1/2L off but travelled wide along the Back Straight, did not progress.
Hard ridden forward to cross and led, handed up passing 700M, couldn't find extra near 250M.
Raced prominently initially, settled front of midfield 2-3/4L behind 2 wide with cover, dropped off badly rounding turn.
Sat in front of midfield but trapped wide throughout, never ran on.
Pressed forward but 3-wide before settling midfield. Covered extra ground turn, very wide into straight, finished powerfully to win close home.
Jumped well, sliding into box seat and following leader to straight. Threw out challenged 350m, hit front 200m, run down close to line.
First out but eased behind the speed battle, sliding to rail 2-back from leader. Left fence on straightening and finished off nicely.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold fence 3-back from leader. Took inside run in straight and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began OK but hampered and taken out on passing 1100m, dropping to last. Made up some ground around turn, took inside run in straight before switching out passing 200m.
Hard ridden on jumping, surging into the front 1150m before crossing to fence. Collared approaching 200m and gave ground gradually.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover 3L from leader to turn. Taken very wide in straight, kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Began fairly, ridden along behind midfield but wide. Took turn 3-wide, kept on fairly to 200m before giving ground.
Jumped OK, not pushed, setting towards rear in one-off position, Severely hampered and taken very wide around home turn, dropping to last. Never a factor after that.
Slow into stride, then hung out 1100m. Continued to hang out around turn, dropping to rear. Never likely.
Began awkwardly, bumping twice, before pressing forward to race 2L from leader in one-off position. Shifted wider in straight and tired quickly final 200m.
Settled down in 6th, 4Ls off leader in a slowly run race, sprinted strongly to draw alongside leader final stages, got up near line.
From 12 quickly crossed to the lead, allowed easy lead in front, kept on well final 300M, just failed to hold off winner near line.
Close up in 4th, always within striking distance, loomed 250M, beaten off by first two 100M but held 3rd comfortably.
Tracked leader in slowly run race, had every chance leaving home turn, fought on same pace only.
In mid-division, 3Ls off the pace home turn, kept on same pace in straight, never a serious threat to first few.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, held up behind midfield 5Ls back, stayed on final 300M without threat to leaders.
Towards the rear 6-7Ls off the slow pace, not quickened to challenge when driven 400M, never in contention.
Chased leaders in 3rd, lacked a finishing response 300M, faded away mid-straight.
Dropped back to last over 8Ls behind leader, wide bid 500M, made only limited progress down outside.
Caught wide no cover behind midfield, found disappointingly little when asked, never reached contention.
Taken keen hold behind midfield, saved ground on fence but didn't respond to riding leaving home turn.
Settled near last over 7Ls off the pace, couldn't keep 400M, soon left behind.

Settled in midfield, commenced move entering home straight, 4-wide when close up turning in, fought on steadily to get up final strides.
Moderate start, settled in handy position far side, hit the front under pressure upon straightening only to be caught close to home.
Settled just worse than midfield, made steady headway out wide down far side to be prominent around the bend, one-paced from 3rd into straight.
Settled just better than midfield, steadied and lost position 1200 metres out, finished off race nicely from behind midfield into straight.
Driven to lead from the widest gate to obtain rails run first bend, led until narrowly headed halfway down back straight, chased leaders to home turn, one-paced.
Travelled wide in midfield, raced keenly far side before shuffled back to last few, produced good late impression.
Well back despite given reminders at the start, took closer order down far side to reach midfield before home bend, very wide entering straight, kept on without quickening.
Settled in last few, produced late impression past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Broke well from the middle gates, soon settled just off the pace on rails, shuffled back to 2L 6th coming out of back straight, found nil in the run home. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began from a poor gate, took up a handy position early stages, not far off in 5th around home bend, faded steadily under pressure in the run home.
Soon dropped well behind, only ran past beaten horses closing stages.
Settled just better than midfield on rails, carried slightly backward approaching home bend, found nothing in straight.
Worked early from a poor gate to keep in touch while very wide, improved far side to take up running at halfway mark, led until headed shortly after straightening, dropped away quickly.
Always in last few, soon tailed-off after straightening. (Irregular heart rhythm)
At back, 2 wide, pace good, unleashed strong finishing effort 300M to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, pace good, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, led 300M, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, overhauled 300M, flattened 100M.
Hard ridden early, midfield, 2 wide, pace good, made some ground 200M.
Pushed early, hold the rail in front of midfield, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, box seat, pace good, however no turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide no cover, pace good, ran on until 150M flattened.
At back, trapped 2-3 wide, pace good, ran on ok in straight.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, pace good, raced 3-4 wide, little dash 100M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, no progress.
Midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, emptied 400M.
Checked start, at rear, never nearer.
Never competitive at rear.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off strongly to score by a head.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on nicely until headed by the winner over the latter stages.
Pressed forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on steadily until weakened final 100M, just held for 3rd.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader, stayed on one pace without any extra acceleration, held for 4th.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, ran on gradually in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off steadily.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, made no impression in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until weakened final 100M.
At back, never in a competitive position throughout the trip.
At rear throughout, never looked competitive.
At back throughout, never ran on.
Jumped very awkwardly, always at rear, never a factor.
Taken back at start to rail 2nd last, strong traveler on turn, progress & switched out 370m, quickened smartly to lead 150m, driven to hold rival.
Taken back at start to rail midfield, niggled along, in pocket turning in, switched out 320m & shaken up, quickened to close 2nd 130m, held in duel.
Bustled at break to sit fore of midfield 1 off with cover, 3 deep & driven into stretch, advanced to 2nd 300m, all out to lead 180m, emptied & headed 150m.
Slow start & rousted to race rail behind midfield, niggled 650m, shifted 1 off 500m, driven into stretch & bumped rival 320m, stayed on without threatening.
Sharp start, led outright on rail 1400m, headed 1120m, continued to press & led 750m, 1L clear & kicked on into stretch, emptied & headed 200m, tapered.
Stumbled start & rousted at tail, shifted 3 deep 600m, very wide into stretch & driven, stayed on past beaten rivals.
Snagged at start to race near rear 1 off, off heels 930m & shuffled to 2nd last, flat-footed last turning in, responded for moderate inroads.
Broke ok but lacked early toe, parked rail fore of midfield, rolled to handy 1 back exiting backstretch, 3rd & driven turning in, tapered in run home.
Moderate start & bustled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven wide on turn, plugged on tepidly centre track.
Driven forward at start to press lead 3 wide no cover, edged lead 1000m & shifted 1 off, headed 750m, struggling 2nd 500m, emptied 300m & faded.
Broke well, battled to sit close up 1 off no cover, shuffled to one back one off 900m, niggled 520m, driven turning in, checked off heels 310m, no extra.
Broke with others, soon outpaced & rousted 3 wide with cover midfield, checked to 1 off 750m, under pump 500m & bumped 4 deep final turn, impeded 320m, no extra.
Moderate break, soon bustled to run midfield 1 off with cover, slid back a spot 850m, 3rd last & ridden 500m, struggled in weakening run.
Prominent 4 wide no cover, pressed lead until edged ahead 1120m, headed 1000m & backpedalled, soon bustled mid rank, found nil & tailed off.
Good break, sat handy 3rd 1 off no cover, pushed 3 deep 1300m, driven to challenge 430m, outkicked but kept on with grinding run to lead close home.
Awkward start, raced rail midfield, driven behind runners turning in, switched out 300m, rattled home centre track to claim 2nd.
Sharp break, rolled wide to lead 1st turn, eventually to rail 1400m, 0.5L up & driven 430m, surged 2L clear, peaked 150m, tapered & headed close home.
Smart start, niggled a touch to park rail fore of midfield, closed to slipstream leader 850m, driven 430m, closed to wire but always held.
Broke well, raced close 2nd no cover on fence until snagged to 1 back 1400m, edged 1 off no cover 1300m, pressed lead on turn, ridden 430m, one-paced.
Started ok but niggled along 3 wide with cover near tail, soon settled, shifted widest 550m, driven turning in, closed for minor inroads.
Tardy start, settled rail behind midfield, niggled a touch 1150m, snatched off heels 600m, shifted out & driven 400m, kept on for minor late headway.
Started ok, dropped in to back of midfield 3 wide with cover, shifted wider final turn & driven, kept on for moderate headway until tapered final 100m.
Prominent wide 1st turn, settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, ridden under pressure 400m, plodded on tepidly, squeezed up close home.
Missed break & bustled to settle last pair on rail, advanced a spot 800m & niggled, switched out & driven 400m, stayed on past beaten rivals.
Broke well, snagged to midfield 1 off with cover, overraced a touch 1650m, niggled 800m, driven into stretch & shifted out, plodded on tamely.
Bustled start & settled last pair 1 off, clear last 800m, shifted wide 550m & driven into stretch, plodded on ineffectively.
Shifted in at break, sat fore of midfield 3 wide no cover until checked off heels 1300m, shifted 4 wide & driven turning in, found nil & faded.
Broke ok, lacked toe & bustled back of midfield, overraced 1600m, snagged off heels 620m, found nil in stretch & soon beaten.
Prominent but raced wide initially, improved to share lead at 700M, kept going and held on to win by a nose.
Travelled at the rear, 8-1/4L behind 2 wide with cover, ran home strongly and just missed out on the prize by a nose.
Urged forward to take the rail and led, headed at 100M but still ran on okay.
Rolled forward into box-seat, held up most Straight until 150M, closed off well in final stages.
Slotted into midfield, 4-1/4L off the pace but trapped 3 wide and without cover, ran on fairly.
Raced in behind midfield, 5-3/4L behind trapped 3 wide with cover, improved steadily.
Pushed to settle midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 5L behind 2 wide with cover, run ended when checked at 150M.
Rolled forward to sit outside the leader until crossed at 700M, remained in touch until 250M.
Raced in behind midfield, 6-1/2L off 2 wide with cover, made ground despite being interrupted at 350M and 150M.
Rolled forward and took one-off one-back position, steadied 350M, one pace thereafter.
Eased back and travelled at the rear, 8-3/4L off on the fence, no progress.
Pushed to sit in midfield along the rail, 3-3/4L behind, never threatened.
Slightly slow start, sat in behind midfield 5-1/2L off along the rail, steadied 400M, did not run on.
First out, pressed forward but wide, crossing to fence 900m and stacking up field. Travelled strongly with head on chest to 300m when shaken up and pulled clear for comfortable win.
Began well, pressed forward, sitting 1L behind leader in one-off position. Shaken up top of straight to challenge but unable close gap to winner.
Began well, ridden to hold position one-back, one-off to straight when switched out to make challenge. Kept on well without threatening winner.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward looking for cover, slotting into one-off position three-back passing 1000m. Under pressure from 500m but kept on well to line.
Jumped OK, not pressed, settling midfield along rail. Left fence turning for home, blocked for run 300m, ran on steadily when clear.
Quickly away, holding rail inside leading pack before throwing head about when crossed 900m. Tailed leader to straight, not much room to 300m, one-paced when clear.
Ridden forward from an outside draw, racing fiercely 3-wide before settling behind midfield around turn. Very wide in straight, boxed on one-paced.
Began awkwardly and bumped, dropping towards rear in one-off position. Taken to rail around turn, took inside run in straight but only one-paced.
Pushed forward 3-wide to stay with pacemakers, but left without cover after 900m when 3L from leader. Continued to race wide entering straight, tiring noticeably after passing 200m.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, then shifted across to rail, settling at rear. Stayed on rail around turn and ran on fairly in straight.
Bumped start, pressed forward, settling 3-back along rail, Kept tabs on leaders to straight when came under pressure and gave ground gradually.
Crowded out start, steadied, and taken in, racing towards rear in one-off position. Shaken up entering straight but little response. Lame left front leg.
Began fairly, taken in from outside draw but held 3-wide at the rear. Very wide into straight, found nothing under hard riding.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear and gradually becoming detached from field. Never likely.
Chased runaway trio, moved strongly into contention 200M, kept on stoutly to go past weakening leader 100M.
In 5th, 4Ls off the strong pace, hung in and proved a difficult ride in straight, did well under the circumstances to claim 2nd final stages, not reached winner though.
From widest barrier shifted to a position behind midfield, 6Ls off the strong pace at 400M, closed off well to go 3rd near line.
Positively ridden from draw 12 but unable to cross the rivals on its inside, vied for lead 3-wide throughout, led 400M-100M, no extra final stages. (Jockey severely reprimanded for his handling.)
Behind midfield settled down 7-8Ls behind runaway leaders, inclined to lay out home turn, closed off steadily final 400M, encouraging debut.
In mid-division but couldn't get closer than 3-wide, 7Ls to make up 400M, ran on mildly without threat.
Settled 2-wide in midfield about 5Ls off the strong pace, kept on fairly, well held by leaders final 200M. (Bled.)
Slowly away, raced back in the field over 10Ls off the strong pace, took a while to get going entering straight, did best work late. (Jockey's riding came under notice.)
Positively ridden, vied for lead along the 2-path setting strong pace, kept on well early straight, run ended 150M, swamped by rivals late.
Held up in midfield along the rails, 5Ls to make up on leader 400M, not quickened under pressure, kept on same pace to line.
Not hurried, dropped back to last over 10Ls off the strong pace, gave limited response entering straight, not reach contention.
Soon led, proved very difficult to settle when being steadied passing 1000M, vied for lead setting strong pace, no extra inside 300M, weakened rapidly.
Towards the rear 10Ls off the strong pace, not picked up leaving the bend, soon left behind.

Pressed forward but wide to 1400m when shifted in and bumped, settling one-off, three-back. Switched out to challenge 400m, finished strongly to win close home. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began well, bumped near 1400M, ridden to stay with pacemakers before settling in slipstream of leading pair 1200m. Had dream run from 450m, hit front 300m, kept on well till run down final strides.
Began well, pressed forward to lead passing 1200m, overshadowed by outside runner 1000m, retook lead 600m, overtaken passing 300m but kept battling to line.
Punched forward from outside draw, racing wide till slotting in one-off, one-back passing 1000m. Rolled forward top of straight, steadied 200m, kept on gamely to line.
Began fairly, ridden to stay close to pace, settling 3-back at turn. Given reminders shortly after straightening but only one-paced to line.
No early pace, settling towards rear in one-off position. A little wide into straight, switched in 450m to get run, kept on gamely to line.
Jumped OK, not pressed, racing in midfield away from fence. Taken wide entering straight and ran on fairly without looking dangerous.
Allowed to stride at own pace, settling along fence behind midfield. Stayed close to fence throughout. Only one-paced in straight when put under pressure.
Began fairly, taken to face, settling at rear. Shuffled back to last turning for home, boxed on one-paced in straight.
Restrained on jumping, shifted across behind runners, and last on settling. Made some progress around turn but found nothing in straight.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, racing outside leader to 1000m before taking narrow lead. Overtaken entering straight and tired gradually.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw but held 3-wide towards rear on settling. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded.

Ridden along to find cover, shifting in passing 1200m but left without cover from 1100m. Under pressure soon after straightening and not ridden out final 200m, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Crowded on jumping, dropping back to sit behind midfield, 1 off the fence. 6L off the leaders as they rounded for home, ran strongly in the straight and flew late to take the win.

Lunged at the gates just before the kick, but stood flat footed, losing early ground. Pushed forward to sit just outside the leader by the 800m. Fading slightly, but looked to still be in control late before winner swooped.
Pushed forward initially before easing back at 1200m to settle 4th, on the rail. Held up early in the straight. Kicked strongly late and was running down 2nd in the closing stages.
Ok away and taken up early to settle just forward of midfield, on the fence. Hung in the straight, but still ran strongly, finishing off well and just missing a place late.

Only eased forward early to sit at the rear of the field, on the rail. Held up early in the straight, before cutting across heels near the 300m. Ran strongly from the 150m to get close in a tight finish.
Taken forward and settled handily in 5th, 1 off the fence. Ran solidly in the straight, but missed a big kick to figure in the close finish.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to sit 2nd/3rd, 1 off the fence. Always prominent in the run home, but was battling late and swamped in the tight finish.
Taken up early, before dropping back to sit midfield, 1 off the fence. 1 paced for the majority of the straight, before kicking in the last 100m to finish off OK late.

Dropped back from the kick to sit at the rear of the field. Raced keen from the 1200m before running onto heels at 1000m and racing wide with limited cover. Plugged away in the straight without threatening.
Bumped on jumping, and steadied back early to eventually sit last passing the 1200m. Only fully clear from the 250m, but only plugged away to the line.
Pushed forward from the wide draw to lead. Competitive at the 250m, before the tank ran dry and dropped out quickly. Vet reported blood in trachea.

Dropped back early to sit worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover. Looked to push forward at 500, but awkwardly placed on heels until 300. Came close to heels again late, but not going well enough to make an impact.
Cruised forward early and managed to get trapped 3 wide with no cover around midfield. Only fair in the straight and was eased out late.
Bumped and unbalanced early, before steadying to find a position around midfield on the rail. Never responded to riding in the straight.

Very sluggish at start, tailed-off to straight, showed a great turn of foot inside final 300 metres down the centre of the track, won going away.

Began well from a wide gate, worked his way to lead on rails passing the 1000m but soon joined on top of home bend, resisted challenge from the same horse throughout home straight, outclassed by winner final stages.
Jumped fairly, gradually improved down far side to join race leader on top of home bend, disputed the lead most of way down straight but unable to peg him back throughout. (Tactic questioned)
Broke well, settled in midfield on rails, soon came to challenge after straightening, only produced moderate progress under pressure.
Niggled at throughout far side travelling mainly in midfield to straight, finished off race nicely.
Ridden along in first few, settled just over 2L back in 4th on rails, kept on before coming one-paced closing stages.
Moderate start, raced wide behind midfield, wider entering straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped in air losing ground, travelled behind midfield, checked when racing keenly behind runners on home bend, one-paced in straight.
Soon dropped well behind, ran past well-beaten horses in straight.
Never far off to straight, folded up quickly after straightening.
Shaken up at start, close up briefly before gradually dropping towards last few coming out of back straight, no response under pressure in the run home.
Broke well before settling in mid-division, faded into straight.
Moderate start, travelled in last few on rails, found nothing in straight.
Began from a wide gate, raced wide in prominent position in back straight and around home bend, dropped away quickly from approaching home turn.
Took lead easily, pace good, hung on strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Pushed forward, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward to cross towards outer part of track, pace good, ran on until 250M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, checked early, pace good, no dash.
At back, pace good, ran on ok on inner part of track.
Hard ridden but not muster, checked early, pace good, ran on ok on inner part of track in final stages.
Eased back, pace good, no progress.
Checked early, midfield, pace good, no turn of foot on inner part of track.
Very slow away, hard ridden throughout to keep up with the field, no progress.
Hard ridden to keep up midfield, pace good, emptied 400M.
Very slow away, pace good, never improved on inner part of track.
Very slow away, not competitive.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly to score by 1.5Ls.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at slow tempo, kept on nicely until headed by the winner final 100M.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite the slow pace, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Pressed forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L at slow sectionals, kept on until weakened over the final furlong.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace to the line.
Pushed forward to settle in a prominent position, however, trapped wide without cover throughout, one paced only.
At back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, despite the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Settled midfield, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, made no impression in straight.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, found nothing when asked. (Roarer)
Always at back, never a factor.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along throughout, never looked likely, tailed out.
Smart break, bustled up to slot fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shaken up & shifted out 500m, driven for grinding inroads centre track, led close home.
Fast start widest, crossed to park 1 off 1 back, shifted out home turn, driven 400m, vied for lead & edged narrow advantage 150m, headed close home.
Missed break, bustled up to sit rail behind midfield, shifted 1 off 800m, ridden 500m, closed off centre track to claim 3rd.
Broke well, niggled initially to rail fore of midfield, switched out 500m but trapped in pocket, driven 200m, blocked 150m, clear run close home & closed too late.
Good break & prominent early, settled 1 back on rail, switched out 400m, driven 300m to press lead, vied for advantage until faded final 50m.
Lacked toe from wide gate & taken to tail, advanced a spot 650m, switched out final turn, shaken up centre track 360m, closed for sound headway.
Prominent early, taken back to rail midfield, driven 350m but trapped in pocket on fence, clear final 50m & plugged on.
Missed break & rousted near rear 1 off with cover, hard-ridden final turn & widest into stretch, stayed on for minor inroads.
Speed to lead, soon to rail, narrow lead turning in, shaken up 400m & kicked 1.5L clear, all out & pressed 200, headed 150m, tapered.
Started well, settled midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 500m & shifted out, plodded on tamely.
Smart start to race 2nd 1 off, shaken up to press lead 500m, emptied 350m, weakened tamely.
Moderate start, settled back of midfield 1 off with cover, edged 3 deep 800m, driven wide home turn, struggled in run to wire.
Outpaced at break & raced 2nd last 1 off, shuffled to tail to rail 600m, shifted put final turn & driven 400m, tepid run home.
Missed break, bustled forward to midfield 3 wide no cover, driven turning in but found nil & weakened.
Smart break, restrained to handy 3 back on fence, progress to slipstream leader 900m, shifted out & driven 400m, grinding run to lead 140m, drew clear.
Moderate start, raced rail midfield, shaken up 400m, stayed on for dour gains down inner to claim 2nd close home
Broke ok to sit 1 off with cover midfield, raced keenly under restraint, advanced a spot on turn, ridden 500m, shadowed winner to go 2nd 110m, tapered last strides.
Lacked toe & bustled 3rd last detached from pack, advanced to rail behind midfield 1000m, niggled 650m, driven 430m, kept on for solid gains.
Sluggish break, niggled along detached 2nd last, joined main group 850m, driven turning in, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke ok, taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, widest into stretch & driven, stayed on for minor inroads.
Started ok, raced midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out final turn, driven 300m, closed late for minor headway.
Bustled forward & to rail, parked 1 back, edged 1 off no cover 1000m, close 3rd turning in, driven to lead 420m, soon 1.5L clear, emptied 200m, headed 140m & swamped.
Started well, parked 3 deep no cover 3rd & overraced, given its head 800m to lead 700m, headed 420m & faded.
Early pace, restrained to track handily but trapped 4 wide no cover & overraced, slotted in 3 deep 800m, wide into stretch, plugged on tamely.
Tardy start, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 900m & shuffled back, shaken up 420m, checked & switched in 370m, kept on tepidly.
Smart start & rousted to lead, to rail 1100m, headed 700m but continued to vie for advantage, driven 430m, tapered in run home.
Good start wide, snagged to midfield wide no cover, slotted in 3 deep 1000m, wide into stretch, one-paced & impeded 330m, no extra thereafter.
Taken back from widest gate to race detached at tail, under pump 600m, found nil, tailed off.
Travelled behind the lead, 1-3/4L off the pace on centre track, drifted away at 150M to score.
Race behind the leaders, 1L behind stand side, held up until 100M, finished off strongly thereafter.
Pressed forward and sat just off the speed on the stand rail, ran on gamely and just missed out on 2nd.
Ridden forward and shared lead on stand side, kept on well until 200M, held on for 4th.
Eased to settle at the rear, 6-3/4L behind stand side, made ground steadily from 400M.
Sent forward, shared lead on centre track, kept on until 200M when couldn't find extra.
Raced in midfield, 3L behind the leaders on centre track, ran on only one pace.
Travelled in midfield, 2-3/4L behind stand side, remained one pace to the line.
Pushed forward and shared lead, remained on stand side, out of steam passing 250M.
Raced centre track, initially behind the leaders, improved to share lead at 600M, ran on until 200M weakened.
Awkward start and taken back, initially 5-1/2L off stand side, shifted to centre track at 500M, made slight ground.
Always at the tail end, did not improve.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4L behind stand side, never threatened.
In midfield, 3L behind on the stand rail, steadied 300M, did not run on thereafter.
Began well, racing one-off behind pace around first turn. Lost position back stretch, shuffled further back final turn, swung wide then finishing strongly to win close home.
Restrained on jumping and shifted in, settling at rear in one-off position. Taken 3-wide back stretch, then 4-wide from 600m to go forward. Hit front 200m, hung in 100m, kept battling.
Quickly into stride but eased to sit 2-back behind the pace first turn. Travelled smoothly to 450m, angled out to make run but shifted back in and finished strongly to miss narrowly.
Jumped with field, shifted in to find cover but held 3-wide in midfield. Kept wide back stretch, bumped entering straight, boxed on gamely down centre track to just miss a place.
Jumped with field, restrained, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Took inside run on straightening and finished well though blocked for run final 100m and not ridden out.
Quickly into stride, grabbed rail and led narrowly to 1350m when passed and settled in box seat. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance 200m before swamped final strides.
Crowded out start, taken to rail, settling 4-back behind midfield. Blocked on run top of straight, stayed close to rail and finished off nicely.
Began well, bumped and unbalanced approaching first turn before slotting into one-off position behind midfield. Blocked for run 500m, wide into straight, boxed on gamely.
Ridden early to find cover but held 4-wide passing 1700m and allowed to roll forward to lead 1350m. Set strong pace to 200m when flattened and gave ground gradually.
Began fairly, checked, dropping towards rear but wide. Kept wide along back stretch, taken wider around final turn, boxed on gamely in straight.
Bumped start, pressed forward, chased leader to 1400m before easing out of pace battle, settling 3-back, one-off. Under pressure soon after straightening and boxed on one-paced.
Restrained, shifted across behind runners to rail, settling towards rear. Caught in traffic early in straight and awkwardly placed closing stages.
Bumped and shifted out start, pressed forward but very wide, settling 3L behind leader back stretch when left without cover. Covered extra ground turn, boxed on to 200m before tiring.
Jumped well, rolled forward, sharing pace to back stretch before settling 2.5L back in one-off position. Under pressure turning for home, weakened badly in straight. Unacceptable performance.
Towards the rear and no closer than 3-wide throughout, 4Ls off leader 400M, quickened up strongly to lead near 150M, won going away.
Urged along after the start, crossed to the lead 900M, kept on well when driven out 300M but not pace of winner final 150M, held on to 2nd from unlucky 3rd.
Held up 2-wide behind midfield, 4Ls off the pace 400M, no clear run until passing 200M, did best work late closing on the runner up with every stride.
Settled down 3-4Ls off the pace, responded readily to pressure, lay in early straight, clipped heels and blundered, responded readily to pressure final 250M, not reach winner though.
Dropped back to the rear, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, no clear run early straight, stayed on well final 200M.
Contested lead early, eased back to 4th entering home turn, kept on steadily under pressure, flattened final 100M.
Held up towards the rear, saved ground on the inside, 5Ls behind leader 400M, switched out for clear run, stayed on mildly and not serious threat to leaders.
4-5Ls back in midfield along the inside, kept on fairly entering straight, not pace to challenge leaders.
Not mustered pace , ended up in last 8Ls off leader, switched 3-wide 650M, ran on fairly down outside of straight.
Went forward, tracked leader 2-wide, unable to quicken entering straight, gave way 250M. (Jockey : raced flat.)
Settled down in midfield, wide no cover after 1000M, crept closer to pace home turn, every chance, weakened 150M.
Taken back from wide draw, near the rear 7Ls off the pace, proved difficult to settle 900M, inclined to lay in when driven out in straight, checked 200M, lacked further response towards finish.
In 5th about 3-4Ls off leader, found no extra passing 300M, soon beaten.
Vied for early lead, tracked leader from 900M, no extra and gave way rapidly inside 300M.
Began well, beaten for pace, settling in box seat 2L from leader. Closed in steadily around turn, switched out 350m to make challenge, vigorously ridden to win on the line.
Jumped OK, restrained and taken back looking for cover, settling one-off towards rear. Began forward move 350m, picked up steam 200m, finished strongly to just fail.
Hard ridden to hold rail inside leader to and around turn. Kicked ahead 350m, kept finding under intense pressure final 200m, to be beaten on line.
Slow into stride, dropping to rear but holding rail. Made progress around turn, stayed on rail in straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began awkwardly losing ground, then pressed forward, settling 3L from leader at turn. Kept on gamely in straight without threatening.
Ridden vigorously between horses to hold forward position but started to over-raced and eased one-back, one-off 700m. Kept on well to 200m before tiring.
Steadied soon after start, shifted across behind horses and last on settling. Made up ground around turn, took inside run in straight and kept on fairly.
Jumped OK, pressed forward, settling midfield in one-off position. Got shuffled back around turn and one-paced in straight.
Began OK but beaten for early pace, gradually dropping back. Last into straight, boxed on one-paced.
Pressed forward from an outside draw, racing 3-wide without cover mostly. Lost position around turn, plodded in straight.
Hard ridden from outside draw to take lead passing 800m but kept away from fence by inside runner. Under pressure soon after straightening and faded.
Hard ridden to hold forward position, racing wide without cover 2L from leader before losing position around turn. Gave ground quickly in straight. Lame left front leg.

Eased back early and stuck 4-5 wide early around midfield. Pushed forward from the 1000m to lead by the 800m. Pushed hard in the straight, and looked beaten at 50m, before kicking again late and just holding on.
Pressed forward early, but couldn't find cover and left 3 wide with no cover in midfield. Came forward to be 2nd on the turn, challenging winner. Nosed in front 100, but winner kicked again.
Pushed forward early, settling midfield, 1 off the fence. Became unsettled and checked off heels at 1100m, and lost ground. Came wider on the turn and ran strongly to the line, holding 3rd late.
Taken forward early to be early leader, before eventually settling 3rd. Drifted back rounding the home turn, before running on again in the straight. Strong late, closing hard on 3rd on the line.
Taken forward early to be handily placed 4th, 1 off the fence and 2.5L off the leader. Pressed forward with the winner at 500m, and sat 3rd until the 100m, before running out of puff late.

Taken forward early to be handily placed, before easing back mid race to sit forward of midfield. Looked to be finished and was losing ground at 500m. Ran strongly over the last 200m, gaining ground quickly.

Hampered and lost ground on jumping, eventually settling around midfield, on the rail. Awkward on heels from 800m, before being checked and unbalanced at 700m and lost ground. Wider on the turn and ran on OK late.
Taken forward early, sitting wide early before settling 2nd, 1 off the fence and 1L off the leader. Went to the line 1 paced in the straight.

Eased forward early to take a position at the rear of the field, on the rail. Pushed forward to be midfield by 800, before being bumped and losing some ground at 700m. Came off heels 250m, and solid to the line late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last, 1 off the fence and 7L off the leader. Last at 200m, and plugged to the line fairly late.

Hampered on jumping and lost ground, but still managed to push forward and find a position forward of midfield, on the fence. Under pressure before the straight and ran flat in the straight. Vet-cut to off hind tendon.
Stuck widest, without cover early from the 14 barrier before pushing forward to lead by the 1000m. Under pressure before the turn, dropped out in the straight and eased late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit at the rear of the field, 3-4 wide with limited cover. No kick in the straight, and eased to the line late.

Began awkwardly and didn't muster early, settling towards the back of the field, 3-4 wide with cover. Awkward on heels and got head up at 800. Began to run on early in the straight, but faded quickly from 300m, easing late.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, travelled well on turn, took the lead near 200M, kept on well to score.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off strongly to get 2nd.
Jumped well from a wide draw, showed early speed to take the lead, still uncontested on turn, headed near 200M, stayed on for 3rd. (Lost right front plate near 500M.)
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still well back on turn, angled out early in straight and made good progress to make frame. (See racing incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, finished off evenly. (See racing incidents.)
Away with them, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after turning in, finished off evenly without threatening.
Slowly away, recovered to race 2 lengths or so back on rail in 5th, there to turn, angled out early in straight and finished off evenly.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced wide and without cover throughout, finished off one-paced. (See racing incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in 4th, still no cover on turn, weakened gradually after turning in.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away well, taken back to race 5 lengths back at rear, same margin back on turn, finished off one-paced.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, weakened after 600M, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Ridden along from the widest gate from forward of midfield to settle 3-wide in 3rd with the leaders, hit the front under pressure 200 metres out and just held on to the line.

Moderate start, raced 3 lengths back on rail, came closer rounding home bend but didn't find much room early in straight, fought on doggedly closing stages while shifting ground to just fail to get up on line.
Taken back to race in rear from a poor gate, trailed the field to the straight, ran on well under pressure near the centre of the track.
Settled at the back on rails, finished off race well, did best work late.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide in 5th, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight, raced tight and carried wider after 200M, finished off evenly.
Began well from the one draw holding narrow lead on rails most of way to straight, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Ridden along to share the pace hitting front briefly in back straight, held every chance early in home straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Raced wide better than midfield after beginning from a wide draw, remained in similar position when 3-wde in 6th turning in, ran home one-paced.
Moderate jump, niggled along early stages in maintain position in mid-division, slightly worse coming out of back straight, produced good late impression final stages despite tight between runners.
Soon dropped to last few despite ridden along, never seen with a chance.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled in rear of midfield, baulked for a run after straightening, one-paced under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Moderate start, travelled within striking distance of 2L back on rails most of way before overhauled inside final 200 metres. (Blood in trachea next day)
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
At back along the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 300M, progressed steadily when clear.
Settled in box seat, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, took rail and lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on until 150M flattened.
At rear, along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, no turn of foot in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, 2 wide, never nearer.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, reduced quickly 400M.
Hard ridden forward, checked early, emptied 300M.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Sent forward to lead along the fence, kept on strongly to score by only a nose.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on strongly to miss by only a nose in a tight finish.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, dashed well for 3rd in a tight finish.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on steadily for 4th without threatening.
Eased back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung wide turning in, made plenty of ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced home.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat from gate 7, kept on one pace until weakened over the last furlong.
Taken back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
At rear throughout, made minor ground in straight.
Settled midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on fairly until weakened final 250M.
Camped handy, however, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Led early, to rail 1400m & headed 1220m, settled 1 back & overraced 1050m, driven turning in & switched out 300m, hard-ridden to lead 40m, just held on.
Broke ok to park back of midfield 1 off, overraced 950m, fanned wide & driven home turn, closed strongly, just failed.
Crowded start & raced rear rank 3 wide with cover, driven very wide home turn, stormed centre track for headway to 3rd.
Tardy break, rousted wide to press lead 1st turn, led 1220m & to rail 1150m, set steady tempo, driven under pressure 380m, dug in & forged on, emptied & swamped close home.
Squeezed up at start & raced at tail until wide advance from 1120m to sit close-up 730m, driven 2nd 380m, pressed lead until emptied 100m, tapered.
Broke ok, raced fence near rear, checked off heels 950m & switched 1 off, niggled 500m, driven & shifted out final turn, boxed on for minor inroads.
Moderate start, raced near rear until switched 3 deep & advanced a spot 900m, overraced & shifted 4 wide no cover until tucked in 650m, wide home turn, kept on.
Smart break & prominent early settled midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 600m, shifted wide & driven home turn, buffeted in stretch run, one-paced.
Started ok, raced rail midfield, shuffled to back of midfield 800m, bustled 600m, shifted out 400m & driven, buffeted in stretch run, not clear & checked 60m, one-paced.
Minor bump early, rolled to sit back of midfield on rail, checked off heels 1000m & overraced 900m, shuffled to rear rank, ridden into home turn, kept on evenly.
Bustled from gate, raced 3 wide no cover midfield, niggled 550m, driven wide home turn, plodded home tamely.
Broke well & prominent, settled handy 1 off no cover, niggled 500m, under pump 400m, found nil & weakened out.
Fast break, raced handy 1 off with cover, shifted 3 deep & niggled 400m, driven into stretch, quickened to lead 180m, drew clear.
Speed wide & driven to lead 1090m, to rail 950m, 1L clear & shaken up turning in, all out & headed 180m, kept battling but tapered.
Outpaced initially, bustled to settle back of midfield, edged 3 deep 750m, niggled 500m, driven very wide into stretch, closed to make frame late.
Outpaced early stages, settled back of midfield 1 off, driven into stretch & shifted out, stayed on for late headway.
Broke ok, raced midfield 3 deep no cover, advanced 800m to press lead 650m, slotted 1 off, ridden 400m, soon all out, tapered.
Sharp start, snagged back to park 3 back on rail, shifted off fence home turn, ridden 300m, switched out 200m, one paced in run home.
Lacked early toe & rousted, settled rail near rear, bustled 520m, plugged on for minor inroads.
Led at break, headed 1090m & raced 1 back on fence, overraced & steadied off heels 700m, driven into stretch, faded in run home.
Taken back from wide gate, soon niggled to sit 3 wide with cover back of midfield, checked off heels 780m, hard-ridden turning in, plodded one pace.
Broke with others, soon niggled to rail at rear of pack, shifted 1 off for progress 750m, steadied 430m, not clear & checked 250m, no extra.
Missed break & raced 5L adrift of main pack, ridden to join tail turning in, soon emptied, never a factor.
Taken back to midfield from wide gate & trapped 4 wide no cover, advanced 820m to sit handy 3 deep, driven 380m, found nil & faded weakly.
Sent forward to take rail and led by 1-1/4L, continued well in the lead and finished off with ease to score by 2-1/2L.
Settled in midfield, 3L off 2 wide with cover, improved gradually and hit the line well for 2nd.
Raced in midfield along the rail, 3-3/4L behind the leader, finished off well inside final 150M for 3rd.
Slotted in just behind midfield, 4-3/4L off 2 wide with cover, closed off well after switching wide at 250M for clear running.
Travelled in midfield, 3-3/4L behind 3 wide with cover, kept on only one pace to the line.
Niggled forward to race prominently but wide and without cover throughout, weakened gradually in the Straight.
Eased back and raced at the rear, 6-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, made slight ground in the Straight.
Pushed forward and raced outside the leader, 1-1/4L off the pace, remained in touch until weakened 150M.
Travelled in midfield, 5-1/4L behind the leader and stayed widest throughout, taken out at 250M, did not run on.
At the rear and detached by 9-1/4L, made slight ground in the Straight.
Awkward start and consequently had to race at the rear, did not improve.
Rolled forward to take box-seat, sat 2-1/4L behind, weakened badly passing 200M.
Began well but not pushed, settling 3-back first turn. Not asked for an effort until passing 450m when urged forward, hitting front 200m and then finding more when challenged.

No early pace, settling towards rear. Taken wide to go forward around final turn, loomed alongside leader 200m, battled strongly but just failed. Stipes reported jockey had restricted use of whip closing stages.
Hard ridden from an outside draw to get a forward position, settling one-off, three-back at first turn. Ran on steadily in the straight to grab 3rd position on the line.
Pressed forward on jumping to share early lead, before settling three-parts of a length behind leader. Rolled forward around turn, joint leader 200m, no extra final stages.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear along rail. Switched out around final turn to go forward, taken to centre track in straight, ran on steadily without threatening.

Crowded out start, pushed forward inside leading pack before taking lead 1000m and slowing pace. Picked up momentum from 800m, boxed on to 200m before tiring. Restricted action behind and sore over the quarters.
Slow to move, hard ridden to go forward, racing 4-wide before getting cover first turn 2L from leader. Kept tabs on leading pack to straight, then one-paced.
Beaten for early pace, racing at rear to 900m when forced to switch out to avoid horse being pulled up. Kept wide around turn, taken to centre track in straight, boxed on one-paced.
Began well, pushed forward, settling two-back from leader. Lost position around turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped with field, holding rail and settling in midfield. Got shuffled back to last around turn and only one-paced in straight under hard riding.

Began fairly, urged forward then steadied 1500m when kept wide. Made long forward move from 1300m, looping field back stretch to get 3rd entering straight when flattened, finishing tailed out. Unacceptable performance.

Placing: PU
Comment: Slow into stride, taken to fence, and made up some ground around first turn before breaking right front leg 900m and pulled up.
Broke well, restrained in midfield along inside, switched out into clear 250M, quickened strongly to lead 80M out, won going away.
Rushed along after the start, led 900M at good pace, continued on well entering straight, headed by impressive winner near 80M, held 2nd comfortably.
Settled down behind midfield 4Ls off the good pace, severely checked near 250M, regrouped and kept on late under top weight, went 3rd before line.
Never far off leader but 3-wide no cover from 800M, moved into contention nearing top of straight, advanced to 2nd 250M, one paced and no impression on leaders final 100M, lost 3rd late.
Chased leaders in 4th, kept on fairly final 300M and not going the pace to challenge leaders.
In mid-division 5Ls off the pace, driven wide passing 400M, ran on only fairly, never troubled leaders.
Given a waiting ride, 6-7Ls towards the rear, brought wide into straight, gave limited response only.
In mid-pack 4Ls off the good pace, kept on same speed only passing 300M, never threatened.
Driven forward from wide draw, prompted the pace, couldn't sustain run passing 300M, weakened towards the finish.
Towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, not picked up entering straight, made no impression on debut.
Unhurried, detached last 9Ls off the pace middle stages, made no progress in straight, never a factor.
Away quickly, chased leaders in 3rd, lacked further response inside 250M, dropped away. (Blood in trachea / Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Began fairly, then crowded, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Shifted to rail around turn, shaken up on straightening, found gap 150m out and powered home to win on the line.
Jumped with field, pressed forward to race one-back, one-off. Turned a little wide, picked up momentum from 200m, finished strongly to just fail.
Hard ridden from outside draw, racing 4-wide outside leading pack before settling outside leader 900m. Rolled forward on straightening, hit front 200m, run down on line.
Jumped well, not pushed, settling 3L from leader in one-off position. Lost position around turn, got going again on straightening and finished strongly.
Began OK, ridden but didn't muster, settling midfield in one-off position. Swung wide into straight, picked up momentum why laying in 200m, raced tight concluding stages and not ridden out.
Beaten for early pace, dropping behind midfield in one-off position. Taken a little wide entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began well, used inside draw to hold rail, settling in taking box seat. Closed in turning for home to look a chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Checked when crowded out at start, dropping to last in one-off position. Stayed at rear to straight where ran on fairly.
Began fairly, then crowded out, dropping to rear along rail. Shuffled back to last around turn and found nothing in straight.
Began OK, taken to fence, settling 5L from leader. Put under pressure turning for home, boxed on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Pressed forward three-wide before taking over lead 1000m and crossing to fence. Collared approaching 200m and faded. Lame left front leg.

Jumped fairly, settled in rear of midfield on rails, switched out for a run entering straight, ran on well under pressure to assert authority closing stages while hanging in throughout.
Soon took up running, led until joined by two runners around the bend, kicked about 3L clear 200 metres out but soon flattered, caught inside final 50 metres.
Sluggish at start and soon dropped to tail-end, trailed the field to straight, finished off race well between runners down the inside of the track.
Crowded at start dropping to last few, commenced move rounding home bend, made up good ground from 10th into straight to be nearest at finish.
Ridden along to hold prominent position, steadied to just over 2L back in 4th rounding home bend, kept on at the one pace under pressure to the finish.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled 2-wide in rear of midfield, unable to quicken under pressure in straight.
Given reminders at the start from a wide gate, worked his way forward to join the leaders coming onto home bend sharing the pace to straight, soon tired after racing wide throughout.
Began from a wide draw, ridden along when wide in first few before hampered, dropped to 6th about 4L off the pace turning in, ran home one-paced.
Gradually dropped towards the rear despite ridden along, remained in last few turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Gradually dropped to last few after beginning from the widest gate, saved ground on rails turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Crowded at start but ridden to soon join the leaders, lost touch under pressure shortly after straightening.
Moderate start, soon recovered along rails to better than midfield reaching within 3L of speed around home bend, weakened under pressure after straightening. (Lame)
Settled in forward of midfield, badly hampered passing the 800 metres dropping well back, never recovered.
Wide in prominent position when clipped heels, blundered and lost ground passing the 800 metres, dropped to near last entering straight.
Settled in midfield on the fence, pace good, closed off strongly 300M to score.
At rear at usual, pace good, 3-5 wide, made early move 600M around the field, just beaten by narrow margin in 2nd.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back, trapped 2-4 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M.
Hard ridden forward to cross, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 300M, ran on ok.
Settled in prominent spot, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 400M, flattened 150M.
Hard ridden early, at back along the rails, pace good, just ran on ok in straight.
At rear, along the fence, pace good, made minor ground 300M, checked badly 200M, ran on ok.
Midfield, pace good, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide in the lead, pace good, out of fuel 250M.
Took rail and lead easily, pace good, hung on until 300M emptied.
Behind midfield, never nearer.
Never a competitive at rear.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, dashed strongly to score by 1-3/4Ls.
Pressed forward to take the fence and share the lead, kept on gamely until headed by the winner final 50M.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, made early moved rounding the Home Turn, kept on strongly until weakened over the concluding stages for 3rd.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily for 4th.
Taken back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, was held up until final 250M, ran on nicely thereafter.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, ran on steadily until weakened final 100M.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in the straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on and passed some tired horses only.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, however, was checked 350M, never ran on thereafter.
Camped handy, travelled 1L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, one paced until final 250M weakened.
Hard ridden to settle midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Failed to muster early, moved forward to park outside the leader gradually from 1200M, weakened soon after straightening. (Roarer)
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, dropped off rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Ridden forward, however, trapped wide without cover throughout, well beaten rounding the Home Turn.
Speedy break & initially bustled in 2nd, led 1off 920m, clear & to rail 780m, pressed & driven 430m, headed 350m, rallied to nick win on nod.
Dashed to lead on rail, headed 920m, 1L 2nd & shifted 1 off to challenge 520m, cruised upsides & driven to narrow lead 350m, unable to impose, emptied 50m & headed at post.
Smart start, raced 2.5L 3rd on rail, edged 1 off 520m, ridden 420m, boxed on & closed to wire but never a threat.
Broke ok, sat fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven 520m, boxed on dourly for minor late headway.
Bustled at break to race rail fore of midfield, driven 520m, plugged on for even inroads.
Missed break & bustled forward to race midfield on rail, niggled 550m, shifted out & driven turning in, kept on for one-paced inroads.
Tardy start, raced rail behind midfield, niggled 800m & driven into stretch, boxing on when impeded 300m, one-paced thereafter.
Broke well, restrained wide fore of midfield, soon rolled to clear 4th & slotted rail 800m, shifted 1 off 500m & driven 430m, kept on one pace.
Broke well, taken back to race a touch keen midfield 1 off with cover, switched wide final turn, niggled for minor progress, hard-ridden 300m, soon emptied & tapered.
Moderate break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven wide into stretch, tepid run home.
Missed break & stumbled, rousted on rail to settle near rear, niggled 500m & driven into stretch, plodded on same speed.
Tardy start, raced near rear 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, found little in tame run to wire.
Slow start & rousted initially to race 2nd last, niggled along, driven final turn, struggled in weak run home.
Restrained from widest gate to race at tail, shifted 3 deep & driven 550m, unable to make noticeable inroads, never a factor.
Taken back to settle 4th last 1 off, switched 3 deep 650m & shaken up 420m, switched inside & checked off heels 300m, quickened smartly, led 50m.
Prominent at break, soon outpaced & bustled to settle rail fore of midfield, ridden 450m & quickened to lead 230m, all out & headed 50m.
Tardy start, niggled rail back of midfield until bustled forward a spot 950m, driven into stretch, gradual closer to claim 3rd.
Snagged start & crossed to rail near rear, overraced 870m, shifted out turning in & driven, checked inside 300m, stayed on for minor late headway.
Smart start, restrained to handy rail berth & overraced, shifted out & driven home turn, boxed on one-pace, drifted & checked off heels140m, plugged on.
Speed to lead, clear & to rail 880m, 2L clear turning in, shaken up 360m, all out & headed 230m.
Taken back at start to behind midfield 3 wide no cover, advanced 700m, driven widest in stretch, kept on evenly.
Started ok, raced midfield on rail, edged 1 off 1000m, shifted out final turn & driven, switched inside 350m, not clear run 300m, one-paced.
Smart break & prominent, eased back 1200m to handy 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven 430m, one-paced & checked 180m, no extra.
Outpaced & soon 2L detached at tail, close up turning in & driven, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Moderate start & bustled widest, slotted fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shuffled back a spot 880m, ridden wide on turn, emptied 300m, impeded 250m & faded.
Broke well & bustled from wide gate, raced handy 3deep no cover, niggled 600m, hard-ridden into stretch, emptied 300m & weakened.
Sharp break, raced 2nd 1 off no cover, 2L down & shaken up turning in, soon hard-ridden, emptied 320m & faded.
Taken back from wide gate to race 1 off near tail, niggled along, under pump 500m, struggled in run home.
Ridden forward to take the rail and led at quick sectionals, kept on going to the line and scored by 2L.
Travelled just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind 2 wide with cover, finished off nicely when cleared at 350M.
Rolled forward to take box-seat, despite not suited to the fast pace, stayed on gamely, only lost out on 2nd inside final 50M.
Settled just fore of midfield, 3-1/4L off 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast pace but still ran on well for 4th.
Rolled forward and raced 3rd 1 off, not suited to the quick tempo, remained in touch until couldn't find extra at 150M.
Eased back, travelled 7L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered 400M, made ground steadily thereafter.
Slow start and at the rear, 6-3/4L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo but one paced home.
Travelled in midfield, 4-1/4L behind but trapped wide and without cover, slight dash before 200M only.
Raced in front of midfield, 2-3/4L off 3 wide without cover, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off gradually.
No early speed and had to race in midfield 3-1/2L behind along the rail, not suited to the fast pace, did not threaten.
Settled towards the rear along the rail, 6L behind the leader, swung wide at the exit, checked at 400M, did not run on.
Raced just behind midfield, 4-1/2L behind the leader 3 wide with cover, run ended when taken out at 400M.
Initially at the rear but improved to midfield rounding turn, never looked likely in the Straight.
Jumped OK, allowed to stride forward at own pace, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Switched wide on entering straight and ran on strongly to win close home.

Pressed forward from wide draw to lead passing 1400m, pulling 2L clear 1000m before crossing to fence and slowing pace. Kicked ahead 400m and kept finding when challenged before losing in final strides.
Jumped with field, not pushed, settling along fence in midfield. Switched wide on straightening and finished strongly to grab minor placing.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-back, one-off 3L from leader approaching turn. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance before flattened final stages.
Shifted out abruptly at start and bumped, dropping towards rear in one-off position. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished off strongly.
Steadied on jumping, shifted across behind runners and last on settling. Taken very wide entering straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward, racing wide 2L from leader to turn. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance 200m when steadied, then one-paced.
Began well, taken to box seat, then kept tabs on pacemakers to straight. Kept on fairly to 200m before tiring.
Outpaced soon after start, then taken to rail, settling at rear. Came off fence entering straight and kept on fairly under hard riding.
First to jump, then ridden along inside pace makers, before settling 2nd, 2L from leader at 900m. Closed to within a half length passing 400m before tiring.
Shifted out and bumped at start, ridden to make up ground but tightened 1400m. Hampered 1200m when trying to improve, dropping behind midfield along fence. One-paced in straight.
Began fairly, ridden to find cover but trapped wide and allowed to roll forward from 1400m, swooping around field to place 3rd passing 900m. Spent force on straightening and weakened gradually.
Steadied on jumping and shifted across behind runners, settling towards rear in one-off position. Tired quickly soon after straightening and finished tailed out. Unacceptable performance.
Settled down behind midfield along the rails, crept closer to pace home turn, came through inside 250M, quickly dashed to the front under top weight, kept on strongly to win in class record time.
Waited with in the rear, challenged down outside passing 400M, ran on well to go 2nd 200M, couldn't get on terms with the impressive HELENE PARAGON.
Held up at the rear, stayed on moderately to go 3rd near finish, no impression on winner though.
Chased leaders, kept on steadily on straightening, held 3rd until concluding stages.
Share lead on the inside, couldn't find extra when hard pressed 300M, shifted out abruptly near 200M, one paced towards the finish.
Settled down 3-4Ls near the tail, stayed on fairly final 300M, no threat to leaders.
Shared lead on the outside, outsprinted mid-straight, faded final 150M.
Tracked leaders but caught 3-wide no cover throughout, kept on same pace in straight, no threat final 150M.
Chased pace early on, shuffled back a bit middle stages but never too far off leaders, ran on only fairly from 400M, not reach contention.
Ridden early to get box seat then settled, sitting 2L behind fast pace set by joint leaders. Left fence 400m, strolled up quickly to take lead 200m, won eased down.
Hard ridden to lead passing 1000m before headed 750m. Retook lead passing 600m, pulled clear 300m, caught passing 200m, battled gamely to hold down 2nd.
Away well, ridden forward, settling close to rail 3-back from leaders. A little flat-footed top of straight before picking up momentum and flashing home for close 3rd.
Not much early speed, settling towards rear but wide to turn. Taken to centre track on straightening and finished strongly to just miss a placing.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, settling towards rear along rail. Made some progress soon after straightening but one-paced final 200m.
Pushed forward from wide draw, racing outside leader before taking narrow lead from 750m to 600m. Battled on well to 300m before giving ground gradually.
Pressed forward from an outside draw to settle in one-off position 3L from leaders. Bumped and unbalanced soon after entering straight, boxed on one-paced.
Jumped OK, no early pace, dropping to midfield along fence. Awkwardly placed turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Ridden to hold midfield position but kept wide mostly. Taken to centre field on straightening but found little under hard riding.
Began fairly, then crowded, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Last on entering straight before running past beaten horses.
Began awkwardly, ridden to make up ground, settling between horses behind midfield. Under pressure soon after entering straight, giving ground gradually.
Crowded out soon after start, dropping to last and taken to fence. Made some progress around home turn but spent force on straightening.
Outpaced and soon at rear in one-off position. Crowded out making the turn at 900m but never competitive.
Began well, sharing early pace but wide, before settling 2L behind leading pair entering final turn. Got shuffled back slightly turning for home and tired quickly soon after straightening.
Taken forward early and resisted temptation to take on the leader, settling clear 2nd, 2L behind. Challenged leader from the 400m, but took until 100m to get clear before clearing out late.
Pushed out early to lead by 2L up the back straight. Challenged at 400m, but didn't give up until peaking at 100m and fading. Just held onto 2nd late.
Taken forward early to be well placed 3rd, on the fence and 4L off the leader. Ran solidly in the straight, and catching 2nd towards the line.
Dropped back early from the wide draw to loop behind the field and sit 3rd last, on the fence and 9L off the leader. Ran steadily in the straight, showing an OK turn of foot in the last 100m.
Settled around midfield, 1 off the fence. Ran steadily to the line late, but slightly 1 paced.
Eased ahead early to sit forward of midfield, on the fence. Loomed up on the turn, but nothing came of it, and went to the line 1 paced under hands and heels.
Briefly crowded on jumping, but easily found his position just behind midfield, 1 off the fence. Only ran fairly to the line, and not used too much late.
Taken forward early to be handily placed 4th, 1 off the fence and 5L off the early leader. Ran steadily to the line late, but was no threat to those up front.
Eased forward early to sit towards the rear of the field, 1 off the fence. Keen on heels from the 1000m. Came off heels and taken wider in the straight, before battling to the line fairly late.
Dropped back from the wide draw to sit last in the early stages, 10L off the leader. Went to run on early in the straight, but ran flat from the 300m and only hands and heels late.
Looked to press forward early, before dropping back to sit at the rear of the field, 3 wide. Bumped and taken to 4 wide no cover at 900m. Plugged away, making no inroads in the straight.
Dropped to the rear of the field soon after jumping, and never in it.

OK early, finding a position just forward of midfield. Over raced when steadied at 1200m, and wide no cover from 1000m. Came off heels and very wide on turn. Nothing in the tank in the straight, easing late.
Fairly away, and eased forward early to sit around midfield, on the fence. Faded from the top of the straight, and not persevered with late.
Checked start, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, improved after 600M, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score narrowly.

Began well, raced 3 lengths back on rail, got its head up on a number of occasions when awkwardly placed close to the heels after 800M, dashed well early in straight and took the lead near 100M, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, carrier wider near 800M, gradually improved thereafter, dashed well early in straight, peaked near 100M, just stayed on to take 3rd.

Bumped start, raced 5 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight, severely checked near 50M and not able to be ridden out thereafter. (Lost right hind plate near 400M.)

Bumped start, raced 5Ls back at rear, travelled keenly and proved difficult to settle for some distance after 1000M, carried very wide on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked and shifted in abruptly near final 50M.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide in midfield, shifted out after 800M and gradually improved, shared lead turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in 2nd, shared lead turning in, peaked near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 1 out 1 back, same position on turn, no daylight early in straight, one-paced thereafter. (Dead-heat for 8th.)
Bumped start, raced 6 lengths back at rear, slightly improved after 600M, awkwardly placed near 350M, finished off evenly thereafter. (Dead-heat for 8th.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to position a length or so back on rail, there to turn, severely checked near 400M and got traffic, made no progress thereafter and eased final 100M.
Moderately away, raced 4 lengths or so back on rail, shifted out on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 2 wide in 5th, 3 wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 3 wide without cover behind midfield, carried wider on turn, emptied early in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, showed early speed to take the lead, shared lead turning in, emptied early in straight, unacceptable performance.
